var book = {
	"name": "Ezekiel",
	"numChapters": 48,
	"chapters": {
		"1": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">1 </span>Now it came about in the thirtieth year, on the fifth <i>day</i> of the fourth month, while I was by the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20466A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20466A\"></sup>river Chebar among the exiles, the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20466B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20466B\"></sup>heavens were opened and I saw <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20466C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20466C\"></sup>visions of God.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>(On the fifth of the month in the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20467D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20467D\"></sup>fifth year of King Jehoiachin’s exile,",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20468E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20468E\"></sup>word of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> came expressly to Ezekiel the priest, son of Buzi, in the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20468F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20468F\"></sup>land of the Chaldeans by the river Chebar; and there <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20468G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20468G\"></sup>the hand of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> came upon him.)",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>As I looked, behold, a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20469H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20469H\"></sup>storm wind was coming from the north, a great cloud with fire flashing forth continually and a bright light around it, and in its midst something like <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20469I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20469I\"></sup>glowing metal in the midst of the fire.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>Within it there were figures resembling <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20470J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20470J\"></sup>four living beings. And this was their appearance: they had human <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20470K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20470K\"></sup>form.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>Each of them had <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20471L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20471L\"></sup>four faces and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20471M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20471M\"></sup>four wings.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>Their legs were straight and their feet were like a calf’s hoof, and they gleamed like <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20472N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20472N\"></sup>burnished bronze.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>Under their wings on their <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20473O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20473O\"></sup>four sides <i>were</i> human <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20473P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20473P\"></sup>hands. As for the faces and wings of the four of them,",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>their wings touched one another; <i>their faces</i> did <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20474Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20474Q\"></sup>not turn when they moved, each <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20474R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20474R\"></sup>went straight forward.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>As for the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20475S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20475S\"></sup>form of their faces, <i>each</i> had the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20475T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20475T\"></sup>face of a man; all four had the face of a lion on the right and the face of a bull on the left, and all four had the face of an eagle.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>Such were their faces. Their wings were spread out above; each had two touching another <i>being</i>, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20476U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20476U\"></sup>two covering their bodies.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20477V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20477V\"></sup>each went straight forward; <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20477W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20477W\"></sup>wherever the spirit was about to go, they would go, without turning as they went.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>In the midst of the living beings there was something that looked like burning coals of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20478X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20478X\"></sup>fire, like torches darting back and forth among the living beings. The fire was bright, and lightning was flashing from the fire.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>And the living beings <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20479Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20479Y\"></sup>ran to and fro like bolts of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20479Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20479Z\"></sup>lightning.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>Now as I looked at the living beings, behold, there was one <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20480AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20480AA\"></sup>wheel on the earth beside the living beings, for <i>each of</i> the four of them.",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>The <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20481AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20481AB\"></sup>appearance of the wheels and their workmanship <i>was</i> like sparkling <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20481AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20481AC\"></sup>beryl, and all four of them had the same form, their appearance and workmanship <i>being</i> as if one wheel were within another.",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>Whenever they moved, they moved in any of their four directions without <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20482AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20482AD\"></sup>turning as they moved.",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>As for their rims they were lofty and awesome, and the rims of all four of them were <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20483AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20483AE\"></sup>full of eyes round about.",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20484AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20484AF\"></sup>Whenever the living beings moved, the wheels moved with them. And whenever the living beings <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20484AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20484AG\"></sup>rose from the earth, the wheels rose <i>also</i>.",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20485AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20485AH\"></sup>Wherever the spirit was about to go, they would go in that direction. And the wheels rose close beside them; for the spirit of the living beings <i>was</i> in the wheels.",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20486AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20486AI\"></sup>Whenever those went, these went; and whenever those stood still, these stood still. And whenever those rose from the earth, the wheels rose close beside them; for the spirit of the living beings <i>was</i> in the wheels.",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>Now <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20487AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20487AJ\"></sup>over the heads of the living beings <i>there was</i> something like an expanse, like the awesome gleam of crystal, spread out over their heads.",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>Under the expanse their wings <i>were stretched out</i> straight, one toward the other; each one also had <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20488AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20488AK\"></sup>two wings covering its body on the one side and on the other.",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>I also heard the sound of their wings like the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20489AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20489AL\"></sup>sound of abundant waters as they went, like the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20489AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20489AM\"></sup>voice of the Almighty, a sound of tumult like the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20489AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20489AN\"></sup>sound of an army camp; whenever they stood still, they dropped their wings.",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup>And there came a voice from above the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20490AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20490AO\"></sup>expanse that was over their heads; whenever they stood still, they dropped their wings.",
			"26": "<sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup>Now <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20491AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20491AP\"></sup>above the expanse that was over their heads there was something <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20491AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20491AQ\"></sup>resembling a throne, like <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20491AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20491AR\"></sup>lapis lazuli in appearance; and on that which resembled a throne, high up, <i>was</i> a figure with the appearance of a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20491AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20491AS\"></sup>man.",
			"27": "<sup class=\"versenum\">27 </sup>Then I noticed from the appearance of His loins and upward something <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20492AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20492AT\"></sup>like glowing metal that looked like fire all around within it, and from the appearance of His loins and downward I saw something like fire; and <i>there was</i> a radiance around Him.",
			"28": "<sup class=\"versenum\">28 </sup>As the appearance of the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20493AU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AU&quot;&gt;AU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20493AU\"></sup>rainbow in the clouds on a rainy day, so <i>was</i> the appearance of the surrounding radiance. Such <i>was</i> the appearance of the likeness of the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20493AV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AV&quot;&gt;AV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20493AV\"></sup>glory of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>. And when I saw <i>it</i>, I <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20493AW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AW&quot;&gt;AW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20493AW\"></sup>fell on my face and heard a voice speaking."
		},
		"2": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">2 </span>Then He said to me, “Son of man, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20494A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20494A\"></sup>stand on your feet that I may speak with you!”",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>As He spoke to me the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20495B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20495B\"></sup>Spirit entered me and set me on my feet; and I heard <i>Him</i> speaking to me.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>Then He said to me, “Son of man, I am sending you to the sons of Israel, to a rebellious people who have <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20496C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20496C\"></sup>rebelled against Me; <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20496D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20496D\"></sup>they and their fathers have transgressed against Me to this very day.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>I am sending you to them who are <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20497E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20497E\"></sup>stubborn and obstinate children, and you shall say to them, ‘Thus says the Lord <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">God</span>.’",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>As for them, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20498F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20498F\"></sup>whether they listen or not—for they are a rebellious house—they will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20498G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20498G\"></sup>know that a prophet has been among them.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>And you, son of man, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20499H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20499H\"></sup>neither fear them nor fear their words, though <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20499I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20499I\"></sup>thistles and thorns are with you and you sit on scorpions; neither fear their words nor be dismayed at their presence, for they are a rebellious house.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>But you shall <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20500J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20500J\"></sup>speak My words to them <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20500K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20500K\"></sup>whether they listen or not, for they are rebellious.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>“Now you, son of man, listen to what I am speaking to you; do not be rebellious like that rebellious house. Open your mouth and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20501L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20501L\"></sup>eat what I am giving you.”",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>Then I looked, and behold, a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20502M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20502M\"></sup>hand was extended to me; and lo, a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20502N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20502N\"></sup>scroll <i>was</i> in it.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>When He spread it out before me, it was written on the front and back, and written on it were lamentations, mourning and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20503O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20503O\"></sup>woe."
		},
		"3": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">3 </span>Then He said to me, “Son of man, eat what you find; <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20504A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20504A\"></sup>eat this scroll, and go, speak to the house of Israel.”",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>So I <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20505B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20505B\"></sup>opened my mouth, and He fed me this scroll.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>He said to me, “Son of man, feed your stomach and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20506C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20506C\"></sup>fill your body with this scroll which I am giving you.” Then I <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20506D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20506D\"></sup>ate it, and it was sweet as <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20506E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20506E\"></sup>honey in my mouth.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>Then He said to me, “Son of man, go to the house of Israel and speak with My words to them.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>For <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20508F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20508F\"></sup>you are not being sent to a people of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20508G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20508G\"></sup>unintelligible speech or difficult language, <i>but</i> to the house of Israel,",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>nor to many peoples of unintelligible speech or difficult language, whose words you cannot understand. But I have sent you to them who should listen to you;",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>yet the house of Israel will not be willing to listen to you, since they are <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20510H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20510H\"></sup>not willing to listen to Me. Surely the whole house of Israel is stubborn and obstinate.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>Behold, I have made your face as hard as their faces and your forehead as hard as their foreheads.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>Like emery harder than flint I have made your forehead. Do not be afraid of them or be dismayed before them, though they are a rebellious house.”",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>Moreover, He said to me, “Son of man, take into your heart all My <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20513I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20513I\"></sup>words which I will speak to you and listen closely.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>Go to the exiles, to the sons of your people, and speak to them and tell them, whether they listen or not, ‘Thus says the Lord <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">God</span>.’”",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>Then the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20515J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20515J\"></sup>Spirit lifted me up, and I heard a great <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20515K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20515K\"></sup>rumbling sound behind me, “Blessed be the glory of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> in His place.”",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>And I <i>heard</i> the sound of the wings of the living beings touching one another and the sound of the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20516L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20516L\"></sup>wheels beside them, even a great rumbling sound.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>So the Spirit lifted me up and took me away; and I went embittered in the rage of my spirit, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20517M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20517M\"></sup>the hand of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> was strong on me.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>Then I came to the exiles who lived beside the river Chebar at Tel-abib, and I sat there <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20518N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20518N\"></sup>seven days where they were living, causing consternation among them.",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20519O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20519O\"></sup>At the end of seven days the word of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> came to me, saying,",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>“Son of man, I have appointed you a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20520P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20520P\"></sup>watchman to the house of Israel; whenever you hear a word from My mouth, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20520Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20520Q\"></sup>warn them from Me.",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>When I say to the wicked, ‘You will surely die,’ and you do not warn him or speak out to warn the wicked from his wicked way that he may live, that wicked man shall die in his iniquity, but his <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20521R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20521R\"></sup>blood I will require at your hand.",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>Yet if you have <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20522S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20522S\"></sup>warned the wicked and he does not turn from his wickedness or from his wicked way, he shall die in his iniquity; but you have <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20522T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20522T\"></sup>delivered yourself.",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>Again, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20523U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20523U\"></sup>when a righteous man turns away from his righteousness and commits iniquity, and I place an <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20523V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20523V\"></sup>obstacle before him, he will die; since you have not warned him, he shall die in his sin, and his righteous deeds which he has done shall not be remembered; but his blood I will require at your hand.",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>However, if you have <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20524W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20524W\"></sup>warned the righteous man that the righteous should not sin and he does not sin, he shall surely live because he took warning; and you have delivered yourself.”",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>The hand of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> was on me there, and He said to me, “Get up, go out to the plain, and there I will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20525X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20525X\"></sup>speak to you.”",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>So I got up and went out to the plain; and behold, the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20526Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20526Y\"></sup>glory of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> was standing there, like the glory which <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20526Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20526Z\"></sup>I saw by the river Chebar, and I fell on my face.",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>The <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20527AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20527AA\"></sup>Spirit then entered me and made me stand on my feet, and He spoke with me and said to me, “Go, shut yourself up in your house.",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup>As for you, son of man, they will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20528AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20528AB\"></sup>put ropes on you and bind you with them so that you cannot go out among them.",
			"26": "<sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup>Moreover, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20529AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20529AC\"></sup>I will make your tongue stick to the roof of your mouth so that you will be mute and cannot be a man who rebukes them, for they are a rebellious house.",
			"27": "<sup class=\"versenum\">27 </sup>But <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20530AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20530AD\"></sup>when I speak to you, I will open your mouth and you will say to them, ‘Thus says the Lord <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">God</span>.’ He who hears, let him hear; and he who refuses, let him refuse; <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20530AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20530AE\"></sup>for they are a rebellious house."
		},
		"4": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">4 </span>“Now you son of man, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20531A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20531A\"></sup>get yourself a brick, place it before you and inscribe a city on it, Jerusalem.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>Then <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20532B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20532B\"></sup>lay siege against it, build a siege wall, raise up a ramp, pitch camps and place battering rams against it all around.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>Then get yourself an iron plate and set it up as an iron wall between you and the city, and set your face toward it so that <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20533C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20533C\"></sup>it is under siege, and besiege it. This is a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20533D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20533D\"></sup>sign to the house of Israel.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>“As for you, lie down on your left side and lay the iniquity of the house of Israel on it; you shall <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20534E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20534E\"></sup>bear their iniquity for the number of days that you lie on it.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>For I have assigned you a number of days corresponding to the years of their iniquity, three hundred and ninety days; thus <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20535F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20535F\"></sup>you shall bear the iniquity of the house of Israel.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>When you have completed these, you shall lie down a second time, <i>but</i> on your right side and bear the iniquity of the house of Judah; I have assigned it to you for forty days, a day for <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20536G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20536G\"></sup>each year.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>Then you shall set your face toward the siege of Jerusalem with your arm bared and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20537H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20537H\"></sup>prophesy against it.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>Now behold, I will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20538I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20538I\"></sup>put ropes on you so that you cannot turn from one side to the other until you have completed the days of your siege.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>“But as for you, take wheat, barley, beans, lentils, millet and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20539J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20539J\"></sup>spelt, put them in one vessel and make them into bread for yourself; you shall eat it according to the number of the days that you lie on your side, three hundred and ninety days.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>Your food which you eat <i>shall be</i> <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20540K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20540K\"></sup>twenty shekels a day by weight; you shall eat it from time to time.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>The water you drink shall be the sixth part of a hin by measure; you shall drink it from time to time.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>You shall eat it as a barley cake, having baked <i>it</i> in their sight over human <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20542L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20542L\"></sup>dung.”",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>Then the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> said, “Thus will the sons of Israel eat their bread <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20543M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20543M\"></sup>unclean among the nations where I will banish them.”",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>But I said, “<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20544N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20544N\"></sup>Ah, Lord <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">God</span>! Behold, I have <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20544O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20544O\"></sup>never been defiled; for from my youth until now I have never eaten what <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20544P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20544P\"></sup>died of itself or was torn by beasts, nor has any <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20544Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20544Q\"></sup>unclean meat ever entered my mouth.”",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>Then He said to me, “See, I will give you cow’s dung in place of human dung over which you will prepare your bread.”",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>Moreover, He said to me, “Son of man, behold, I am going to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20546R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20546R\"></sup>break the staff of bread in Jerusalem, and they will eat bread by <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20546S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20546S\"></sup>weight and with anxiety, and drink water by <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20546T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20546T\"></sup>measure and in horror,",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>because bread and water will be scarce; and they will be appalled with one another and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20547U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20547U\"></sup>waste away in their iniquity."
		},
		"5": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">5 </span>“As for you, son of man, take a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20548A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20548A\"></sup>sharp sword; take and use it <i>as</i> a barber’s razor on your head and beard. Then take <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20548B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20548B\"></sup>scales for weighing and divide the hair.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>One third you shall burn in the fire at the center of the city, when the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20549C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20549C\"></sup>days of the siege are completed. Then you shall take one third and strike <i>it</i> with the sword all around the city, and one third you shall scatter to the wind; and I will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20549D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20549D\"></sup>unsheathe a sword behind them.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>Take also a few in number from them and bind them in the edges of your <i>robes</i>.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>Take again some of them and throw them into the fire and burn them in the fire; from it a fire will spread to all the house of Israel.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>“Thus says the Lord <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">God</span>, ‘This is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20552E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20552E\"></sup>Jerusalem; I have set her at the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20552F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20552F\"></sup>center of the nations, with lands around her.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>But she has rebelled against My ordinances more wickedly than the nations and against My statutes <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20553G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20553G\"></sup>more than the lands which surround her; for they have <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20553H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20553H\"></sup>rejected My ordinances and have not walked in My statutes.’",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>Therefore, thus says the Lord <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">God</span>, ‘Because you have <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20554I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20554I\"></sup>more turmoil than the nations which surround you <i>and</i> have not walked in My statutes, nor observed My ordinances, nor observed the ordinances of the nations which surround you,’",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>therefore, thus says the Lord <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">God</span>, ‘Behold, I, even I, am <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20555J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20555J\"></sup>against you, and I will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20555K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20555K\"></sup>execute judgments among you in the sight of the nations.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>And because of all your abominations, I will do among you what I have <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20556L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20556L\"></sup>not done, and the like of which I will never do again.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>Therefore, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20557M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20557M\"></sup>fathers will eat <i>their</i> sons among you, and sons will eat their fathers; for I will execute judgments on you and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20557N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20557N\"></sup>scatter all your remnant to every wind.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>So as I live,’ declares the Lord <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">God</span>, ‘surely, because you have <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20558O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20558O\"></sup>defiled My sanctuary with all your <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20558P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20558P\"></sup>detestable idols and with all your abominations, therefore I will also withdraw, and My eye will have no pity and I will not spare.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>One third of you will die by <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20559Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20559Q\"></sup>plague or be consumed by famine among you, one third will fall by the sword around you, and one third I will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20559R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20559R\"></sup>scatter to every wind, and I will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20559S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20559S\"></sup>unsheathe a sword behind them.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>‘Thus My anger will be spent and I will satisfy My wrath on them, and I will be <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20560T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20560T\"></sup>appeased; then they will know that I, the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, have <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20560U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20560U\"></sup>spoken in My zeal when I have spent My wrath upon them.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>Moreover, I will make you a desolation and a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20561V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20561V\"></sup>reproach among the nations which surround you, in the sight of all who pass by.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>So it will be a reproach, a reviling, a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20562W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20562W\"></sup>warning and an object of horror to the nations who surround you when I <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20562X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20562X\"></sup>execute judgments against you in anger, wrath and raging rebukes. I, the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, have spoken.",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>When I send against them the deadly arrows of famine which were for the destruction of those whom I will send to destroy you, then I will also intensify the famine upon you and break the staff of bread.",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>Moreover, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20564Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20564Y\"></sup>I will send on you famine and wild beasts, and they will bereave you of children; <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20564Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20564Z\"></sup>plague and bloodshed also will pass through you, and I will bring the sword on you. I, the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, have spoken.’”"
		},
		"6": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">6 </span>And the word of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> came to me saying,",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>“Son of man, set your face toward the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20566A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20566A\"></sup>mountains of Israel, and prophesy against them",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>and say, ‘Mountains of Israel, listen to the word of the Lord <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">God</span>! Thus says the Lord <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">God</span> to the mountains, the hills, the ravines and the valleys: “Behold, I Myself am going to bring a sword on you, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20567B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20567B\"></sup>I will destroy your high places.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>So your <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20568C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20568C\"></sup>altars will become desolate and your incense altars will be smashed; and I will make your slain fall in front of your idols.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>I will also lay the dead bodies of the sons of Israel in front of their idols; and I will scatter your <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20569D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20569D\"></sup>bones around your altars.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>In all your dwellings, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20570E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20570E\"></sup>cities will become waste and the high places will be desolate, that your altars may become waste and desolate, your <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20570F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20570F\"></sup>idols may be broken and brought to an end, your incense altars may be cut down, and your works may be blotted out.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>The slain will fall among you, and you will know that I am the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>“However, I will leave a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20572G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20572G\"></sup>remnant, for you will have those who <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20572H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20572H\"></sup>escaped the sword among the nations when you are scattered among the countries.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>Then those of you who escape will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20573I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20573I\"></sup>remember Me among the nations to which they will be carried captive, how I have <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20573J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20573J\"></sup>been hurt by their adulterous hearts which turned away from Me, and by their eyes which played the harlot after their idols; and they will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20573K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20573K\"></sup>loathe themselves in their own sight for the evils which they have committed, for all their abominations.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>Then they will know that I am the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>; I have not said in vain that I would inflict this disaster on them.”’",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>“Thus says the Lord <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">God</span>, ‘Clap your hand, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20575L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20575L\"></sup>stamp your foot and say, “<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20575M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20575M\"></sup>Alas, because of all the evil abominations of the house of Israel, which will fall by <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20575N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20575N\"></sup>sword, famine and plague!",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>He who is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20576O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20576O\"></sup>far off will die by the plague, and he who is near will fall by the sword, and he who remains and is besieged will die by the famine. Thus will I <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20576P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20576P\"></sup>spend My wrath on them.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>Then you will know that I am the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, when their <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20577Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20577Q\"></sup>slain are among their idols around their altars, on <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20577R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20577R\"></sup>every high hill, on all the tops of the mountains, under every green tree and under every leafy oak—the places where they offered soothing aroma to all their idols.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>So throughout all their habitations I will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20578S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20578S\"></sup>stretch out My hand against them and make the land more desolate and waste than the wilderness toward Diblah; thus they will know that I am the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.”’”"
		},
		"7": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">7 </span>Moreover, the word of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> came to me saying,",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>“And you, son of man, thus says the Lord <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">God</span> to the land of Israel, ‘An <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20580A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20580A\"></sup>end! The end is coming on the four corners of the land.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>Now the end is upon you, and I will send My anger against you; I will judge you according to your ways and bring all your abominations upon you.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>For My eye will have no pity on you, nor will I spare <i>you</i>, but I will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20582B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20582B\"></sup>bring your ways upon you, and your abominations will be among you; then you will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20582C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20582C\"></sup>know that I am the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>!’",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>“Thus says the Lord <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">God</span>, ‘A <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20583D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20583D\"></sup>disaster, unique disaster, behold it is coming!",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>An end is coming; the end has come! It has <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20584E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20584E\"></sup>awakened against you; behold, it has come!",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>Your doom has come to you, O inhabitant of the land. The <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20585F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20585F\"></sup>time has come, the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20585G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20585G\"></sup>day is near—tumult rather than joyful shouting on the mountains.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>Now I will shortly <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20586H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20586H\"></sup>pour out My wrath on you and spend My anger against you; <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20586I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20586I\"></sup>judge you according to your ways and bring on you all your abominations.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>My eye will show no pity nor will I spare. I will repay you according to your ways, while your abominations are in your midst; then you will know that I, the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, do the smiting.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>‘Behold, the day! Behold, it is coming! <i>Your</i> doom has gone forth; the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20588J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20588J\"></sup>rod has budded, arrogance has blossomed.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>Violence has grown into a rod of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20589K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20589K\"></sup>wickedness. None of them <i>shall remain</i>, none of their people, none of their <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20589L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20589L\"></sup>wealth, nor anything eminent among them.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>The <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20590M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20590M\"></sup>time has come, the day has arrived. Let not the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20590N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20590N\"></sup>buyer rejoice nor the seller mourn; for <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20590O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20590O\"></sup>wrath is against all their multitude.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>Indeed, the seller will not <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20591P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20591P\"></sup>regain what he sold as long as they <i>both</i> live; for the vision regarding all their multitude will not be averted, nor will any of them maintain his life by his iniquity.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>‘They have <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20592Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20592Q\"></sup>blown the trumpet and made everything ready, but no one is going to the battle, for My wrath is against all their multitude.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>The <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20593R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20593R\"></sup>sword is outside and the plague and the famine are within. He who is in the field will die by the sword; famine and the plague will also consume those in the city.",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>Even when their survivors <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20594S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20594S\"></sup>escape, they will be on the mountains like <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20594T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20594T\"></sup>doves of the valleys, all of them <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20594U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20594U\"></sup>mourning, each over his own iniquity.",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>All <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20595V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20595V\"></sup>hands will hang limp and all knees will become <i>like</i> water.",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>They will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20596W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20596W\"></sup>gird themselves with sackcloth and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20596X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20596X\"></sup>shuddering will overwhelm them; and shame <i>will be</i> on all faces and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20596Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20596Y\"></sup>baldness on all their heads.",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>They will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20597Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20597Z\"></sup>fling their silver into the streets and their gold will become an abhorrent thing; their <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20597AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20597AA\"></sup>silver and their gold will not be able to deliver them in the day of the wrath of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>. They cannot satisfy their appetite nor can they fill their stomachs, for their iniquity has become an occasion of stumbling.",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>They transformed the beauty of His ornaments into pride, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20598AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20598AB\"></sup>they made the images of their abominations <i>and</i> their detestable things with it; therefore I will make it an abhorrent thing to them.",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>I will give it into the hands of the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20599AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20599AC\"></sup>foreigners as plunder and to the wicked of the earth as spoil, and they will profane it.",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>I will also turn My <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20600AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20600AD\"></sup>face from them, and they will profane My secret place; then robbers will enter and profane it.",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>‘<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20601AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20601AE\"></sup>Make the chain, for the land is full of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20601AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20601AF\"></sup>bloody crimes and the city is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20601AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20601AG\"></sup>full of violence.",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>Therefore, I will bring the worst of the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20602AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20602AH\"></sup>nations, and they will possess their houses. I will also make the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20602AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20602AI\"></sup>pride of the strong ones cease, and their <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20602AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20602AJ\"></sup>holy places will be profaned.",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup>When anguish comes, they will seek <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20603AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20603AK\"></sup>peace, but there will be none.",
			"26": "<sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20604AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20604AL\"></sup>Disaster will come upon disaster and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20604AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20604AM\"></sup>rumor will be <i>added</i> to rumor; then they will seek a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20604AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20604AN\"></sup>vision from a prophet, but the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20604AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20604AO\"></sup>law will be lost from the priest and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20604AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20604AP\"></sup>counsel from the elders.",
			"27": "<sup class=\"versenum\">27 </sup>The king will mourn, the prince will be <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20605AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20605AQ\"></sup>clothed with horror, and the hands of the people of the land will tremble. According to their conduct I will deal with them, and by their judgments I will judge them. And they will know that I am the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.’”"
		},
		"8": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">8 </span>It came about in the sixth year, on the fifth <i>day</i> of the sixth month, as I was sitting in my house with the elders of Judah sitting before me, that the hand of the Lord <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">God</span> fell on me there.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>Then I looked, and behold, a likeness as the appearance of a man; from His loins and downward <i>there was</i> the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20607A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20607A\"></sup>appearance of fire, and from His loins and upward the appearance of brightness, like the appearance <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20607B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20607B\"></sup>of glowing metal.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>He stretched out the form of a hand and caught me by a lock of my head; and the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20608C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20608C\"></sup>Spirit lifted me up between earth and heaven and brought me in the visions of God to Jerusalem, to the entrance of the north gate of the inner <i>court</i>, where the seat of the idol of jealousy, which <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20608D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20608D\"></sup>provokes to jealousy, was <i>located</i>.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>And behold, the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20609E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20609E\"></sup>glory of the God of Israel <i>was</i> there, like the appearance which I saw in the plain.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>Then He said to me, “Son of man, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20610F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20610F\"></sup>raise your eyes now toward the north.” So I raised my eyes toward the north, and behold, to the north of the altar gate <i>was</i> this <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20610G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20610G\"></sup>idol of jealousy at the entrance.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>And He said to me, “Son of man, do you see what they are doing, the great <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20611H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20611H\"></sup>abominations which the house of Israel are committing here, so that I would be far from My sanctuary? But yet you will see still greater abominations.”",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>Then He brought me to the entrance of the court, and when I looked, behold, a hole in the wall.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>He said to me, “Son of man, now <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20613I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20613I\"></sup>dig through the wall.” So I dug through the wall, and behold, an entrance.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>And He said to me, “Go in and see the wicked abominations that they are committing here.”",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>So I entered and looked, and behold, every form of creeping things and beasts <i>and</i> detestable things, with all the idols of the house of Israel, were carved on the wall all around.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>Standing in front of them were <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20616J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20616J\"></sup>seventy <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20616K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20616K\"></sup>elders of the house of Israel, with Jaazaniah the son of Shaphan standing among them, each man with his <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20616L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20616L\"></sup>censer in his hand and the fragrance of the cloud of incense rising.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>Then He said to me, “Son of man, do you see what the elders of the house of Israel are committing in the dark, each man in the room of his carved images? For they say, ‘<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20617M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20617M\"></sup>The <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> does not see us; the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> has <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20617N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20617N\"></sup>forsaken the land.’”",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>And He said to me, “Yet you will see still greater abominations which they are committing.”",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>Then He brought me to the entrance of the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20619O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20619O\"></sup>gate of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord’s</span> house which <i>was</i> toward the north; and behold, women were sitting there weeping for Tammuz.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>He said to me, “Do you see <i>this</i>, son of man? Yet you will see still greater abominations than these.”",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>Then He brought me into the inner court of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord’s</span> house. And behold, at the entrance to the temple of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, between the porch and the altar, <i>were</i> about twenty-five men with their <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20621P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20621P\"></sup>backs to the temple of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> and their faces toward the east; and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20621Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20621Q\"></sup>they were prostrating themselves eastward toward the sun.",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>He said to me, “Do you see <i>this</i>, son of man? Is it too light a thing for the house of Judah to commit the abominations which they have committed here, that they have <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20622R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20622R\"></sup>filled the land with violence and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20622S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20622S\"></sup>provoked Me repeatedly? For behold, they are putting the twig to their nose.",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>Therefore, I indeed will deal in wrath. My eye will have no pity nor will I spare; and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20623T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20623T\"></sup>though they cry in My ears with a loud voice, yet I will not listen to them.”"
		},
		"9": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">9 </span>Then He cried out in my hearing with a loud <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20624A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20624A\"></sup>voice saying, “Draw near, O executioners of the city, each with his destroying weapon in his hand.”",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>Behold, six men came from the direction of the upper gate which faces north, each with his shattering weapon in his hand; and among them was <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20625B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20625B\"></sup>a certain man clothed in linen with a writing case at his loins. And they went in and stood beside the bronze altar.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>Then the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20626C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20626C\"></sup>glory of the God of Israel went up from the cherub on which it had been, to the threshold of the temple. And He called to the man clothed in linen at whose loins was the writing case.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>The <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> said to him, “Go through the midst of the city, <i>even</i> through the midst of Jerusalem, and put a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20627D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20627D\"></sup>mark on the foreheads of the men who <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20627E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20627E\"></sup>sigh and groan over all the abominations which are being committed in its midst.”",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>But to the others He said in my hearing, “Go through the city after him and strike; do not let your eye have pity and do not spare.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>Utterly <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20629F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20629F\"></sup>slay old men, young men, maidens, little children, and women, but do not <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20629G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20629G\"></sup>touch any man on whom is the mark; and you shall <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20629H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20629H\"></sup>start from My sanctuary.” So they started with the elders who <i>were</i> before the temple.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>And He said to them, “<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20630I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20630I\"></sup>Defile the temple and fill the courts with the slain. Go out!” Thus they went out and struck down <i>the people</i> in the city.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>As they were striking <i>the people</i> and I <i>alone</i> was left, I <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20631J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20631J\"></sup>fell on my face and cried out saying, “<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20631K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20631K\"></sup>Alas, Lord <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">God</span>! Are You destroying the whole remnant of Israel by pouring out Your wrath on Jerusalem?”",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>Then He said to me, “The iniquity of the house of Israel and Judah is very, very great, and the land is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20632L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20632L\"></sup>filled with blood and the city is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20632M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20632M\"></sup>full of perversion; for <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20632N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20632N\"></sup>they say, ‘The <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> has forsaken the land, and the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> does not see!’",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>But as for Me, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20633O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20633O\"></sup>My eye will have no pity nor will I spare, but <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20633P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20633P\"></sup>I will bring their conduct upon their heads.”",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>Then behold, the man clothed in linen at whose loins was the writing case reported, saying, “I have done just as You have commanded me.”"
		},
		"10": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">10 </span>Then I looked, and behold, in the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20635A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20635A\"></sup>expanse that was over the heads of the cherubim something like a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20635B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20635B\"></sup>sapphire stone, in appearance resembling a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20635C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20635C\"></sup>throne, appeared above them.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>And He spoke to the man clothed in linen and said, “Enter between the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20636D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20636D\"></sup>whirling wheels under the cherubim and fill your hands with <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20636E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20636E\"></sup>coals of fire from between the cherubim and scatter <i>them</i> over the city.” And he entered in my sight.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>Now the cherubim were standing on the right side of the temple when the man entered, and the cloud filled the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20637F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20637F\"></sup>inner court.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>Then the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20638G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20638G\"></sup>glory of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> went up from the cherub to the threshold of the temple, and the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20638H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20638H\"></sup>temple was filled with the cloud and the court was filled with the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20638I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20638I\"></sup>brightness of the glory of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>Moreover, the sound of the wings of the cherubim was heard as far as the outer court, like the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20639J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20639J\"></sup>voice of God Almighty when He speaks.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>It came about when He commanded the man clothed in linen, saying, “Take fire from between the whirling wheels, from between the cherubim,” he entered and stood beside a wheel.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>Then the cherub stretched out his hand from between the cherubim to the fire which was between the cherubim, took <i>some</i> and put <i>it</i> into the hands of the one clothed in linen, who took <i>it</i> and went out.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>The cherubim appeared to have the form of a man’s hand under their wings.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>Then I looked, and behold, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20643K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20643K\"></sup>four wheels beside the cherubim, one wheel beside each cherub; and the appearance of the wheels <i>was</i> like the gleam of a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20643L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20643L\"></sup>Tarshish stone.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>As for their appearance, all four of them had the same likeness, as if one wheel were within another wheel.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>When they moved, they went <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20645M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20645M\"></sup>in <i>any of</i> their four directions without turning as they went; but they followed in the direction which they faced, without turning as they went.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>Their <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20646N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20646N\"></sup>whole body, their backs, their hands, their wings and the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20646O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20646O\"></sup>wheels were full of eyes all around, the wheels belonging to all four of them.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>The wheels were called in my hearing, the whirling wheels.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20648P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20648P\"></sup>each one had four faces. The first face <i>was</i> the face of a cherub, the second face <i>was</i> the face of a man, the third the face of a lion, and the fourth the face of an eagle.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>Then the cherubim rose up. They are the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20649Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20649Q\"></sup>living beings that I saw by the river Chebar.",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>Now when the cherubim moved, the wheels would go beside them; also when the cherubim lifted up their wings to rise from the ground, the wheels would not turn from beside them.",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>When the cherubim <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20651R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20651R\"></sup>stood still, the wheels would stand still; and when they rose up, the wheels would rise with them, for the spirit of the living beings <i>was</i> in them.",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>Then the glory of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> departed from the threshold of the temple and stood <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20652S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20652S\"></sup>over the cherubim.",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>When <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20653T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20653T\"></sup>the cherubim departed, they lifted their wings and rose up from the earth in my sight with the wheels beside them; and they stood still at the entrance of the east gate of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord’s</span> house, and the glory of the God of Israel hovered over them.",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>These are the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20654U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20654U\"></sup>living beings that I saw beneath the God of Israel by <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20654V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20654V\"></sup>the river Chebar; so I knew that they <i>were</i> cherubim.",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20655W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20655W\"></sup>Each one had four faces and each one four wings, and beneath their wings <i>was</i> the form of human hands.",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>As for the likeness of their faces, they were the same faces whose appearance I had seen by the river Chebar. Each one went straight ahead."
		},
		"11": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">11 </span>Moreover, the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20657A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20657A\"></sup>Spirit lifted me up and brought me to the east gate of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord’s</span> house which faced eastward. And behold, <i>there were</i> twenty-five men at the entrance of the gate, and among them I saw Jaazaniah son of Azzur and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20657B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20657B\"></sup>Pelatiah son of Benaiah, leaders of the people.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>He said to me, “Son of man, these are the men who devise iniquity and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20658C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20658C\"></sup>give evil advice in this city,",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>who say, ‘<i>The time</i> is not near to build houses. This <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20659D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20659D\"></sup><i>city</i> is the pot and we are the flesh.’",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>Therefore, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20660E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20660E\"></sup>prophesy against them, son of man, prophesy!”",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>Then the Spirit of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> fell upon me, and He said to me, “Say, ‘Thus says the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, “So you think, house of Israel, for <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20661F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20661F\"></sup>I know your <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20661G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20661G\"></sup>thoughts.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>You have <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20662H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20662H\"></sup>multiplied your slain in this city, filling its streets with them.”",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>Therefore, thus says the Lord <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">God</span>, “Your <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20663I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20663I\"></sup>slain whom you have laid in the midst of the city are the flesh and this <i>city</i> is the pot; but I will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20663J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20663J\"></sup>bring you out of it.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>You have <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20664K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20664K\"></sup>feared a sword; so I will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20664L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20664L\"></sup>bring a sword upon you,” the Lord <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">God</span> declares.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>“And I will bring you out of the midst of the city and deliver you into the hands of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20665M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20665M\"></sup>strangers and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20665N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20665N\"></sup>execute judgments against you.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>You will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20666O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20666O\"></sup>fall by the sword. I will judge you to the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20666P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20666P\"></sup>border of Israel; so you shall know that I am the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>This <i>city</i> will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20667Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20667Q\"></sup>not be a pot for you, nor will you be flesh in the midst of it, <i>but</i> I will judge you to the border of Israel.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>Thus you will know that I am the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>; for you have not walked in My statutes nor have you <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20668R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20668R\"></sup>executed My ordinances, but have acted according to the ordinances of the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20668S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20668S\"></sup>nations around you.”’”",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>Now it came about as I prophesied, that <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20669T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20669T\"></sup>Pelatiah son of Benaiah died. Then I fell on my face and cried out with a loud voice and said, “<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20669U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20669U\"></sup>Alas, Lord <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">God</span>! Will You bring the remnant of Israel to a complete end?”",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>Then the word of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> came to me, saying,",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>“Son of man, your brothers, your relatives, your fellow exiles and the whole house of Israel, all of them, <i>are those</i> to whom the inhabitants of Jerusalem have said, ‘Go far from the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>; this land has been given <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20671V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20671V\"></sup>us as a possession.’",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>Therefore say, ‘Thus says the Lord <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">God</span>, “Though I had removed them far away among the nations and though I had scattered them among the countries, yet I was a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20672W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20672W\"></sup>sanctuary for them a little while in the countries where they had gone.”’",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>Therefore say, ‘Thus says the Lord <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">God</span>, “I will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20673X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20673X\"></sup>gather you from the peoples and assemble you out of the countries among which you have been scattered, and I will give you the land of Israel.”’",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>When they come there, they will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20674Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20674Y\"></sup>remove all its <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20674Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20674Z\"></sup>detestable things and all its abominations from it.",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>And I will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20675AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20675AA\"></sup>give them one heart, and put a new spirit within them. And I will take the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20675AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20675AB\"></sup>heart of stone out of their flesh and give them a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20675AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20675AC\"></sup>heart of flesh,",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>that they may <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20676AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20676AD\"></sup>walk in My statutes and keep My ordinances and do them. Then they will be <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20676AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20676AE\"></sup>My people, and I shall be their God.",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>But as for those whose hearts go after their <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20677AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20677AF\"></sup>detestable things and abominations, I will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20677AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20677AG\"></sup>bring their conduct down on their heads,” declares the Lord <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">God</span>.",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>Then the cherubim <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20678AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20678AH\"></sup>lifted up their wings with the wheels beside them, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20678AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20678AI\"></sup>the glory of the God of Israel hovered over them.",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>The <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20679AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20679AJ\"></sup>glory of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> went up from the midst of the city and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20679AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20679AK\"></sup>stood over the mountain which is east of the city.",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>And the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20680AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20680AL\"></sup>Spirit lifted me up and brought me in a vision by the Spirit of God to the exiles in Chaldea. So the vision that I had seen <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20680AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20680AM\"></sup>left me.",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup>Then I <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20681AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20681AN\"></sup>told the exiles all the things that the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> had shown me."
		},
		"12": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">12 </span>Then the word of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> came to me, saying,",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>“Son of man, you live in the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20683A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20683A\"></sup>midst of the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20683B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20683B\"></sup>rebellious house, who <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20683C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20683C\"></sup>have eyes to see but do not see, ears to hear but do not hear; for they are a rebellious house.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>Therefore, son of man, prepare for yourself baggage for exile and go into exile by day in their sight; even go into exile from your place to another place in their sight. <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20684D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20684D\"></sup>Perhaps they will understand though they are a rebellious house.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>Bring your baggage out by day in their sight, as baggage for exile. Then you will go out <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20685E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20685E\"></sup>at evening in their sight, as those going into exile.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>Dig a hole through the wall in their sight and go out through it.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>Load <i>the baggage</i> on <i>your</i> shoulder in their sight <i>and</i> carry <i>it</i> out in the dark. You shall <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20687F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20687F\"></sup>cover your face so that you cannot see the land, for I have set you as a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20687G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20687G\"></sup>sign to the house of Israel.”",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>I <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20688H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20688H\"></sup>did so, as I had been commanded. By day I <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20688I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20688I\"></sup>brought out my baggage like the baggage of an exile. Then in the evening I dug through the wall with my hands; I went out in the dark <i>and</i> carried <i>the baggage</i> on <i>my</i> shoulder in their sight.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>In the morning the word of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> came to me, saying,",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>“Son of man, has not the house of Israel, the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20690J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20690J\"></sup>rebellious house, said to you, ‘<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20690K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20690K\"></sup>What are you doing?’",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>Say to them, ‘Thus says the Lord <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">God</span>, “This <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20691L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20691L\"></sup>burden <i>concerns</i> the prince in Jerusalem as well as all the house of Israel who are in it.”’",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>Say, ‘I am a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20692M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20692M\"></sup>sign to you. As I have done, so it will be done to them; they will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20692N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20692N\"></sup>go into exile, into captivity.’",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>The <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20693O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20693O\"></sup>prince who is among them will load <i>his baggage</i> on <i>his</i> shoulder in the dark and go out. They will dig a hole through the wall to bring <i>it</i> out. He will cover his face so that he can not see the land with <i>his</i> eyes.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>I will also spread My <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20694P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20694P\"></sup>net over him, and he will be caught in My snare. And I will bring him to Babylon in the land of the Chaldeans; yet he will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20694Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20694Q\"></sup>not see it, though he will die there.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>I will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20695R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20695R\"></sup>scatter to every wind all who are around him, his helpers and all his troops; and I will draw out a sword after them.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>So they will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20696S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20696S\"></sup>know that I am the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> when I scatter them among the nations and spread them among the countries.",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>But I will spare a few of them from the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20697T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20697T\"></sup>sword, the famine and the pestilence that they may tell all their abominations among the nations where they go, and may <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20697U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20697U\"></sup>know that I am the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.”",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>Moreover, the word of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> came to me saying,",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>“Son of man, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20699V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20699V\"></sup>eat your bread with trembling and drink your water with quivering and anxiety.",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>Then say to the people of the land, ‘Thus says the Lord <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">God</span> concerning the inhabitants of Jerusalem in the land of Israel, “They will eat their bread with anxiety and drink their water with horror, because their land will be <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20700W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20700W\"></sup>stripped of its fullness on account of the violence of all who live in it.",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>The inhabited <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20701X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20701X\"></sup>cities will be laid waste and the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20701Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20701Y\"></sup>land will be a desolation. So you will know that I am the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.”’”",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>Then the word of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> came to me, saying,",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>“Son of man, what is this <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20703Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20703Z\"></sup>proverb you <i>people</i> have concerning the land of Israel, saying, ‘The <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20703AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20703AA\"></sup>days are long and every <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20703AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20703AB\"></sup>vision fails’?",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>Therefore say to them, ‘Thus says the Lord <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">God</span>, “I will make this proverb cease so that they will no longer use it as a proverb in Israel.” But tell them, “<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20704AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20704AC\"></sup>The days draw near as well as the fulfillment of every vision.",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>For there will no longer be any <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20705AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20705AD\"></sup>false vision or flattering divination within the house of Israel.",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup>For I the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> will speak, and whatever <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20706AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20706AE\"></sup>word I speak will be performed. It will no longer be delayed, for in <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20706AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20706AF\"></sup>your days, O <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20706AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20706AG\"></sup>rebellious house, I will speak the word and perform it,” declares the Lord <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">God</span>.’”",
			"26": "<sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup>Furthermore, the word of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> came to me, saying,",
			"27": "<sup class=\"versenum\">27 </sup>“Son of man, behold, the house of Israel is saying, ‘The vision that he sees is for <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20708AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20708AH\"></sup>many years <i>from now</i>, and he prophesies of times far off.’",
			"28": "<sup class=\"versenum\">28 </sup>Therefore say to them, ‘Thus says the Lord <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">God</span>, “None of My words will be delayed any longer. Whatever word I speak will be performed,”’” declares the Lord <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">God</span>."
		},
		"13": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">13 </span>Then the word of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> came to me saying,",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>“Son of man, prophesy against the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20711A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20711A\"></sup>prophets of Israel who prophesy, and say to those who prophesy from their own inspiration, ‘<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20711B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20711B\"></sup>Listen to the word of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>!",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>Thus says the Lord <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">God</span>, “Woe to the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20712C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20712C\"></sup>foolish prophets who are following their own spirit and have <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20712D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20712D\"></sup>seen nothing.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>O Israel, your prophets have been like foxes among ruins.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>You have not <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20714E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20714E\"></sup>gone up into the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20714F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20714F\"></sup>breaches, nor did you build the wall around the house of Israel to stand in the battle on the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20714G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20714G\"></sup>day of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>They see <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20715H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20715H\"></sup>falsehood and lying divination who are saying, ‘The <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> declares,’ when the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> has not sent them; <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20715I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20715I\"></sup>yet they hope for the fulfillment of <i>their</i> word.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20716J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20716J\"></sup>Did you not see a false vision and speak a lying divination when you said, ‘The <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> declares,’ but it is not I who have spoken?”’”",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>Therefore, thus says the Lord <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">God</span>, “Because you have spoken falsehood and seen a lie, therefore behold, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20717K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20717K\"></sup>I am against you,” declares the Lord <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">God</span>.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>“So My hand will be against the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20718L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20718L\"></sup>prophets who see false visions and utter lying divinations. They will have no place in the council of My people, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20718M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20718M\"></sup>nor will they be written down in the register of the house of Israel, nor will they enter the land of Israel, that you may know that I am the Lord <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">God</span>.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>It is definitely because they have <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20719N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20719N\"></sup>misled My people by saying, ‘<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20719O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20719O\"></sup>Peace!’ when there is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20719P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20719P\"></sup>no peace. And when anyone builds a wall, behold, they plaster it over with whitewash;",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup><i>so</i> tell those who plaster <i>it</i> over with whitewash, that it will fall. A <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20720Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20720Q\"></sup>flooding rain will come, and you, O hailstones, will fall; and a violent wind will break out.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>Behold, when the wall has fallen, will you not be asked, ‘Where is the plaster with which you plastered <i>it</i>?’”",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>Therefore, thus says the Lord <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">God</span>, “I will make a violent wind break out in My wrath. There will also be in My anger a flooding rain and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20722R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20722R\"></sup>hailstones to consume <i>it</i> in wrath.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>So I will tear down the wall which you plastered over with whitewash and bring it down to the ground, so that its <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20723S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20723S\"></sup>foundation is laid bare; and when it falls, you will be <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20723T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20723T\"></sup>consumed in its midst. And you will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20723U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20723U\"></sup>know that I am the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>Thus I will spend My wrath on the wall and on those who have plastered it over with whitewash; and I will say to you, ‘The wall is gone and its plasterers are gone,",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup><i>along with</i> the prophets of Israel who prophesy to Jerusalem, and who <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20725V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20725V\"></sup>see visions of peace for her when there is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20725W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20725W\"></sup>no peace,’ declares the Lord <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">God</span>.",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>“Now you, son of man, set your face against the daughters of your people who are <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20726X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20726X\"></sup>prophesying <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20726Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20726Y\"></sup>from their own inspiration. Prophesy against them",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>and say, ‘Thus says the Lord <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">God</span>, “Woe to the women who sew <i>magic</i> bands on all wrists and make veils for the heads of <i>persons</i> of every stature to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20727Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20727Z\"></sup>hunt down lives! Will you hunt down the lives of My people, but preserve the lives <i>of others</i> for yourselves?",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20728AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20728AA\"></sup>For handfuls of barley and fragments of bread, you have profaned Me to My people to put to death some who should not die and to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20728AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20728AB\"></sup>keep others alive who should not live, by your lying to My people who listen to lies.”’”",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>Therefore, thus says the Lord <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">God</span>, “Behold, I am against your <i>magic</i> bands by which you hunt lives there as birds and I will tear them from your arms; and I will let them go, even those lives whom you hunt as birds.",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>I will also tear off your veils and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20730AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20730AC\"></sup>deliver My people from your hands, and they will no longer be in your hands to be hunted; and you will know that I am the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>Because you <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20731AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20731AD\"></sup>disheartened the righteous with falsehood when I did not cause him grief, but have <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20731AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20731AE\"></sup>encouraged the wicked not to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20731AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20731AF\"></sup>turn from his wicked way <i>and</i> preserve his life,",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>therefore, you women will no longer see <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20732AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20732AG\"></sup>false visions or practice divination, and I will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20732AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20732AH\"></sup>deliver My people out of your hand. Thus you will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20732AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20732AI\"></sup>know that I am the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.”"
		},
		"14": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">14 </span>Then some <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20733A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20733A\"></sup>elders of Israel came to me and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20733B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20733B\"></sup>sat down before me.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>And the word of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> came to me, saying,",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>“Son of man, these men have <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20735C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20735C\"></sup>set up their idols in their hearts and have <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20735D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20735D\"></sup>put right before their faces the stumbling block of their iniquity. Should I be <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20735E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20735E\"></sup>consulted by them at all?",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>Therefore speak to them and tell them, ‘Thus says the Lord <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">God</span>, “Any man of the house of Israel who sets up his idols in his heart, puts right before his face the stumbling block of his iniquity, and <i>then</i> comes to the prophet, I the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> will be brought to give him an answer in the matter in view of the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20736F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20736F\"></sup>multitude of his idols,",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>in order to lay hold of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20737G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20737G\"></sup>the hearts of the house of Israel who are <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20737H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20737H\"></sup>estranged from Me through all their idols.”’",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>“Therefore say to the house of Israel, ‘Thus says the Lord <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">God</span>, “<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20738I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20738I\"></sup>Repent and turn away from your idols and turn your faces away from all your <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20738J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20738J\"></sup>abominations.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>For anyone of the house of Israel or of the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20739K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20739K\"></sup>immigrants who stay in Israel who separates himself from Me, sets up his idols in his heart, puts right before his face the stumbling block of his iniquity, and <i>then</i> comes to the prophet to inquire of Me for himself, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20739L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20739L\"></sup>I the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> will be brought to answer him in My own person.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>I will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20740M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20740M\"></sup>set My face against that man and make him a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20740N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20740N\"></sup>sign and a proverb, and I will cut him off from among My people. So you will know that I am the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>“But if the prophet is prevailed upon to speak a word, it is I, the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, who have prevailed upon that prophet, and I will stretch out My hand against him and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20741O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20741O\"></sup>destroy him from among My people Israel.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>They will bear <i>the punishment of</i> their iniquity; as the iniquity of the inquirer is, so the iniquity of the prophet will be,",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>in order that the house of Israel may no longer <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20743P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20743P\"></sup>stray from Me and no longer <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20743Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20743Q\"></sup>defile themselves with all their transgressions. Thus they will be <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20743R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20743R\"></sup>My people, and I shall be their God,”’ declares the Lord <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">God</span>.”",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>Then the word of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> came to me saying,",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>“Son of man, if a country sins against Me by <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20745S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20745S\"></sup>committing unfaithfulness, and I stretch out My hand against it, destroy its <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20745T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20745T\"></sup>supply of bread, send famine against it and cut off from it both man and beast,",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>even <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20746U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20746U\"></sup><i>though</i> these three men, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20746V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20746V\"></sup>Noah, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20746W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20746W\"></sup>Daniel and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20746X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20746X\"></sup>Job were in its midst, by their <i>own</i> righteousness they could <i>only</i> deliver <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20746Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20746Y\"></sup>themselves,” declares the Lord <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">God</span>.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>“If I were to cause <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20747Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20747Z\"></sup>wild beasts to pass through the land and they depopulated it, and it became desolate so that no one would pass through it because of the beasts,",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup><i>though</i> these three men were in its midst, as I live,” declares the Lord <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">God</span>, “they could not deliver either <i>their</i> sons or <i>their</i> daughters. <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20748AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20748AA\"></sup>They alone would be delivered, but the country would be desolate.",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>Or <i>if</i> I should <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20749AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20749AB\"></sup>bring a sword on that country and say, ‘Let the sword pass through the country and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20749AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20749AC\"></sup>cut off man and beast from it,’",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>even <i>though</i> these three men were in its midst, as I live,” declares the Lord <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">God</span>, “they could not deliver either <i>their</i> sons or <i>their</i> daughters, but they alone would be delivered.",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>Or <i>if</i> I should send a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20751AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20751AD\"></sup>plague against that country and pour out My wrath in blood on it to cut off man and beast from it,",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>even <i>though</i> Noah, Daniel and Job were in its midst, as I live,” declares the Lord <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">God</span>, “they could not deliver either <i>their</i> son or <i>their</i> daughter. They would deliver only themselves by their righteousness.”",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>For thus says the Lord <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">God</span>, “How much more when <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20753AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20753AE\"></sup>I send My four severe judgments against Jerusalem: sword, famine, wild beasts and plague to cut off man and beast from it!",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>Yet, behold, survivors will be left in it who will be brought out, <i>both</i> sons and daughters. Behold, they are going to come forth to you and you will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20754AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20754AF\"></sup>see their conduct and actions; then you will be <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20754AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20754AG\"></sup>comforted for the calamity which I have brought against Jerusalem for everything which I have brought upon it.",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>Then they will comfort you when you see their conduct and actions, for you will know that I have not done <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20755AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20755AH\"></sup>in vain whatever I did to it,” declares the Lord <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">God</span>."
		},
		"15": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">15 </span>Then the word of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> came to me, saying,",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>“Son of man, how is the wood of the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20757A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20757A\"></sup>vine <i>better</i> than any wood of a branch which is among the trees of the forest?",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>Can wood be taken from it to make anything, or can <i>men</i> take a peg from it on which to hang any vessel?",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>If it has been put into the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20759B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20759B\"></sup>fire for fuel, <i>and</i> the fire has consumed both of its ends and its middle part has been charred, is it <i>then</i> useful for anything?",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>Behold, while it is intact, it is not made into anything. How much less, when the fire has consumed it and it is charred, can it still be made into anything!",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>Therefore, thus says the Lord <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">God</span>, ‘As the wood of the vine among the trees of the forest, which I have given to the fire for fuel, so have I given up the inhabitants of Jerusalem;",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>and I <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20762C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20762C\"></sup>set My face against them. <i>Though</i> they have <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20762D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20762D\"></sup>come out of the fire, yet the fire will consume them. Then you will know that I am the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, when I set My face against them.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>Thus I will make the land desolate, because they have <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20763E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20763E\"></sup>acted unfaithfully,’” declares the Lord <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">God</span>."
		},
		"16": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">16 </span>Then the word of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> came to me, saying,",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>“Son of man, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20765A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20765A\"></sup>make known to Jerusalem her abominations",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>and say, ‘Thus says the Lord <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">God</span> to Jerusalem, “Your origin and your birth are from the land of the Canaanite, your father was an Amorite and your mother a Hittite.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>As for your birth, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20767B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20767B\"></sup>on the day you were born your navel cord was not cut, nor were you washed with water for cleansing; you were not rubbed with salt or even wrapped in cloths.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>No eye looked with pity on you to do any of these things for you, to have compassion on you. Rather you were thrown out into the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20768C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20768C\"></sup>open field, for you were abhorred on the day you were born.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>“When I passed by you and saw you squirming in your blood, I said to you <i>while you were</i> in your blood, ‘Live!’ Yes, I said to you <i>while you were</i> in your blood, ‘Live!’",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>I <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20770D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20770D\"></sup>made you numerous like plants of the field. Then you grew up, became tall and reached the age for fine ornaments; <i>your</i> breasts were formed and your hair had grown. Yet you were naked and bare.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>“Then I passed by you and saw you, and behold, you were at the time for love; so I <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20771E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20771E\"></sup>spread My skirt over you and covered your nakedness. I also <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20771F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20771F\"></sup>swore to you and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20771G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20771G\"></sup>entered into a covenant with you so that you <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20771H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20771H\"></sup>became Mine,” declares the Lord <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">God</span>.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>“Then I bathed you with water, washed off your blood from you and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20772I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20772I\"></sup>anointed you with oil.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>I also clothed you with <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20773J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20773J\"></sup>embroidered cloth and put sandals of porpoise skin on your feet; and I wrapped you with fine linen and covered you with silk.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>I adorned you with ornaments, put <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20774K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20774K\"></sup>bracelets on your hands and a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20774L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20774L\"></sup>necklace around your neck.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>I also put a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20775M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20775M\"></sup>ring in your nostril, earrings in your ears and a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20775N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20775N\"></sup>beautiful crown on your head.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>Thus you were adorned with <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20776O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20776O\"></sup>gold and silver, and your dress was of fine linen, silk and embroidered cloth. You ate fine flour, honey and oil; so you were exceedingly beautiful and advanced to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20776P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20776P\"></sup>royalty.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>Then your <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20777Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20777Q\"></sup>fame went forth among the nations on account of your beauty, for it was <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20777R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20777R\"></sup>perfect because of My splendor which I bestowed on you,” declares the Lord <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">God</span>.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>“But you <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20778S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20778S\"></sup>trusted in your beauty and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20778T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20778T\"></sup>played the harlot because of your fame, and you poured out your harlotries on every passer-by who might be <i>willing</i>.",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>You took some of your clothes, made for yourself high places of various colors and played the harlot on them, which should never come about nor happen.",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>You also took your beautiful <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20780U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20780U\"></sup>jewels <i>made</i> of My gold and of My silver, which I had given you, and made for yourself male images that you might play the harlot with them.",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>Then you took your embroidered cloth and covered them, and offered My oil and My incense before them.",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>Also <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20782V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20782V\"></sup>My bread which I gave you, fine flour, oil and honey with which I fed you, you would offer before them for a soothing aroma; so it happened,” declares the Lord <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">God</span>.",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>“Moreover, you took your sons and daughters whom you had borne to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20783W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20783W\"></sup>Me and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20783X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20783X\"></sup>sacrificed them to idols to be devoured. Were your harlotries so small a matter?",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>You slaughtered <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20784Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20784Y\"></sup>My children and offered them up to idols by <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20784Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20784Z\"></sup>causing them to pass through <i>the fire</i>.",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>Besides all your abominations and harlotries you did not remember the days of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20785AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20785AA\"></sup>your youth, when you were naked and bare and squirming in your blood.",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>“Then it came about after all your wickedness (‘Woe, woe to you!’ declares the Lord <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">God</span>),",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>that you built yourself a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20787AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20787AB\"></sup>shrine and made yourself a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20787AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20787AC\"></sup>high place in every square.",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup>You built yourself a high place at the top of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20788AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20788AD\"></sup>every street and made your beauty abominable, and you spread your legs to every passer-by to multiply your harlotry.",
			"26": "<sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup>You also played the harlot with the Egyptians, your lustful neighbors, and multiplied your harlotry to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20789AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20789AE\"></sup>make Me angry.",
			"27": "<sup class=\"versenum\">27 </sup>Behold now, I have stretched out My hand against you and diminished your rations. And I delivered you up to the desire of those who hate you, the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20790AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20790AF\"></sup>daughters of the Philistines, who are ashamed of your lewd conduct.",
			"28": "<sup class=\"versenum\">28 </sup>Moreover, you played the harlot with the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20791AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20791AG\"></sup>Assyrians because you were not satisfied; you played the harlot with them and still were not satisfied.",
			"29": "<sup class=\"versenum\">29 </sup>You also multiplied your harlotry with the land of merchants, Chaldea, yet even with this you were not satisfied.”’”",
			"30": "<sup class=\"versenum\">30 </sup>“How <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20793AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20793AH\"></sup>languishing is your heart,” declares the Lord <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">God</span>, “while you do all these things, the actions of a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20793AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20793AI\"></sup>bold-faced harlot.",
			"31": "<sup class=\"versenum\">31 </sup>When you built your shrine at the beginning of every street and made your high place in every square, in <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20794AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20794AJ\"></sup>disdaining money, you were not like a harlot.",
			"32": "<sup class=\"versenum\">32 </sup>You adulteress wife, who takes strangers instead of her husband!",
			"33": "<sup class=\"versenum\">33 </sup>Men give gifts to all harlots, but you <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20796AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20796AK\"></sup>give your gifts to all your lovers to bribe them to come to you from every direction for your harlotries.",
			"34": "<sup class=\"versenum\">34 </sup>Thus you are different from those women in your harlotries, in that no one plays the harlot as you do, because you give money and no money is given you; thus you are different.”",
			"35": "<sup class=\"versenum\">35 </sup>Therefore, O harlot, hear the word of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.",
			"36": "<sup class=\"versenum\">36 </sup>Thus says the Lord <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">God</span>, “Because your lewdness was poured out and your nakedness uncovered through your harlotries with your lovers and with all your detestable <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20799AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20799AL\"></sup>idols, and because of the blood of your sons which you gave to idols,",
			"37": "<sup class=\"versenum\">37 </sup>therefore, behold, I will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20800AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20800AM\"></sup>gather all your lovers with whom you took pleasure, even all those whom you loved <i>and</i> all those whom you <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20800AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20800AN\"></sup>hated. So I will gather them against you from every direction and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20800AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20800AO\"></sup>expose your nakedness to them that they may see all your nakedness.",
			"38": "<sup class=\"versenum\">38 </sup>Thus I will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20801AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20801AP\"></sup>judge you like women who commit adultery or shed blood are judged; and I will bring on you the blood of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20801AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20801AQ\"></sup>wrath and jealousy.",
			"39": "<sup class=\"versenum\">39 </sup>I will also give you into the hands of your lovers, and they will tear down your shrines, demolish your high places, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20802AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20802AR\"></sup>strip you of your clothing, take away your jewels, and will leave you naked and bare.",
			"40": "<sup class=\"versenum\">40 </sup>They will incite a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20803AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20803AS\"></sup>crowd against you and they will stone you and cut you to pieces with their swords.",
			"41": "<sup class=\"versenum\">41 </sup>They will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20804AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20804AT\"></sup>burn your houses with fire and execute judgments on you in the sight of many women. Then I will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20804AU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AU&quot;&gt;AU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20804AU\"></sup>stop you from playing the harlot, and you will also no longer pay your lovers.",
			"42": "<sup class=\"versenum\">42 </sup>So I <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20805AV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AV&quot;&gt;AV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20805AV\"></sup>will calm My fury against you and My jealousy will depart from you, and I will be pacified and angry <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20805AW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AW&quot;&gt;AW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20805AW\"></sup>no more.",
			"43": "<sup class=\"versenum\">43 </sup>Because you have <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20806AX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AX&quot;&gt;AX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20806AX\"></sup>not remembered the days of your youth but have <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20806AY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AY&quot;&gt;AY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20806AY\"></sup>enraged Me by all these things, behold, I in turn will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20806AZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AZ&quot;&gt;AZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20806AZ\"></sup>bring your conduct down on your own head,” declares the Lord <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">God</span>, “so that you will not commit this lewdness on top of all your <i>other</i> abominations.",
			"44": "<sup class=\"versenum\">44 </sup>“Behold, everyone who quotes <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20807BA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BA&quot;&gt;BA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20807BA\"></sup>proverbs will quote <i>this</i> proverb concerning you, saying, ‘Like mother, like daughter.’",
			"45": "<sup class=\"versenum\">45 </sup>You are the daughter of your mother, who loathed her husband and children. You are also the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20808BB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BB&quot;&gt;BB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20808BB\"></sup>sister of your sisters, who <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20808BC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BC&quot;&gt;BC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20808BC\"></sup>loathed their husbands and children. Your mother was a Hittite and your father an Amorite.",
			"46": "<sup class=\"versenum\">46 </sup>Now your <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20809BD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BD&quot;&gt;BD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20809BD\"></sup>older sister is Samaria, who lives north of you with her daughters; and your younger sister, who lives south of you, is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20809BE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BE&quot;&gt;BE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20809BE\"></sup>Sodom with her daughters.",
			"47": "<sup class=\"versenum\">47 </sup>Yet you have not merely walked in their ways or done according to their abominations; but, as if that were <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20810BF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BF&quot;&gt;BF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20810BF\"></sup>too little, you acted <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20810BG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BG&quot;&gt;BG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20810BG\"></sup>more corruptly in all your conduct than they.",
			"48": "<sup class=\"versenum\">48 </sup>As I live,” declares the Lord <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">God</span>, “Sodom, your sister and her daughters have <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20811BH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BH&quot;&gt;BH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20811BH\"></sup>not done as you and your daughters have done.",
			"49": "<sup class=\"versenum\">49 </sup>Behold, this was the guilt of your sister Sodom: she and her daughters had <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20812BI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BI&quot;&gt;BI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20812BI\"></sup>arrogance, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20812BJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BJ&quot;&gt;BJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20812BJ\"></sup>abundant food and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20812BK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BK&quot;&gt;BK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20812BK\"></sup>careless ease, but she did not help the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20812BL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BL&quot;&gt;BL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20812BL\"></sup>poor and needy.",
			"50": "<sup class=\"versenum\">50 </sup>Thus they were haughty and committed <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20813BM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BM&quot;&gt;BM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20813BM\"></sup>abominations before Me. Therefore I <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20813BN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BN&quot;&gt;BN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20813BN\"></sup>removed them when I saw <i>it</i>.",
			"51": "<sup class=\"versenum\">51 </sup>Furthermore, Samaria did not commit half of your sins, for you have multiplied your abominations more than they. Thus you have made your sisters appear <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20814BO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BO&quot;&gt;BO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20814BO\"></sup>righteous by all your abominations which you have committed.",
			"52": "<sup class=\"versenum\">52 </sup>Also bear your disgrace in that you have made judgment favorable for your sisters. Because of your sins in which you acted <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20815BP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BP&quot;&gt;BP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20815BP\"></sup>more abominably than they, they are more in the right than you. Yes, be also ashamed and bear your disgrace, in that you made your sisters appear righteous.",
			"53": "<sup class=\"versenum\">53 </sup>“Nevertheless, I will restore their captivity, the captivity of Sodom and her daughters, the captivity of Samaria and her daughters, and along with them your own captivity,",
			"54": "<sup class=\"versenum\">54 </sup>in order that you may bear your humiliation and feel <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20817BQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BQ&quot;&gt;BQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20817BQ\"></sup>ashamed for all that you have done when you become <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20817BR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BR&quot;&gt;BR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20817BR\"></sup>a consolation to them.",
			"55": "<sup class=\"versenum\">55 </sup>Your sisters, Sodom with her daughters and Samaria with her daughters, will return to their former state, and you with your daughters will <i>also</i> return to your former state.",
			"56": "<sup class=\"versenum\">56 </sup>As <i>the name of</i> your sister Sodom was not heard from your lips in your day of pride,",
			"57": "<sup class=\"versenum\">57 </sup>before your <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20820BS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BS&quot;&gt;BS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20820BS\"></sup>wickedness was uncovered, so now you have become the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20820BT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BT&quot;&gt;BT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20820BT\"></sup>reproach of the daughters of Edom and of all who are around her, of the daughters of the Philistines—those surrounding <i>you</i> who despise you.",
			"58": "<sup class=\"versenum\">58 </sup>You have <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20821BU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BU&quot;&gt;BU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20821BU\"></sup>borne <i>the penalty of</i> your lewdness and abominations,” the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> declares.",
			"59": "<sup class=\"versenum\">59 </sup>For thus says the Lord <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">God</span>, “I will also do with you as you have done, you who have <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20822BV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BV&quot;&gt;BV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20822BV\"></sup>despised the oath by breaking the covenant.",
			"60": "<sup class=\"versenum\">60 </sup>“Nevertheless, I will remember My covenant with you in the days of your youth, and I will establish an <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20823BW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BW&quot;&gt;BW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20823BW\"></sup>everlasting covenant with you.",
			"61": "<sup class=\"versenum\">61 </sup>Then you will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20824BX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BX&quot;&gt;BX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20824BX\"></sup>remember your ways and be ashamed when you receive your sisters, <i>both</i> your older and your younger; and I will give them to you as daughters, but not because of your covenant.",
			"62": "<sup class=\"versenum\">62 </sup>Thus I will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20825BY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BY&quot;&gt;BY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20825BY\"></sup>establish My covenant with you, and you shall <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20825BZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BZ&quot;&gt;BZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20825BZ\"></sup>know that I am the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>,",
			"63": "<sup class=\"versenum\">63 </sup>so that you may <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20826CA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CA&quot;&gt;CA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20826CA\"></sup>remember and be ashamed and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20826CB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CB&quot;&gt;CB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20826CB\"></sup>never open your mouth anymore because of your humiliation, when I have <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20826CC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CC&quot;&gt;CC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20826CC\"></sup>forgiven you for all that you have done,” the Lord <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">God</span> declares."
		},
		"17": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">17 </span>Now the word of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> came to me saying,",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>“Son of man, propound a riddle and speak a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20828A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20828A\"></sup>parable to the house of Israel,",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>saying, ‘Thus says the Lord <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">God</span>, “A great <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20829B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20829B\"></sup>eagle with <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20829C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20829C\"></sup>great wings, long pinions and a full plumage of many colors came to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20829D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20829D\"></sup>Lebanon and took away the top of the cedar.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>He plucked off the topmost of its young twigs and brought it to a land of merchants; he set it in a city of traders.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>He also took some of the seed of the land and planted it in <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20831E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20831E\"></sup>fertile soil. He placed <i>it</i> beside abundant waters; he set it <i>like</i> a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20831F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20831F\"></sup>willow.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>Then it sprouted and became a low, spreading vine with its branches turned toward him, but its roots remained under it. So it became a vine and yielded shoots and sent out branches.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>“But there was another great eagle with great wings and much plumage; and behold, this vine bent its roots toward him and sent out its branches toward him from the beds where it was <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20833G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20833G\"></sup>planted, that he might water it.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>It was planted in good soil beside abundant waters, that it might yield branches and bear fruit <i>and</i> become a splendid vine.”’",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>Say, ‘Thus says the Lord <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">God</span>, “Will it thrive? Will he not pull up its roots and cut off its fruit, so that it withers—so that all its sprouting leaves wither? And neither by great strength nor by many people can it be raised from its roots <i>again</i>.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>Behold, though it is planted, will it thrive? Will it not <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20836H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20836H\"></sup>completely wither as soon as the east wind strikes it—wither on the beds where it grew?”’”",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>Moreover, the word of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> came to me, saying,",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>“Say now to the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20838I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20838I\"></sup>rebellious house, ‘Do you not <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20838J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20838J\"></sup>know what these things <i>mean</i>?’ Say, ‘Behold, the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20838K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20838K\"></sup>king of Babylon came to Jerusalem, took its king and princes and brought them to him in Babylon.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>He took one of the royal <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20839L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20839L\"></sup>family and made a covenant with him, putting him under <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20839M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20839M\"></sup>oath. He also took away the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20839N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20839N\"></sup>mighty of the land,",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>that the kingdom might <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20840O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20840O\"></sup>be in subjection, not exalting itself, <i>but</i> keeping his covenant that it might continue.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>But he <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20841P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20841P\"></sup>rebelled against him by sending his envoys to Egypt that they might give him horses and many troops. Will he succeed? Will he who does such things <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20841Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20841Q\"></sup>escape? Can he indeed break the covenant and escape?",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>As I live,’ declares the Lord <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">God</span>, ‘Surely in the country of the king who put him on the throne, whose oath he <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20842R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20842R\"></sup>despised and whose covenant he broke, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20842S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20842S\"></sup>in Babylon he shall die.",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20843T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20843T\"></sup>Pharaoh with <i>his</i> mighty army and great company will not help him in the war, when they cast up ramps and build siege walls to cut off many lives.",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>Now he despised the oath by breaking the covenant, and behold, he <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20844U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20844U\"></sup>pledged his allegiance, yet did all these things; he shall not escape.’”",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>Therefore, thus says the Lord <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">God</span>, “As I live, surely My oath which he despised and My covenant which he broke, I will inflict on his head.",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>I will spread My <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20846V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20846V\"></sup>net over him, and he will be <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20846W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20846W\"></sup>caught in My snare. Then I will bring him to Babylon and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20846X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20846X\"></sup>enter into judgment with him there <i>regarding</i> the unfaithful act which he has committed against Me.",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>All the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20847Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20847Y\"></sup>choice men in all his troops will fall by the sword, and the survivors will be scattered to every wind; and you will know that I, the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, have spoken.”",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>Thus says the Lord <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">God</span>, “I will also take <i>a sprig</i> from the lofty top of the cedar and set <i>it</i> out; I will pluck from the topmost of its young twigs a tender one and I will plant <i>it</i> on a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20848Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20848Z\"></sup>high and lofty mountain.",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>On the high mountain of Israel I will plant it, that it may bring forth boughs and bear fruit and become a stately <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20849AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20849AA\"></sup>cedar. And birds of every kind will nest under it; they will nest in the shade of its branches.",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>All the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20850AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20850AB\"></sup>trees of the field will know that I am the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>; I bring down the high tree, exalt the low tree, dry up the green tree and make the dry tree <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20850AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20850AC\"></sup>flourish. I am the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>; I have spoken, and I will perform <i>it</i>.”"
		},
		"18": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">18 </span>Then the word of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> came to me, saying,",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>“<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20852A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20852A\"></sup>What do you mean by using this proverb concerning the land of Israel, saying,‘<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20852B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20852B\"></sup>The fathers eat the sour grapes,But the children’s teeth are set on edge’?",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>As I live,” declares the Lord <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">God</span>, “you are surely not going to use this proverb in Israel anymore.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>Behold, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20854C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20854C\"></sup>all souls are Mine; the soul of the father as well as the soul of the son is Mine. The soul who <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20854D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20854D\"></sup>sins will die.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>“But if a man is righteous and practices justice and righteousness,",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>and does not <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20856E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20856E\"></sup>eat at the mountain <i>shrines</i> or <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20856F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20856F\"></sup>lift up his eyes to the idols of the house of Israel, or <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20856G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20856G\"></sup>defile his neighbor’s wife or approach a woman during her menstrual period—",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>if a man does not oppress anyone, but <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20857H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20857H\"></sup>restores to the debtor his pledge, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20857I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20857I\"></sup>does not commit robbery, <i>but</i> <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20857J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20857J\"></sup>gives his bread to the hungry and covers the naked with clothing,",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>if he does not lend <i>money</i> on <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20858K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20858K\"></sup>interest or take <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20858L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20858L\"></sup>increase, <i>if</i> he keeps his hand from iniquity <i>and</i> <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20858M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20858M\"></sup>executes true justice between man and man,",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup><i>if</i> he walks in <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20859N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20859N\"></sup>My statutes and My ordinances so as to deal faithfully—<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20859O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20859O\"></sup>he is righteous <i>and</i> will surely <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20859P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20859P\"></sup>live,” declares the Lord <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">God</span>.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>“Then he may have a violent son who sheds blood and who does any of these things to a brother",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>(though he himself did not do any of these things), that is, he even eats at the mountain <i>shrines</i>, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20861Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20861Q\"></sup>defiles his neighbor’s wife,",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>oppresses the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20862R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20862R\"></sup>poor and needy, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20862S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20862S\"></sup>commits robbery, does not restore a pledge, but lifts up his eyes to the idols <i>and</i> <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20862T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20862T\"></sup>commits abomination,",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>he <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20863U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20863U\"></sup>lends <i>money</i> on interest and takes increase; will he live? He will not live! He has committed all these abominations, he will surely be put to death; his <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20863V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20863V\"></sup>blood will be on his own head.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>“Now behold, he has a son who has observed all his father’s sins which he committed, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20864W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20864W\"></sup>observing does not do likewise.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>He does not eat at the mountain <i>shrines</i> or lift up his eyes to the idols of the house of Israel, or defile his neighbor’s wife,",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>or oppress anyone, or retain a pledge, or commit robbery, <i>but</i> he <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20866X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20866X\"></sup>gives his bread to the hungry and covers the naked with clothing,",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>he keeps his hand from the poor, does not take interest or increase, <i>but</i> executes My ordinances, and walks in My statutes; <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20867Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20867Y\"></sup>he will not die for his father’s iniquity, he will surely live.",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>As for his father, because he practiced extortion, robbed <i>his</i> brother and did what was not good among his people, behold, he will die for his iniquity.",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>“Yet you say, ‘<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20869Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20869Z\"></sup>Why should the son not bear the punishment for the father’s iniquity?’ When the son has practiced <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20869AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20869AA\"></sup>justice and righteousness and has observed all My statutes and done them, he shall surely live.",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>The person who <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20870AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20870AB\"></sup>sins will die. The <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20870AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20870AC\"></sup>son will not bear the punishment for the father’s iniquity, nor will the father bear the punishment for the son’s iniquity; the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20870AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20870AD\"></sup>righteousness of the righteous will be upon himself, and the wickedness of the wicked will be upon himself.",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>“But if the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20871AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20871AE\"></sup>wicked man turns from all his sins which he has committed and observes all My statutes and practices justice and righteousness, he shall surely live; he shall not die.",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20872AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20872AF\"></sup>All his transgressions which he has committed will not be remembered against him; because of his <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20872AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20872AG\"></sup>righteousness which he has practiced, he will live.",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20873AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20873AH\"></sup>Do I have any pleasure in the death of the wicked,” declares the Lord <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">God</span>, “rather than that he should <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20873AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20873AI\"></sup>turn from his ways and live?",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>“But when a righteous man <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20874AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20874AJ\"></sup>turns away from his righteousness, commits iniquity and does according to all the abominations that a wicked man does, will he live? <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20874AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20874AK\"></sup>All his righteous deeds which he has done will not be remembered for his <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20874AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20874AL\"></sup>treachery which he has committed and his sin which he has committed; for them he will die.",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup>Yet you say, ‘<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20875AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20875AM\"></sup>The way of the Lord is not right.’ Hear now, O house of Israel! Is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20875AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20875AN\"></sup>My way not right? Is it not your ways that are not right?",
			"26": "<sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup>When a righteous man turns away from his righteousness, commits iniquity and dies because of it, for his iniquity which he has committed he will die.",
			"27": "<sup class=\"versenum\">27 </sup>Again, when a wicked man turns away <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20877AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20877AO\"></sup>from his wickedness which he has committed and practices justice and righteousness, he will save his life.",
			"28": "<sup class=\"versenum\">28 </sup>Because he considered and turned away from all his transgressions which he had committed, he shall surely live; he shall not die.",
			"29": "<sup class=\"versenum\">29 </sup>But the house of Israel says, ‘The way of the Lord is not right.’ Are My ways not right, O house of Israel? Is it not your ways that are not right?",
			"30": "<sup class=\"versenum\">30 </sup>“Therefore I will judge you, O house of Israel, each according to his conduct,” declares the Lord <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">God</span>. “<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20880AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20880AP\"></sup>Repent and turn away from all your transgressions, so that iniquity may not become a stumbling block to you.",
			"31": "<sup class=\"versenum\">31 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20881AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20881AQ\"></sup>Cast away from you all your transgressions which you have committed and make yourselves a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20881AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20881AR\"></sup>new heart and a new spirit! For why will you die, O house of Israel?",
			"32": "<sup class=\"versenum\">32 </sup>For I have <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20882AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20882AS\"></sup>no pleasure in the death of anyone who dies,” declares the Lord <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">God</span>. “Therefore, repent and live.”"
		},
		"19": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">19 </span>“As for you, take up a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20883A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20883A\"></sup>lamentation for the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20883B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20883B\"></sup>princes of Israel",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>and say,‘What was your mother?A lioness among lions!She lay down among young lions,She reared her cubs.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>‘When she brought up one of her cubs,He became a lion,And he learned to tear <i>his</i> prey;He devoured men.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>‘Then nations heard about him;He was captured in their pit,And they <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20886C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20886C\"></sup>brought him with hooksTo the land of Egypt.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>‘When she saw, as she waited,<i>That</i> her hope was lost,She took another of her cubsAnd made him a young lion.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>‘And he <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20888D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20888D\"></sup>walked about among the lions;He became a young lion,He learned to tear <i>his</i> prey;He devoured men.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>‘He destroyed their fortified towersAnd laid waste their cities;And the land and its fullness were appalledBecause of the sound of his roaring.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>‘Then <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20890E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20890E\"></sup>nations set against himOn every side from <i>their</i> provinces,And they spread their net over him;He was captured in their pit.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>‘<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20891F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20891F\"></sup>They put him in a cage with hooksAnd <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20891G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20891G\"></sup>brought him to the king of Babylon;They brought him in hunting netsSo that his voice would be heard no moreOn the mountains of Israel.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>‘Your mother was <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20892H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20892H\"></sup>like a vine in your vineyard,Planted by the waters;It was fruitful and full of branchesBecause of abundant waters.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>‘And it had <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20893I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20893I\"></sup>strong branches <i>fit</i> for scepters of rulers,And its <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20893J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20893J\"></sup>height was raised above the cloudsSo that it was seen in its height with the mass of its branches.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>‘But it was <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20894K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20894K\"></sup>plucked up in fury;It was <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20894L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20894L\"></sup>cast down to the ground;And the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20894M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20894M\"></sup>east wind dried up its fruit.Its <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20894N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20894N\"></sup>strong branch was torn offSo that it withered;The fire consumed it.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>‘And now it is planted in the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20895O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20895O\"></sup>wilderness,In a dry and thirsty land.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>‘And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20896P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20896P\"></sup>fire has gone out from <i>its</i> branch;It has consumed its shoots <i>and</i> fruit,So that there is not in it a strong branch,A scepter to rule.’”This is a lamentation, and has become a lamentation."
		},
		"20": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">20 </span>Now in the seventh year, in the fifth <i>month</i>, on the tenth of the month, certain of the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20897A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20897A\"></sup>elders of Israel came to inquire of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, and sat before me.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>And the word of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> came to me saying,",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>“Son of man, speak to the elders of Israel and say to them, ‘Thus says the Lord <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">God</span>, “Do you come to inquire of Me? As I live,” declares the Lord <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">God</span>, “<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20899B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20899B\"></sup>I will not be inquired of by you.”’",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>Will you judge them, will you judge them, son of man? <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20900C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20900C\"></sup>Make them know the abominations of their fathers;",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>and say to them, ‘Thus says the Lord <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">God</span>, “On the day when I <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20901D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20901D\"></sup>chose Israel and swore to the descendants of the house of Jacob and made Myself known to them in the land of Egypt, when I swore to them, saying, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20901E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20901E\"></sup>I am the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> your God,",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>on that day I swore to them, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20902F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20902F\"></sup>to bring them out from the land of Egypt into a land that I had selected for them, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20902G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20902G\"></sup>flowing with milk and honey, which is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20902H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20902H\"></sup>the glory of all lands.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>I said to them, ‘<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20903I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20903I\"></sup>Cast away, each of you, the detestable things of his eyes, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20903J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20903J\"></sup>do not defile yourselves with the idols of Egypt; <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20903K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20903K\"></sup>I am the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> your God.’",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>But they <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20904L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20904L\"></sup>rebelled against Me and were not willing to listen to Me; they did not cast away the detestable things of their eyes, nor did they forsake the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20904M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20904M\"></sup>idols of Egypt.Then I resolved to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20904N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20904N\"></sup>pour out My wrath on them, to accomplish My anger against them in the midst of the land of Egypt.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>But I acted <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20905O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20905O\"></sup>for the sake of My name, that it should <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20905P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20905P\"></sup>not be profaned in the sight of the nations among whom they <i>lived</i>, in whose sight I made Myself known to them by bringing them out of the land of Egypt.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>So I took them out of the land of Egypt and brought them into the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20906Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20906Q\"></sup>wilderness.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>I gave them My <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20907R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20907R\"></sup>statutes and informed them of My ordinances, by <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20907S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20907S\"></sup>which, if a man observes them, he will live.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>Also I gave them My sabbaths to be a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20908T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20908T\"></sup>sign between Me and them, that they might know that I am the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> who sanctifies them.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>But the house of Israel <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20909U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20909U\"></sup>rebelled against Me in the wilderness. They did not walk in My statutes and they rejected My ordinances, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20909V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20909V\"></sup>by which, if a man observes them, he will live; and My <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20909W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20909W\"></sup>sabbaths they greatly profaned. Then I resolved to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20909X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20909X\"></sup>pour out My wrath on them in the wilderness, to annihilate them.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>But I acted for the sake of My name, that it should not be profaned in the sight of the nations, before whose sight I had brought them out.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>Also <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20911Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20911Y\"></sup>I swore to them in the wilderness that I would not bring them into the land which I had given them, flowing with milk and honey, which is the glory of all lands,",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>because they rejected My ordinances, and as for My statutes, they did not walk in them; they even profaned My sabbaths, for their <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20912Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20912Z\"></sup>heart continually went after their idols.",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>Yet My eye spared them rather than destroying them, and I did not cause their <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20913AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20913AA\"></sup>annihilation in the wilderness.",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>“I said to their <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20914AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20914AB\"></sup>children in the wilderness, ‘<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20914AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20914AC\"></sup>Do not walk in the statutes of your fathers or keep their ordinances or defile yourselves with their idols.",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20915AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20915AD\"></sup>I am the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> your God; <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20915AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20915AE\"></sup>walk in My statutes and keep My ordinances and observe them.",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20916AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20916AF\"></sup>Sanctify My sabbaths; and they shall be a sign between Me and you, that you may know that I am the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> your God.’",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>But the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20917AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20917AG\"></sup>children rebelled against Me; they did not walk in My statutes, nor were they careful to observe My ordinances, by which, <i>if</i> a man observes them, he will live; they profaned My sabbaths. So I resolved to pour out My wrath on them, to accomplish My anger against them in the wilderness.",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>But I <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20918AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20918AH\"></sup>withdrew My hand and acted <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20918AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20918AI\"></sup>for the sake of My name, that it should not be profaned in the sight of the nations in whose sight I had brought them out.",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>Also I swore to them in the wilderness that I would <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20919AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20919AJ\"></sup>scatter them among the nations and disperse them among the lands,",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>because they had not observed My ordinances, but had rejected My statutes and had profaned My sabbaths, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20920AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20920AK\"></sup>their eyes were on the idols of their fathers.",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup>I also gave them statutes that were <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20921AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20921AL\"></sup>not good and ordinances by which they could not live;",
			"26": "<sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup>and I pronounced them <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20922AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20922AM\"></sup>unclean because of their gifts, in that they <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20922AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20922AN\"></sup>caused all their firstborn to pass through <i>the fire</i> so that I might make them desolate, in order that they might <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20922AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20922AO\"></sup>know that I am the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.”’",
			"27": "<sup class=\"versenum\">27 </sup>“Therefore, son of man, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20923AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20923AP\"></sup>speak to the house of Israel and say to them, ‘Thus says the Lord <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">God</span>, “Yet in this your fathers have <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20923AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20923AQ\"></sup>blasphemed Me by <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20923AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20923AR\"></sup>acting treacherously against Me.",
			"28": "<sup class=\"versenum\">28 </sup>When I had <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20924AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20924AS\"></sup>brought them into the land which I swore to give to them, then they saw every <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20924AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20924AT\"></sup>high hill and every leafy tree, and they offered there their sacrifices and there they presented the provocation of their offering. There also they made their soothing aroma and there they poured out their drink offerings.",
			"29": "<sup class=\"versenum\">29 </sup>Then I said to them, ‘What is the high place to which you go?’ So its name is called Bamah to this day.”’",
			"30": "<sup class=\"versenum\">30 </sup>Therefore, say to the house of Israel, ‘Thus says the Lord <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">God</span>, “Will you defile yourselves after the manner of your <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20926AU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AU&quot;&gt;AU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20926AU\"></sup>fathers and play the harlot after their detestable things?",
			"31": "<sup class=\"versenum\">31 </sup>When you offer your gifts, when you <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20927AV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AV&quot;&gt;AV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20927AV\"></sup>cause your sons to pass through the fire, you are defiling yourselves with all your idols to this day. And shall I be inquired of by you, O house of Israel? As I live,” declares the Lord <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">God</span>, “I will not be inquired of by you.",
			"32": "<sup class=\"versenum\">32 </sup>What <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20928AW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AW&quot;&gt;AW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20928AW\"></sup>comes into your mind will not come about, when you say: ‘We will be like the nations, like the tribes of the lands, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20928AX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AX&quot;&gt;AX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20928AX\"></sup>serving wood and stone.’",
			"33": "<sup class=\"versenum\">33 </sup>“As I live,” declares the Lord <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">God</span>, “surely with a mighty hand and with an <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20929AY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AY&quot;&gt;AY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20929AY\"></sup>outstretched arm and with wrath poured out, I shall be <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20929AZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AZ&quot;&gt;AZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20929AZ\"></sup>king over you.",
			"34": "<sup class=\"versenum\">34 </sup>I will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20930BA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BA&quot;&gt;BA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20930BA\"></sup>bring you out from the peoples and gather you from the lands where you are scattered, with a mighty hand and with an outstretched arm and with <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20930BB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BB&quot;&gt;BB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20930BB\"></sup>wrath poured out;",
			"35": "<sup class=\"versenum\">35 </sup>and I will bring you into the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20931BC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BC&quot;&gt;BC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20931BC\"></sup>wilderness of the peoples, and there I will enter into judgment with you face to face.",
			"36": "<sup class=\"versenum\">36 </sup>As I <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20932BD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BD&quot;&gt;BD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20932BD\"></sup>entered into judgment with your fathers in the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20932BE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BE&quot;&gt;BE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20932BE\"></sup>wilderness of the land of Egypt, so I will enter into judgment with you,” declares the Lord <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">God</span>.",
			"37": "<sup class=\"versenum\">37 </sup>“I will make you <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20933BF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BF&quot;&gt;BF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20933BF\"></sup>pass under the rod, and I will bring you into the bond of the covenant;",
			"38": "<sup class=\"versenum\">38 </sup>and I will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20934BG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BG&quot;&gt;BG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20934BG\"></sup>purge from you the rebels and those who transgress against Me; I will bring them out of the land where they sojourn, but they will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20934BH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BH&quot;&gt;BH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20934BH\"></sup>not enter the land of Israel. Thus you will know that I am the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.",
			"39": "<sup class=\"versenum\">39 </sup>“As for you, O house of Israel,” thus says the Lord <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">God</span>, “<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20935BI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BI&quot;&gt;BI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20935BI\"></sup>Go, serve everyone his idols; but later you will surely listen to Me, and My holy name you will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20935BJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BJ&quot;&gt;BJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20935BJ\"></sup>profane no longer with your gifts and with your idols.",
			"40": "<sup class=\"versenum\">40 </sup>For on My holy mountain, on the high mountain of Israel,” declares the Lord <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">God</span>, “there the whole house of Israel, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20936BK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BK&quot;&gt;BK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20936BK\"></sup>all of them, will serve Me in the land; there I will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20936BL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BL&quot;&gt;BL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20936BL\"></sup>accept them and there I will seek your contributions and the choicest of your gifts, with all your holy things.",
			"41": "<sup class=\"versenum\">41 </sup>As a soothing aroma I will accept you when I <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20937BM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BM&quot;&gt;BM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20937BM\"></sup>bring you out from the peoples and gather you from the lands where you are scattered; and I will prove Myself <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20937BN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BN&quot;&gt;BN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20937BN\"></sup>holy among you in the sight of the nations.",
			"42": "<sup class=\"versenum\">42 </sup>And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20938BO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BO&quot;&gt;BO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20938BO\"></sup>you will know that I am the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20938BP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BP&quot;&gt;BP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20938BP\"></sup>when I bring you into the land of Israel, into the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20938BQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BQ&quot;&gt;BQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20938BQ\"></sup>land which I swore to give to your forefathers.",
			"43": "<sup class=\"versenum\">43 </sup>There you will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20939BR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BR&quot;&gt;BR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20939BR\"></sup>remember your ways and all your deeds with which you have defiled yourselves; and you will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20939BS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BS&quot;&gt;BS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20939BS\"></sup>loathe yourselves in your own sight for all the evil things that you have done.",
			"44": "<sup class=\"versenum\">44 </sup>Then <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20940BT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BT&quot;&gt;BT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20940BT\"></sup>you will know that I am the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> when I have dealt with you <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20940BU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BU&quot;&gt;BU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20940BU\"></sup>for My name’s sake, not according to your evil ways or according to your corrupt deeds, O house of Israel,” declares the Lord <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">God</span>.’”",
			"45": "<sup class=\"versenum\">45 </sup>Now the word of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> came to me, saying,",
			"46": "<sup class=\"versenum\">46 </sup>“Son of man, set your face toward Teman, and speak out against the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20942BV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BV&quot;&gt;BV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20942BV\"></sup>south and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20942BW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BW&quot;&gt;BW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20942BW\"></sup>prophesy against the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20942BX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BX&quot;&gt;BX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20942BX\"></sup>forest land of the Negev,",
			"47": "<sup class=\"versenum\">47 </sup>and say to the forest of the Negev, ‘Hear the word of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>: thus says the Lord <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">God</span>, “Behold, I am about to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20943BY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BY&quot;&gt;BY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20943BY\"></sup>kindle a fire in you, and it will consume every green tree in you, as well as every dry tree; the blazing flame will not be quenched and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20943BZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BZ&quot;&gt;BZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20943BZ\"></sup>the whole surface from south to north will be burned by it.",
			"48": "<sup class=\"versenum\">48 </sup>All flesh will see that I, the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, have kindled it; it shall <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20944CA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CA&quot;&gt;CA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20944CA\"></sup>not be quenched.”’”",
			"49": "<sup class=\"versenum\">49 </sup>Then I said, “Ah Lord <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">God</span>! They are saying of me, ‘Is he not <i>just</i> speaking <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20945CB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CB&quot;&gt;CB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20945CB\"></sup>parables?’”"
		},
		"21": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">21 </span>And the word of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> came to me saying,",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>“Son of man, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20947A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20947A\"></sup>set your face toward Jerusalem, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20947B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20947B\"></sup>speak against the sanctuaries and prophesy against the land of Israel;",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>and say to the land of Israel, ‘Thus says the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, “Behold, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20948C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20948C\"></sup>I am against you; and I will draw My sword out of its sheath and cut off from you the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20948D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20948D\"></sup>righteous and the wicked.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>Because I will cut off from you the righteous and the wicked, therefore My sword will go forth from its sheath against <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20949E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20949E\"></sup>all flesh from south <i>to</i> north.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>Thus all flesh will know that I, the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, have drawn My sword out of its sheath. It will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20950F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20950F\"></sup>not return <i>to its sheath</i> again.”’",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>As for you, son of man, groan with breaking heart and bitter grief, groan in their sight.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>And when they say to you, ‘Why do you groan?’ you shall say, ‘Because of the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20952G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20952G\"></sup>news that is coming; and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20952H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20952H\"></sup>every heart will melt, all hands will be feeble, every spirit will faint and all knees will be weak as water. Behold, it comes and it will happen,’ declares the Lord <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">God</span>.”",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>Again the word of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> came to me, saying,",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>“Son of man, prophesy and say, ‘Thus says the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.’ Say,‘<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20954I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20954I\"></sup>A sword, a sword sharpenedAnd also polished!",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>‘Sharpened to make a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20955J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20955J\"></sup>slaughter,Polished to flash like lightning!’Or shall we rejoice, the rod of My son <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20955K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20955K\"></sup>despising every tree?",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>It is given to be polished, that it may be handled; the sword is sharpened and polished, to give it into the hand of the slayer.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20957L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20957L\"></sup>Cry out and wail, son of man; for it is against My people, it is against all the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20957M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20957M\"></sup>officials of Israel. They are delivered over to the sword with My people, therefore strike <i>your</i> thigh.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>For <i>there is</i> a testing; and what if even the rod which despises will be no more?” declares the Lord <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">God</span>.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>“You therefore, son of man, prophesy and clap <i>your</i> hands together; and let the sword be <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20959N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20959N\"></sup>doubled the third time, the sword for the slain. It is the sword for the great one slain, which surrounds them,",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>that <i>their</i> <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20960O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20960O\"></sup>hearts may melt, and many <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20960P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20960P\"></sup>fall at all their <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20960Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20960Q\"></sup>gates. I have given the glittering sword. Ah! It is made <i>for striking</i> like lightning, it is wrapped up <i>in readiness</i> for slaughter.",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>Show yourself sharp, go to the right; set yourself; go to the left, wherever your edge is appointed.",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>I will also clap My hands together, and I will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20962R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20962R\"></sup>appease My wrath; I, the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, have spoken.”",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>The word of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> came to me saying,",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>“As for you, son of man, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20964S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20964S\"></sup>make two ways for the sword of the king of Babylon to come; both of them will go out of one land. And make a signpost; make it at the head of the way to the city.",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>You shall mark a way for the sword to come to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20965T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20965T\"></sup>Rabbah of the sons of Ammon, and to Judah into <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20965U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20965U\"></sup>fortified Jerusalem.",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>For the king of Babylon stands at the parting of the way, at the head of the two ways, to use <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20966V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20966V\"></sup>divination; he <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20966W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20966W\"></sup>shakes the arrows, he consults the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20966X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20966X\"></sup>household idols, he looks at the liver.",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>Into his right hand came the divination, ‘Jerusalem,’ to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20967Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20967Y\"></sup>set battering rams, to open the mouth for slaughter, to lift up the voice with a battle cry, to set battering rams against the gates, to cast up ramps, to build a siege wall.",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>And it will be to them like a false divination in their eyes; <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20968Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20968Z\"></sup>they have <i>sworn</i> solemn oaths. But he <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20968AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20968AA\"></sup>brings iniquity to remembrance, that they may be seized.",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>“Therefore, thus says the Lord <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">God</span>, ‘Because you have made your iniquity to be remembered, in that your transgressions are uncovered, so that in all your deeds your sins appear—because you have come to remembrance, you will be seized with the hand.",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup>And you, O slain, wicked one, the prince of Israel, whose <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20970AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20970AB\"></sup>day has come, in the time of the punishment of the end,’",
			"26": "<sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup>thus says the Lord <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">God</span>, ‘Remove the turban and take off the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20971AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20971AC\"></sup>crown; this <i>will</i> no longer <i>be</i> the same. <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20971AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20971AD\"></sup>Exalt that which is low and abase that which is high.",
			"27": "<sup class=\"versenum\">27 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20972AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20972AE\"></sup>A ruin, a ruin, a ruin, I will make it. This also will be no more until <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20972AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20972AF\"></sup>He comes whose right it is, and I will give it <i>to Him</i>.’",
			"28": "<sup class=\"versenum\">28 </sup>“And you, son of man, prophesy and say, ‘Thus says the Lord <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">God</span> concerning the sons of Ammon and concerning their <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20973AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20973AG\"></sup>reproach,’ and say: ‘A sword, a sword is drawn, polished for the slaughter, to cause it to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20973AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20973AH\"></sup>consume, that it may be like lightning—",
			"29": "<sup class=\"versenum\">29 </sup>while they see for you <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20974AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20974AI\"></sup>false visions, while they divine lies for you—to place you on the necks of the wicked who are slain, whose day has come, in the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20974AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20974AJ\"></sup>time of the punishment of the end.",
			"30": "<sup class=\"versenum\">30 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20975AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20975AK\"></sup>Return <i>it</i> to its sheath. In the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20975AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20975AL\"></sup>place where you were created, in the land of your origin, I will judge you.",
			"31": "<sup class=\"versenum\">31 </sup>I will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20976AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20976AM\"></sup>pour out My indignation on you; I will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20976AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20976AN\"></sup>blow on you with the fire of My wrath, and I will give you into the hand of brutal men, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20976AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20976AO\"></sup>skilled in destruction.",
			"32": "<sup class=\"versenum\">32 </sup>You will be <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20977AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20977AP\"></sup>fuel for the fire; your blood will be in the midst of the land. You will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20977AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20977AQ\"></sup>not be remembered, for I, the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, have spoken.’”"
		},
		"22": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">22 </span>Then the word of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> came to me, saying,",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>“And you, son of man, will you judge, will you judge the bloody city? Then cause her to know all her abominations.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>You shall say, ‘Thus says the Lord <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">God</span>, “A city <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20980A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20980A\"></sup>shedding blood in her midst, so that her time will come, and that makes idols, contrary to her <i>interest</i>, for defilement!",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>You have become <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20981B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20981B\"></sup>guilty by the blood which you have shed, and defiled by your idols which you have made. Thus you have brought your day near and have come to your years; therefore I have made you a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20981C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20981C\"></sup>reproach to the nations and a mocking to all the lands.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>Those who are near and those who are far from you will mock you, you of ill repute, full of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20982D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20982D\"></sup>turmoil.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>“Behold, the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20983E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20983E\"></sup>rulers of Israel, each according to his power, have been in you for the purpose of shedding blood.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>They have <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20984F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20984F\"></sup>treated father and mother lightly within you. The <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20984G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20984G\"></sup>alien they have oppressed in your midst; the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20984H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20984H\"></sup>fatherless and the widow they have wronged in you.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>You have <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20985I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20985I\"></sup>despised My holy things and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20985J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20985J\"></sup>profaned My sabbaths.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>Slanderous men have been in you for the purpose of shedding blood, and in you they have eaten at the mountain <i>shrines</i>. In your midst they have <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20986K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20986K\"></sup>committed acts of lewdness.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>In you they have <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20987L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20987L\"></sup>uncovered <i>their</i> fathers’ nakedness; in you they have humbled her who was <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20987M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20987M\"></sup>unclean in her menstrual impurity.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>One has committed abomination with his <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20988N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20988N\"></sup>neighbor’s wife and another has lewdly defiled his <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20988O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20988O\"></sup>daughter-in-law. And another in you has <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20988P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20988P\"></sup>humbled his sister, his father’s daughter.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>In you they have <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20989Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20989Q\"></sup>taken bribes to shed blood; you have taken <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20989R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20989R\"></sup>interest and profits, and you have injured your neighbors for gain by <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20989S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20989S\"></sup>oppression, and you have <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20989T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20989T\"></sup>forgotten Me,” declares the Lord <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">God</span>.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>“Behold, then, I smite My hand at your <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20990U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20990U\"></sup>dishonest gain which you have acquired and at the bloodshed which is among you.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>Can <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20991V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20991V\"></sup>your heart endure, or can your hands be strong in the days that I will deal with you? <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20991W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20991W\"></sup>I, the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, have spoken and will act.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>I will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20992X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20992X\"></sup>scatter you among the nations and I will disperse you through the lands, and I will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20992Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20992Y\"></sup>consume your uncleanness from you.",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>You will profane yourself in the sight of the nations, and you will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20993Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20993Z\"></sup>know that I am the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.”’”",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>And the word of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> came to me, saying,",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>“Son of man, the house of Israel has become <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20995AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20995AA\"></sup>dross to Me; all of them are <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20995AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20995AB\"></sup>bronze and tin and iron and lead in the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20995AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20995AC\"></sup>furnace; they are the dross of silver.",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>Therefore, thus says the Lord <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">God</span>, ‘Because all of you have become dross, therefore, behold, I am going to gather you into the midst of Jerusalem.",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>As they gather silver and bronze and iron and lead and tin into the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20997AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20997AD\"></sup>furnace to blow fire on it in order to melt <i>it</i>, so I will gather <i>you</i> in My anger and in My wrath and I will lay you <i>there</i> and melt you.",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>I will gather you and blow on you with the fire of My wrath, and you will be melted in the midst of it.",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>As silver is melted in the furnace, so you will be melted in the midst of it; and you will know that I, the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, have <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20999AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20999AE\"></sup>poured out My wrath on you.’”",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>And the word of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> came to me, saying,",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>“Son of man, say to her, ‘You are a land that is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21001AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21001AF\"></sup>not cleansed or rained on in the day of indignation.’",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup>There is a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21002AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21002AG\"></sup>conspiracy of her prophets in her midst like a roaring lion tearing the prey. They have <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21002AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21002AH\"></sup>devoured lives; they have taken treasure and precious things; they have made many <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21002AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21002AI\"></sup>widows in the midst of her.",
			"26": "<sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup>Her <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21003AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21003AJ\"></sup>priests have done violence to My law and have <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21003AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21003AK\"></sup>profaned My holy things; they have made no <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21003AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21003AL\"></sup>distinction between the holy and the profane, and they have not taught the difference between the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21003AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21003AM\"></sup>unclean and the clean; and they hide their eyes from My sabbaths, and I am profaned among them.",
			"27": "<sup class=\"versenum\">27 </sup>Her princes within her are like wolves tearing the prey, by shedding blood <i>and</i> <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21004AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21004AN\"></sup>destroying lives in order to get <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21004AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21004AO\"></sup>dishonest gain.",
			"28": "<sup class=\"versenum\">28 </sup>Her prophets have smeared whitewash for them, seeing <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21005AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21005AP\"></sup>false visions and divining lies for them, saying, ‘Thus says the Lord <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">God</span>,’ when the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> has not spoken.",
			"29": "<sup class=\"versenum\">29 </sup>The people of the land have practiced <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21006AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21006AQ\"></sup>oppression and committed robbery, and they have wronged the poor and needy and have <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21006AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21006AR\"></sup>oppressed the sojourner without justice.",
			"30": "<sup class=\"versenum\">30 </sup>I <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21007AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21007AS\"></sup>searched for a man among them who would <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21007AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21007AT\"></sup>build up the wall and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21007AU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AU&quot;&gt;AU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21007AU\"></sup>stand in the gap before Me for the land, so that I would not destroy it; but I found no one.",
			"31": "<sup class=\"versenum\">31 </sup>Thus I have poured out My <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21008AV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AV&quot;&gt;AV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21008AV\"></sup>indignation on them; I have consumed them with the fire of My wrath; <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21008AW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AW&quot;&gt;AW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21008AW\"></sup>their way I have brought upon their heads,” declares the Lord <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">God</span>."
		},
		"23": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">23 </span>The word of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> came to me again, saying,",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>“Son of man, there were <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21010A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21010A\"></sup>two women, the daughters of one mother;",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>and they played the harlot in Egypt. They <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21011B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21011B\"></sup>played the harlot in their youth; there their breasts were pressed and there their virgin bosom was handled.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>Their names were Oholah the elder and Oholibah her sister. And they became Mine, and they bore sons and daughters. And <i>as for</i> their names, Samaria is Oholah and Jerusalem is Oholibah.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>“Oholah played the harlot while she was Mine; and she lusted after her lovers, after the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21013C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21013C\"></sup>Assyrians, <i>her</i> neighbors,",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>who were clothed in purple, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21014D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21014D\"></sup>governors and officials, all of them desirable young men, horsemen riding on horses.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>She bestowed her harlotries on them, all of whom <i>were</i> the choicest men of Assyria; and with all whom she lusted after, with all their idols she <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21015E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21015E\"></sup>defiled herself.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>She did not forsake her harlotries <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21016F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21016F\"></sup>from <i>the time in</i> Egypt; for in her youth men had lain with her, and they handled her virgin bosom and poured out their lust on her.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>Therefore, I gave her into the hand of her <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21017G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21017G\"></sup>lovers, into the hand of the Assyrians, after whom she lusted.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>They <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21018H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21018H\"></sup>uncovered her nakedness; they took her sons and her daughters, but they slew her with the sword. Thus she became a byword among women, and they executed judgments on her.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>“Now her sister Oholibah saw <i>this</i>, yet she was <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21019I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21019I\"></sup>more corrupt in her lust than she, and her harlotries were more than the harlotries of her sister.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>She lusted after the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21020J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21020J\"></sup>Assyrians, governors and officials, the ones near, magnificently dressed, horsemen riding on horses, all of them desirable young men.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>I saw that she had defiled herself; they both took the same way.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>So she increased her harlotries. And she saw men <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21022K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21022K\"></sup>portrayed on the wall, images of the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21022L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21022L\"></sup>Chaldeans portrayed with vermilion,",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>girded with belts on their loins, with flowing turbans on their heads, all of them looking like officers, like the Babylonians <i>in</i> Chaldea, the land of their birth.",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>When she saw them she <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21024M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21024M\"></sup>lusted after them and sent messengers to them in Chaldea.",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>The <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21025N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21025N\"></sup>Babylonians came to her to the bed of love and defiled her with their harlotry. And when she had been defiled by them, she became disgusted with them.",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>She <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21026O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21026O\"></sup>uncovered her harlotries and uncovered her nakedness; then I became <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21026P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21026P\"></sup>disgusted with her, as I had become disgusted with her <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21026Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21026Q\"></sup>sister.",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>Yet she multiplied her harlotries, remembering the days of her youth, when she played the harlot in the land of Egypt.",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>She <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21028R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21028R\"></sup>lusted after their paramours, whose flesh is <i>like</i> the flesh of donkeys and whose issue is <i>like</i> the issue of horses.",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>Thus you longed for the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21029S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21029S\"></sup>lewdness of your youth, when the Egyptians handled your bosom because of the breasts of your youth.",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>“Therefore, O Oholibah, thus says the Lord <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">God</span>, ‘Behold I will arouse your lovers against you, from whom you were alienated, and I will bring them against you from every side:",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21031T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21031T\"></sup>Babylonians and all the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21031U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21031U\"></sup>Chaldeans, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21031V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21031V\"></sup>Pekod and Shoa and Koa, <i>and</i> all the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21031W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21031W\"></sup>Assyrians with them; desirable young men, governors and officials all of them, officers and men of renown, all of them riding on horses.",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>They will come against you with weapons, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21032X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21032X\"></sup>chariots and wagons, and with a company of peoples. They will set themselves against you on every side with buckler and shield and helmet; and I will commit the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21032Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21032Y\"></sup>judgment to them, and they will judge you according to their customs.",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup>I will set My <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21033Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21033Z\"></sup>jealousy against you, that they may deal with you in wrath. They will remove your nose and your ears; and your survivors will fall by the sword. They will take your <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21033AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21033AA\"></sup>sons and your daughters; and your survivors will be consumed by the fire.",
			"26": "<sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup>They will also <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21034AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21034AB\"></sup>strip you of your clothes and take away your <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21034AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21034AC\"></sup>beautiful jewels.",
			"27": "<sup class=\"versenum\">27 </sup>Thus <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21035AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21035AD\"></sup>I will make your lewdness and your harlotry <i>brought</i> from the land of Egypt to cease from you, so that you will not lift up your eyes to them or remember Egypt anymore.’",
			"28": "<sup class=\"versenum\">28 </sup>For thus says the Lord <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">God</span>, ‘Behold, I will give you into the hand of those whom you <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21036AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21036AE\"></sup>hate, into the hand of those from whom you were alienated.",
			"29": "<sup class=\"versenum\">29 </sup>They will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21037AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21037AF\"></sup>deal with you in hatred, take all your property, and leave you naked and bare. And the nakedness of your harlotries will be uncovered, both your lewdness and your harlotries.",
			"30": "<sup class=\"versenum\">30 </sup>These things will be done to you because you have <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21038AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21038AG\"></sup>played the harlot with the nations, because you have defiled yourself with their idols.",
			"31": "<sup class=\"versenum\">31 </sup>You have walked in the way of your sister; therefore I will give <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21039AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21039AH\"></sup>her cup into your hand.’",
			"32": "<sup class=\"versenum\">32 </sup>Thus says the Lord <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">God</span>,‘You will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21040AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21040AI\"></sup>drink your sister’s cup,Which is deep and wide.You will be <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21040AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21040AJ\"></sup>laughed at and held in derision;It contains much.",
			"33": "<sup class=\"versenum\">33 </sup>‘You will be filled with <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21041AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21041AK\"></sup>drunkenness and sorrow,The cup of horror and desolation,The cup of your sister Samaria.",
			"34": "<sup class=\"versenum\">34 </sup>‘You will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21042AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21042AL\"></sup>drink it and drain it.Then you will gnaw its fragmentsAnd tear your breasts;for I have spoken,’ declares the Lord <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">God</span>.",
			"35": "<sup class=\"versenum\">35 </sup>Therefore, thus says the Lord <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">God</span>, ‘Because you have <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21043AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21043AM\"></sup>forgotten Me and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21043AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21043AN\"></sup>cast Me behind your back, bear now the <i>punishment</i> of your lewdness and your harlotries.’”",
			"36": "<sup class=\"versenum\">36 </sup>Moreover, the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> said to me, “Son of man, will you <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21044AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21044AO\"></sup>judge Oholah and Oholibah? Then <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21044AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21044AP\"></sup>declare to them their abominations.",
			"37": "<sup class=\"versenum\">37 </sup>For they have committed adultery, and blood is on their hands. Thus they have committed adultery with their idols and even caused their sons, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21045AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21045AQ\"></sup>whom they bore to Me, to pass through <i>the fire</i> to them as food.",
			"38": "<sup class=\"versenum\">38 </sup>Again, they have done this to Me: they have <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21046AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21046AR\"></sup>defiled My sanctuary on the same day and have <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21046AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21046AS\"></sup>profaned My sabbaths.",
			"39": "<sup class=\"versenum\">39 </sup>For when they had slaughtered their children for their idols, they entered My <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21047AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21047AT\"></sup>sanctuary on the same day to profane it; and lo, thus they did within My house.",
			"40": "<sup class=\"versenum\">40 </sup>“Furthermore, they have even sent for men who come from afar, to whom a messenger was sent; and lo, they came—for whom you bathed, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21048AU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AU&quot;&gt;AU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21048AU\"></sup>painted your eyes and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21048AV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AV&quot;&gt;AV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21048AV\"></sup>decorated yourselves with ornaments;",
			"41": "<sup class=\"versenum\">41 </sup>and you sat on a splendid <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21049AW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AW&quot;&gt;AW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21049AW\"></sup>couch with a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21049AX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AX&quot;&gt;AX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21049AX\"></sup>table arranged before it on which you had set My <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21049AY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AY&quot;&gt;AY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21049AY\"></sup>incense and My <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21049AZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AZ&quot;&gt;AZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21049AZ\"></sup>oil.",
			"42": "<sup class=\"versenum\">42 </sup>The sound of a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21050BA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BA&quot;&gt;BA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21050BA\"></sup>carefree multitude was with her; and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21050BB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BB&quot;&gt;BB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21050BB\"></sup>drunkards were brought from the wilderness with men of the common sort. And they put <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21050BC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BC&quot;&gt;BC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21050BC\"></sup>bracelets on the hands of the women and beautiful crowns on their heads.",
			"43": "<sup class=\"versenum\">43 </sup>“Then I said concerning her who was <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21051BD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BD&quot;&gt;BD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21051BD\"></sup>worn out by adulteries, ‘Will they now commit adultery with her when she is <i>thus</i>?’",
			"44": "<sup class=\"versenum\">44 </sup>But they went in to her as they would go in to a harlot. Thus they went in to Oholah and to Oholibah, the lewd women.",
			"45": "<sup class=\"versenum\">45 </sup>But they, righteous men, will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21053BE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BE&quot;&gt;BE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21053BE\"></sup>judge them with the judgment of adulteresses and with the judgment of women who shed blood, because they are adulteresses and blood is on their hands.",
			"46": "<sup class=\"versenum\">46 </sup>“For thus says the Lord <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">God</span>, ‘Bring up a company against them and give them over to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21054BF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BF&quot;&gt;BF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21054BF\"></sup>terror and plunder.",
			"47": "<sup class=\"versenum\">47 </sup>The company will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21055BG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BG&quot;&gt;BG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21055BG\"></sup>stone them with stones and cut them down with their swords; they will slay their sons and their daughters and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21055BH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BH&quot;&gt;BH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21055BH\"></sup>burn their houses with fire.",
			"48": "<sup class=\"versenum\">48 </sup>Thus I will make lewdness cease from the land, that all women may be admonished and not commit lewdness as you have done.",
			"49": "<sup class=\"versenum\">49 </sup>Your lewdness will be <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21057BI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BI&quot;&gt;BI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21057BI\"></sup>requited upon you, and you will bear the penalty of <i>worshiping</i> your idols; thus you will know that I am the Lord <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">God</span>.’”"
		},
		"24": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">24 </span>And the word of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> came to me in the ninth year, in the tenth month, on the tenth of the month, saying,",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>“Son of man, write the name of the day, this very day. The king of Babylon has <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21059A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21059A\"></sup>laid siege to Jerusalem this very day.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>Speak a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21060B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21060B\"></sup>parable to the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21060C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21060C\"></sup>rebellious house and say to them, ‘Thus says the Lord <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">God</span>,“Put on the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21060D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21060D\"></sup>pot, put <i>it</i> on and also pour water in it;",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21061E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21061E\"></sup>Put in it the pieces,Every good piece, the thigh and the shoulder;Fill <i>it</i> with choice bones.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>“Take the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21062F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21062F\"></sup>choicest of the flock,And also pile wood under the pot.Make it boil vigorously.Also seethe its bones in it.”",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>‘Therefore, thus says the Lord <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">God</span>,“Woe to the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21063G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21063G\"></sup>bloody city,To the pot in which there is rustAnd whose rust has not gone out of it!Take out of it piece after piece,Without making a choice.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>“For her blood is in her midst;She placed it on the bare rock;She did not <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21064H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21064H\"></sup>pour it on the groundTo cover it with dust.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>“That it may <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21065I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21065I\"></sup>cause wrath to come up to take vengeance,I have put her blood on the bare rock,That it may not be covered.”",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>‘Therefore, thus says the Lord <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">God</span>,“<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21066J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21066J\"></sup>Woe to the bloody city!I also will make the pile great.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>“Heap on the wood, kindle the fire,Boil the flesh wellAnd mix in the spices,And let the bones be burned.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>“Then <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21068K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21068K\"></sup>set it empty on its coalsSo that it may be hotAnd its bronze may glowAnd its <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21068L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21068L\"></sup>filthiness may be melted in it,Its rust consumed.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>“She has <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21069M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21069M\"></sup>wearied <i>Me</i> with toil,Yet her great rust has not gone from her;<i>Let</i> her rust <i>be</i> in the fire!",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>“In your filthiness is lewdness.Because I <i>would</i> have cleansed you,Yet you are <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21070N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21070N\"></sup>not clean,You will not be cleansed from your filthiness againUntil I have <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21070O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21070O\"></sup>spent My wrath on you.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>I, the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, have spoken; it is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21071P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21071P\"></sup>coming and I will act. I will not relent, and I will not <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21071Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21071Q\"></sup>pity and I will not be sorry; <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21071R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21071R\"></sup>according to your ways and according to your deeds I will judge you,” declares the Lord <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">God</span>.’”",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>And the word of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> came to me saying,",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>“Son of man, behold, I am about to take from you the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21073S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21073S\"></sup>desire of your eyes with a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21073T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21073T\"></sup>blow; but you shall not <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21073U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21073U\"></sup>mourn and you shall not weep, and your <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21073V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21073V\"></sup>tears shall not come.",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>Groan silently; make <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21074W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21074W\"></sup>no mourning for the dead. Bind on your turban and put your shoes on your feet, and do not cover <i>your</i> mustache and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21074X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21074X\"></sup>do not eat the bread of men.”",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>So I spoke to the people in the morning, and in the evening my wife died. And in the morning I did as I was commanded.",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>The people said to me, “Will you not tell us what these things that you are doing mean for us?”",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>Then I said to them, “The word of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> came to me saying,",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>‘Speak to the house of Israel, “Thus says the Lord <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">God</span>, ‘Behold, I am about to profane My sanctuary, the pride of your power, the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21078Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21078Y\"></sup>desire of your eyes and the delight of your soul; and your <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21078Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21078Z\"></sup>sons and your daughters whom you have left behind will fall by the sword.",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>You will do as I have done; you will not cover <i>your</i> mustache and you will not eat the bread of men.",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>Your turbans will be on your heads and your shoes on your feet. You <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21080AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21080AA\"></sup>will not mourn and you will not weep, but <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21080AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21080AB\"></sup>you will rot away in your iniquities and you will groan to one another.",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>Thus Ezekiel will be a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21081AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21081AC\"></sup>sign to you; according to all that he has done you will do; when it comes, then you will know that I am the Lord <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">God</span>.’”",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup>‘As for you, son of man, will <i>it</i> not be on the day when I take from them their <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21082AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21082AD\"></sup>stronghold, the joy of their pride, the desire of their eyes and their heart’s delight, their sons and their daughters,",
			"26": "<sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup>that on that day he who <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21083AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21083AE\"></sup>escapes will come to you with information for <i>your</i> ears?",
			"27": "<sup class=\"versenum\">27 </sup>On that day your <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21084AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21084AF\"></sup>mouth will be opened to him who escaped, and you will speak and be mute no longer. Thus you will be a sign to them, and they will know that I am the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.’”"
		},
		"25": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">25 </span>And the word of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> came to me saying,",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>“Son of man, set your face toward the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21086A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21086A\"></sup>sons of Ammon and prophesy against them,",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>and say to the sons of Ammon, ‘Hear the word of the Lord <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">God</span>! Thus says the Lord <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">God</span>, “Because you said, ‘<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21087B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21087B\"></sup>Aha!’ against My sanctuary when it was profaned, and against the land of Israel when it was made desolate, and against the house of Judah when they went into exile,",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>therefore, behold, I am going to give you to the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21088C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21088C\"></sup>sons of the east for a possession, and they will set their encampments among you and make their dwellings among you; they will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21088D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21088D\"></sup>eat your fruit and drink your milk.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>I will make <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21089E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21089E\"></sup>Rabbah a pasture for camels and the sons of Ammon a resting place for flocks. Thus you will know that I am the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.”",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>For thus says the Lord <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">God</span>, “Because you have <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21090F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21090F\"></sup>clapped your hands and stamped your feet and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21090G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21090G\"></sup>rejoiced with all the scorn of your soul against the land of Israel,",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>therefore, behold, I have <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21091H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21091H\"></sup>stretched out My hand against you and I will give you for <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21091I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21091I\"></sup>spoil to the nations. And I will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21091J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21091J\"></sup>cut you off from the peoples and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21091K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21091K\"></sup>make you perish from the lands; I will destroy you. Thus you will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21091L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21091L\"></sup>know that I am the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.”",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>‘Thus says the Lord <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">God</span>, “Because <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21092M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21092M\"></sup>Moab and Seir say, ‘Behold, the house of Judah is like all the nations,’",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>therefore, behold, I am going to deprive the flank of Moab of <i>its</i> cities, of its cities which are on its frontiers, the glory of the land, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21093N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21093N\"></sup>Beth-jeshimoth, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21093O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21093O\"></sup>Baal-meon and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21093P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21093P\"></sup>Kiriathaim,",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>and I will give it for a possession along with the sons of Ammon to the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21094Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21094Q\"></sup>sons of the east, so that the sons of Ammon will not be remembered among the nations.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>Thus I will execute judgments on Moab, and they will know that I am the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.”",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>‘Thus says the Lord <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">God</span>, “Because <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21096R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21096R\"></sup>Edom has acted against the house of Judah by taking vengeance, and has incurred grievous guilt, and avenged themselves upon them,”",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>therefore thus says the Lord <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">God</span>, “I will also <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21097S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21097S\"></sup>stretch out My hand against Edom and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21097T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21097T\"></sup>cut off man and beast from it. And I will lay it waste; from <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21097U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21097U\"></sup>Teman even to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21097V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21097V\"></sup>Dedan they will fall by the sword.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21098W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21098W\"></sup>I will lay My vengeance on Edom by the hand of My people Israel. Therefore, they will act in Edom <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21098X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21098X\"></sup>according to My anger and according to My wrath; thus they will know My vengeance,” declares the Lord <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">God</span>.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>‘Thus says the Lord <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">God</span>, “Because the Philistines have acted in <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21099Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21099Y\"></sup>revenge and have taken vengeance with scorn of soul to destroy with everlasting enmity,”",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>therefore thus says the Lord <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">God</span>, “Behold, I will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21100Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21100Z\"></sup>stretch out My hand against the Philistines, even cut off the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21100AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21100AA\"></sup>Cherethites and destroy the remnant of the seacoast.",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>I will execute great vengeance on them with wrathful rebukes; and they will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21101AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21101AB\"></sup>know that I am the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> when I lay My vengeance on them.”’”"
		},
		"26": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">26 </span>Now in the eleventh year, on the first of the month, the word of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> came to me saying,",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>“Son of man, because <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21103A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21103A\"></sup>Tyre has said concerning Jerusalem, ‘Aha, the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21103B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21103B\"></sup>gateway of the peoples is broken; it has <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21103C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21103C\"></sup>opened to me. I shall be filled, <i>now that</i> she is laid waste,’",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>therefore thus says the Lord <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">God</span>, ‘Behold, I am against you, O Tyre, and I will bring up <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21104D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21104D\"></sup>many nations against you, as the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21104E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21104E\"></sup>sea brings up its waves.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>They will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21105F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21105F\"></sup>destroy the walls of Tyre and break down her towers; and I will scrape her debris from her and make her a bare rock.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>She will be a place for the spreading of nets in the midst of the sea, for I have spoken,’ declares the Lord <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">God</span>, ‘and she will become <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21106G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21106G\"></sup>spoil for the nations.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>Also her <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21107H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21107H\"></sup>daughters who are on the mainland will be slain by the sword, and they will know that I am the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.’”",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>For thus says the Lord <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">God</span>, “Behold, I will bring upon Tyre from the north Nebuchadnezzar king of Babylon, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21108I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21108I\"></sup>king of kings, with horses, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21108J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21108J\"></sup>chariots, cavalry and a great army.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>He will slay your daughters on the mainland with the sword; and he will make <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21109K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21109K\"></sup>siege walls against you, cast up a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21109L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21109L\"></sup>ramp against you and raise up a large shield against you.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>The blow of his battering rams he will direct against your walls, and with his axes he will break down your towers.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>Because of the multitude of his <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21111M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21111M\"></sup>horses, the dust <i>raised by</i> them will cover you; your walls will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21111N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21111N\"></sup>shake at the noise of cavalry and wagons and chariots when he <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21111O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21111O\"></sup>enters your gates as men enter a city that is breached.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>With the hoofs of his <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21112P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21112P\"></sup>horses he will trample all your streets. He will slay your people with the sword; and your strong pillars will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21112Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21112Q\"></sup>come down to the ground.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>Also they will make a spoil of your riches and a prey of your <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21113R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21113R\"></sup>merchandise, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21113S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21113S\"></sup>break down your walls and destroy your <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21113T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21113T\"></sup>pleasant houses, and throw your stones and your timbers and your debris <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21113U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21113U\"></sup>into the water.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>So I will silence the sound of your <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21114V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21114V\"></sup>songs, and the sound of your <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21114W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21114W\"></sup>harps will be heard no more.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>I will make you a bare rock; you will be a place for the spreading of nets. You will be <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21115X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21115X\"></sup>built no more, for I the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21115Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21115Y\"></sup><span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> have spoken,” declares the Lord <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">God</span>.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>Thus says the Lord <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">God</span> to Tyre, “Shall not the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21116Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21116Z\"></sup>coastlands <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21116AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21116AA\"></sup>shake at the sound of your fall when the wounded groan, when the slaughter occurs in your midst?",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>Then all the princes of the sea will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21117AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21117AB\"></sup>go down from their thrones, remove their robes and strip off their embroidered garments. They will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21117AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21117AC\"></sup>clothe themselves with trembling; they will sit on the ground, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21117AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21117AD\"></sup>tremble every moment and be appalled at you.",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>They will take up a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21118AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21118AE\"></sup>lamentation over you and say to you,‘<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21118AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21118AF\"></sup>How you have perished, O inhabited one,From the seas, O renowned city,Which was <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21118AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21118AG\"></sup>mighty on the sea,She and her inhabitants,Who imposed her terrorOn all her inhabitants!",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>‘Now the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21119AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21119AH\"></sup>coastlands will trembleOn the day of your fall;Yes, the coastlands which are by the seaWill be terrified at your <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21119AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21119AI\"></sup>passing.’”",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>For thus says the Lord <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">God</span>, “When I make you a desolate city, like the cities which are not inhabited, when I <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21120AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21120AJ\"></sup>bring up the deep over you and the great waters cover you,",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>then I will bring you down with those who <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21121AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21121AK\"></sup>go down to the pit, to the people of old, and I will make you dwell in the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21121AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21121AL\"></sup>lower parts of the earth, like the ancient waste places, with those who go down to the pit, so that you will not be inhabited; but I will set <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21121AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21121AM\"></sup>glory in the land of the living.",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>I will bring <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21122AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21122AN\"></sup>terrors on you and you will be no more; though you will be sought, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21122AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21122AO\"></sup>you will never be found again,” declares the Lord <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">God</span>."
		},
		"27": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">27 </span>Moreover, the word of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> came to me saying,",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>“And you, son of man, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21124A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21124A\"></sup>take up a lamentation over Tyre;",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>and say to Tyre, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21125B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21125B\"></sup>who dwells at the entrance to the sea, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21125C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21125C\"></sup>merchant of the peoples to many coastlands, ‘Thus says the Lord <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">God</span>,“O Tyre, you have said, ‘I am perfect in beauty.’",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>“Your borders are in the heart of the seas;Your builders have perfected your beauty.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>“They have made all <i>your</i> planks of fir trees from <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21127D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21127D\"></sup>Senir;They have taken a cedar from Lebanon to make a mast for you.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>“Of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21128E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21128E\"></sup>oaks from <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21128F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21128F\"></sup>Bashan they have made your oars;With ivory they have inlaid your deck of boxwood from the coastlands of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21128G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21128G\"></sup>Cyprus.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>“Your sail was of fine embroidered linen from EgyptSo that it became your distinguishing mark;Your awning was <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21129H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21129H\"></sup>blue and purple from the coastlands of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21129I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21129I\"></sup>Elishah.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>“The inhabitants of Sidon and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21130J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21130J\"></sup>Arvad were your rowers;Your <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21130K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21130K\"></sup>wise men, O Tyre, were aboard; they were your pilots.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>“The elders of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21131L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21131L\"></sup>Gebal and her wise men were with you repairing your seams;All the ships of the sea and their sailors were with you in order to deal in your merchandise.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>“<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21132M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21132M\"></sup>Persia and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21132N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21132N\"></sup>Lud and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21132O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21132O\"></sup>Put were in your army, your men of war. They hung shield and helmet in you; they set forth your splendor.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>The sons of Arvad and your army were on your walls, <i>all</i> around, and the Gammadim were in your towers. They hung their shields on your walls <i>all</i> around; they perfected your beauty.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>“Tarshish was your customer because of the abundance of all <i>kinds</i> of wealth; with silver, iron, tin and lead they paid for your wares.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21135P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21135P\"></sup>Javan, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21135Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21135Q\"></sup>Tubal and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21135R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21135R\"></sup>Meshech, they were your traders; with the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21135S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21135S\"></sup>lives of men and vessels of bronze they paid for your merchandise.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>Those from <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21136T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21136T\"></sup>Beth-togarmah gave horses and war horses and mules for your wares.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>The sons of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21137U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21137U\"></sup>Dedan were your traders. Many coastlands were your market; <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21137V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21137V\"></sup>ivory tusks and ebony they brought as your payment.",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21138W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21138W\"></sup>Aram was your customer because of the abundance of your goods; they paid for your wares with <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21138X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21138X\"></sup>emeralds, purple, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21138Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21138Y\"></sup>embroidered work, fine linen, coral and rubies.",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>Judah and the land of Israel, they were your traders; with the wheat of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21139Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21139Z\"></sup>Minnith, cakes, honey, oil and balm they paid for your merchandise.",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21140AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21140AA\"></sup>Damascus was your customer because of the abundance of your goods, because of the abundance of all <i>kinds</i> of wealth, because of the wine of Helbon and white wool.",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>Vedan and Javan paid for your wares from Uzal; wrought iron, cassia and sweet cane were among your merchandise.",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21142AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21142AB\"></sup>Dedan traded with you in saddlecloths for riding.",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21143AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21143AC\"></sup>Arabia and all the princes of Kedar, they were your customers for <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21143AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21143AD\"></sup>lambs, rams and goats; for these they were your customers.",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>The traders of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21144AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21144AE\"></sup>Sheba and Raamah, they traded with you; they paid for your wares with the best of all <i>kinds</i> of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21144AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21144AF\"></sup>spices, and with all <i>kinds</i> of precious stones and gold.",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>Haran, Canneh, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21145AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21145AG\"></sup>Eden, the traders of Sheba, Asshur <i>and</i> Chilmad traded with you.",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>They traded with you in choice garments, in clothes of blue and embroidered work, and in carpets of many colors <i>and</i> tightly wound cords, <i>which were</i> among your merchandise.",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup>The <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21147AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21147AH\"></sup>ships of Tarshish were the carriers for your merchandise.And you were filled and were very gloriousIn the heart of the seas.",
			"26": "<sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup>“Your rowers have brought youInto <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21148AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21148AI\"></sup>great waters;The <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21148AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21148AJ\"></sup>east wind has broken youIn the heart of the seas.",
			"27": "<sup class=\"versenum\">27 </sup>“Your wealth, your wares, your merchandise,Your sailors and your pilots,Your repairers of seams, your dealers in merchandiseAnd all your men of war who are in you,With all your company that is in your midst,Will fall into the heart of the seasOn the day of your overthrow.",
			"28": "<sup class=\"versenum\">28 </sup>“At the sound of the cry of your pilotsThe pasture lands will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21150AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21150AK\"></sup>shake.",
			"29": "<sup class=\"versenum\">29 </sup>“All who handle the oar,The <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21151AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21151AL\"></sup>sailors <i>and</i> all the pilots of the seaWill come down from their ships;They will stand on the land,",
			"30": "<sup class=\"versenum\">30 </sup>And they will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21152AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21152AM\"></sup>make their voice heard over youAnd will cry bitterly.They will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21152AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21152AN\"></sup>cast dust on their heads,They will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21152AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21152AO\"></sup>wallow in ashes.",
			"31": "<sup class=\"versenum\">31 </sup>“Also they will make themselves <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21153AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21153AP\"></sup>bald for youAnd <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21153AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21153AQ\"></sup>gird themselves with sackcloth;And they will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21153AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21153AR\"></sup>weep for you in bitterness of soulWith bitter mourning.",
			"32": "<sup class=\"versenum\">32 </sup>“Moreover, in their wailing they will take up a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21154AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21154AS\"></sup>lamentation for youAnd lament over you:‘Who is like Tyre,Like her who is silent in the midst of the sea?",
			"33": "<sup class=\"versenum\">33 </sup>‘When your wares went out from the seas,You satisfied many peoples;With the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21155AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21155AT\"></sup>abundance of your wealth and your merchandiseYou enriched the kings of earth.",
			"34": "<sup class=\"versenum\">34 </sup>‘Now that you are <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21156AU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AU&quot;&gt;AU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21156AU\"></sup>broken by the seasIn the depths of the waters,Your <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21156AV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AV&quot;&gt;AV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21156AV\"></sup>merchandise and all your companyHave fallen in the midst of you.",
			"35": "<sup class=\"versenum\">35 </sup>‘All the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21157AW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AW&quot;&gt;AW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21157AW\"></sup>inhabitants of the coastlandsAre appalled at you,And their kings are horribly afraid;They are troubled in countenance.",
			"36": "<sup class=\"versenum\">36 </sup>‘The merchants among the peoples <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21158AX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AX&quot;&gt;AX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21158AX\"></sup>hiss at you;You have become terrifiedAnd you <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21158AY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AY&quot;&gt;AY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21158AY\"></sup>will cease to be forever.’”’”"
		},
		"28": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">28 </span>The word of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> came again to me, saying,",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>“Son of man, say to the leader of Tyre, ‘Thus says the Lord <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">God</span>,“Because your heart is lifted upAnd you have said, ‘<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21160A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21160A\"></sup>I am a god,I sit in the seat of godsIn the heart of the seas’;Yet you are a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21160B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21160B\"></sup>man and not God,Although you make your heart like the heart of God—",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>Behold, you are wiser than <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21161C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21161C\"></sup>Daniel;There is no secret that is a match for you.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>“By your wisdom and understandingYou have acquired <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21162D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21162D\"></sup>riches for yourselfAnd have acquired gold and silver for your treasuries.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>“By your great wisdom, by your <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21163E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21163E\"></sup>tradeYou have increased your richesAnd your <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21163F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21163F\"></sup>heart is lifted up because of your riches—",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>Therefore thus says the Lord <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">God</span>,‘Because you have <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21164G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21164G\"></sup>made your heartLike the heart of God,",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>Therefore, behold, I will bring <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21165H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21165H\"></sup>strangers upon you,The <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21165I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21165I\"></sup>most ruthless of the nations.And they will draw their swordsAgainst the beauty of your wisdomAnd defile your splendor.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>‘They will bring you down to the pit,And you will die the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21166J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21166J\"></sup>death of those who are slainIn the heart of the seas.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>‘Will you still say, “I am a god,”In the presence of your slayer,Though you are a man and not God,In the hands of those who wound you?",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>‘You will die the death of the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21168K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21168K\"></sup>uncircumcisedBy the hand of strangers,For I have spoken!’ declares the Lord <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">God</span>!”’”",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>Again the word of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> came to me saying,",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>“Son of man, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21170L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21170L\"></sup>take up a lamentation over the king of Tyre and say to him, ‘Thus says the Lord <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">God</span>,“You had the seal of perfection,Full of wisdom and perfect in beauty.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>“You were in <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21171M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21171M\"></sup>Eden, the garden of God;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21171N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21171N\"></sup>Every precious stone was your covering:The <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21171O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21171O\"></sup>ruby, the topaz and the diamond;The beryl, the onyx and the jasper;The lapis lazuli, the turquoise and the emerald;And the gold, the workmanship of your <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21171P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21171P\"></sup>settings and sockets,Was in you.On the day that you were createdThey were prepared.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>“You were the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21172Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21172Q\"></sup>anointed cherub who covers,And I placed you <i>there</i>.You were on the holy <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21172R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21172R\"></sup>mountain of God;You walked in the midst of the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21172S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21172S\"></sup>stones of fire.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>“You were <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21173T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21173T\"></sup>blameless in your waysFrom the day you were createdUntil <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21173U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21173U\"></sup>unrighteousness was found in you.",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>“By the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21174V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21174V\"></sup>abundance of your tradeYou were internally <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21174W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21174W\"></sup>filled with violence,And you sinned;Therefore I have cast you as profaneFrom the mountain of God.And I have destroyed you, O covering cherub,From the midst of the stones of fire.",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>“Your heart was lifted up because of your <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21175X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21175X\"></sup>beauty;You <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21175Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21175Y\"></sup>corrupted your wisdom by reason of your splendor.I cast you to the ground;I put you before <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21175Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21175Z\"></sup>kings,That they may see you.",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>“By the multitude of your iniquities,In the unrighteousness of your tradeYou profaned your sanctuaries.Therefore I have brought <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21176AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21176AA\"></sup>fire from the midst of you;It has consumed you,And I have turned you to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21176AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21176AB\"></sup>ashes on the earthIn the eyes of all who see you.",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>“All who know you among the peoplesAre appalled at you;You have become <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21177AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21177AC\"></sup>terrifiedAnd you will cease to be <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21177AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21177AD\"></sup>forever.”’”",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>And the word of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> came to me saying,",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>“Son of man, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21179AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21179AE\"></sup>set your face toward <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21179AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21179AF\"></sup>Sidon, prophesy against her",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>and say, ‘Thus says the Lord <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">God</span>,“Behold, I am against you, O Sidon,And I will be glorified in your midst.Then they will know that I am the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> when I <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21180AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21180AG\"></sup>execute judgments in her,And I will manifest My holiness in her.",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>“For <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21181AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21181AH\"></sup>I will send pestilence to herAnd blood to her streets,And the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21181AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21181AI\"></sup>wounded will fall in her midstBy the sword upon her on every side;Then they will know that I am the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>And there will be no more for the house of Israel a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21182AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21182AJ\"></sup>prickling brier or a painful thorn from any round about them who scorned them; then they will know that I am the Lord <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">God</span>.”",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup>‘Thus says the Lord <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">God</span>, “When I <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21183AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21183AK\"></sup>gather the house of Israel from the peoples among whom they are scattered, and will manifest My holiness in them in the sight of the nations, then they will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21183AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21183AL\"></sup>live in their land which I gave to My servant Jacob.",
			"26": "<sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup>They will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21184AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21184AM\"></sup>live in it securely; and they will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21184AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21184AN\"></sup>build houses, plant vineyards and live securely when I <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21184AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21184AO\"></sup>execute judgments upon all who scorn them round about them. Then they will know that I am the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> their God.”’”"
		},
		"29": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">29 </span>In the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21185A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21185A\"></sup>tenth year, in the tenth <i>month</i>, on the twelfth of the month, the word of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> came to me saying,",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>“Son of man, set your face against <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21186B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21186B\"></sup>Pharaoh king of Egypt and prophesy against him and against all <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21186C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21186C\"></sup>Egypt.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>Speak and say, ‘Thus says the Lord <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">God</span>,“Behold, I am against you, Pharaoh king of Egypt,The great <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21187D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21187D\"></sup>monster that lies in the midst of his rivers,That <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21187E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21187E\"></sup>has said, ‘My Nile is mine, and I myself have made <i>it</i>.’",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>“I will put <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21188F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21188F\"></sup>hooks in your jawsAnd make the fish of your rivers cling to your scales.And I will bring you up out of the midst of your rivers,And all the fish of your rivers will cling to your scales.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>“I will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21189G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21189G\"></sup>abandon you to the wilderness, you and all the fish of your rivers;You will fall on the open field; you will not be brought together or <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21189H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21189H\"></sup>gathered.I have given you for <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21189I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21189I\"></sup>food to the beasts of the earth and to the birds of the sky.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>“Then all the inhabitants of Egypt will know that I am the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>,Because they have been <i>only</i> a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21190J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21190J\"></sup>staff <i>made</i> of reed to the house of Israel.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>“When they took hold of you with the hand,You <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21191K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21191K\"></sup>broke and tore all their hands;And when they leaned on you,You broke and made all their loins quake.”",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>‘Therefore thus says the Lord <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">God</span>, “Behold, I will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21192L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21192L\"></sup>bring upon you a sword and I will cut off from you man and beast.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>The <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21193M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21193M\"></sup>land of Egypt will become a desolation and waste. Then they will know that I am the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.Because you <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21193N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21193N\"></sup>said, ‘The Nile is mine, and I have made <i>it</i>,’",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>therefore, behold, I am <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21194O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21194O\"></sup>against you and against your rivers, and I will make the land of Egypt an utter waste and desolation, from Migdol <i>to</i> Syene and even to the border of Ethiopia.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>A man’s foot will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21195P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21195P\"></sup>not pass through it, and the foot of a beast will not pass through it, and it will not be inhabited for forty years.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>So I will make the land of Egypt a desolation in the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21196Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21196Q\"></sup>midst of desolated lands. And her cities, in the midst of cities that are laid waste, will be desolate forty years; and I will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21196R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21196R\"></sup>scatter the Egyptians among the nations and disperse them among the lands.”",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>‘For thus says the Lord <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">God</span>, “At the end of forty years I will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21197S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21197S\"></sup>gather the Egyptians from the peoples among whom they were scattered.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>I will turn the fortunes of Egypt and make them return to the land of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21198T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21198T\"></sup>Pathros, to the land of their origin, and there they will be a lowly kingdom.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>It will be the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21199U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21199U\"></sup>lowest of the kingdoms, and it will never again lift itself up above the nations. And I will make them so small that they will not <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21199V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21199V\"></sup>rule over the nations.",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>And it will never again be the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21200W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21200W\"></sup>confidence of the house of Israel, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21200X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21200X\"></sup>bringing to mind the iniquity of their having turned to Egypt. Then they will know that I am the Lord <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">God</span>.”’”",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>Now in the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21201Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21201Y\"></sup>twenty-seventh year, in the first <i>month</i>, on the first of the month, the word of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> came to me saying,",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>“Son of man, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21202Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21202Z\"></sup>Nebuchadnezzar king of Babylon made his army labor hard against Tyre; every head was made <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21202AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21202AA\"></sup>bald and every shoulder was rubbed bare. But he and his army had no wages from Tyre for the labor that he had performed against it.”",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>Therefore thus says the Lord <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">God</span>, “Behold, I <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21203AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21203AB\"></sup>will give the land of Egypt to Nebuchadnezzar king of Babylon. And he will carry off her <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21203AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21203AC\"></sup>wealth and capture her spoil and seize her plunder; and it will be wages for his army.",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>I have given him the land of Egypt <i>for</i> his labor which he <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21204AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21204AD\"></sup>performed, because they acted for Me,” declares the Lord <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">God</span>.",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>“On that day I will make a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21205AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21205AE\"></sup>horn sprout for the house of Israel, and I will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21205AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21205AF\"></sup>open your mouth in their midst. Then they will know that I am the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.”"
		},
		"30": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">30 </span>The word of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> came again to me saying,",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>“Son of man, prophesy and say, ‘Thus says the Lord <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">God</span>,“<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21207A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21207A\"></sup>Wail, ‘Alas for the day!’",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>“For the day is near,Even <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21208B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21208B\"></sup>the day of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> is near;It will be a day of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21208C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21208C\"></sup>clouds,A time <i>of doom</i> for the nations.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>“A sword will come upon Egypt,And anguish will be in Ethiopia;When the slain fall in Egypt,They <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21209D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21209D\"></sup>take away her wealth,And her foundations are torn down.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>Ethiopia, Put, Lud, all <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21210E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21210E\"></sup>Arabia, Libya and the people of the land that is in league will fall with them by the sword.”",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>‘Thus says the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>,“Indeed, those who support <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21211F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21211F\"></sup>Egypt will fallAnd the pride of her power will come down;From Migdol <i>to</i> SyeneThey will fall within her by the sword,”Declares the Lord <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">God</span>.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>“They will be desolateIn the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21212G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21212G\"></sup>midst of the desolated lands;And her cities will beIn the midst of the devastated cities.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>“And they will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21213H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21213H\"></sup>know that I am the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>,When I set a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21213I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21213I\"></sup>fire in EgyptAnd all her helpers are broken.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>On that day <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21214J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21214J\"></sup>messengers will go forth from Me in ships to frighten <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21214K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21214K\"></sup>secure Ethiopia; and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21214L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21214L\"></sup>anguish will be on them as on the day of Egypt; for behold, it comes!”",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>‘Thus says the Lord <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">God</span>,“<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21215M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21215M\"></sup>I will also make the hordes of Egypt ceaseBy the hand of Nebuchadnezzar king of Babylon.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>“He and his people with him,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21216N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21216N\"></sup>The most ruthless of the nations,Will be brought in to destroy the land;And they will draw their swords against EgyptAnd fill the land with the slain.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>“Moreover, I will make the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21217O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21217O\"></sup>Nile canals dryAnd <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21217P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21217P\"></sup>sell the land into the hands of evil men.And I will make the land desolateAnd all that is in it,By the hand of strangers; I the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> have spoken.”",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>‘Thus says the Lord <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">God</span>,“I will also <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21218Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21218Q\"></sup>destroy the idolsAnd make the images cease from <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21218R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21218R\"></sup>Memphis.And there will no longer be a prince in the land of Egypt;And I will put fear in the land of Egypt.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>“I will make <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21219S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21219S\"></sup>Pathros desolate,Set a fire in <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21219T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21219T\"></sup>ZoanAnd execute judgments on <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21219U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21219U\"></sup>Thebes.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>“I will pour out My wrath on Sin,The stronghold of Egypt;I will also cut off the hordes of Thebes.",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>“I will set a fire in Egypt;Sin will writhe in anguish,Thebes will be breachedAnd Memphis <i>will have</i> distresses daily.",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>“The young men of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21222V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21222V\"></sup>On and of Pi-besethWill fall by the sword,And the women will go into captivity.",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>“In <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21223W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21223W\"></sup>Tehaphnehes the day will be <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21223X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21223X\"></sup>darkWhen I <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21223Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21223Y\"></sup>break there the yoke bars of Egypt.Then the pride of her power will cease in her;A cloud will cover her,And her daughters will go into captivity.",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>“Thus I will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21224Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21224Z\"></sup>execute judgments on Egypt,And they will know that I am the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.”’”",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>In the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21225AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21225AA\"></sup>eleventh year, in the first <i>month</i>, on the seventh of the month, the word of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> came to me saying,",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>“Son of man, I have <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21226AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21226AB\"></sup>broken the arm of Pharaoh king of Egypt; and, behold, it has not been <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21226AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21226AC\"></sup>bound up for healing or wrapped with a bandage, that it may be strong to hold the sword.",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>Therefore thus says the Lord <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">God</span>, ‘Behold, I am <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21227AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21227AD\"></sup>against Pharaoh king of Egypt and will break his arms, both the strong and the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21227AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21227AE\"></sup>broken; and I will make the sword <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21227AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21227AF\"></sup>fall from his hand.",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>I will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21228AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21228AG\"></sup>scatter the Egyptians among the nations and disperse them among the lands.",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>For I will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21229AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21229AH\"></sup>strengthen the arms of the king of Babylon and put <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21229AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21229AI\"></sup>My sword in his hand; and I will break the arms of Pharaoh, so that he will groan before him with the groanings of a wounded man.",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup>Thus I will strengthen the arms of the king of Babylon, but the arms of Pharaoh will fall. Then they will know that I am the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, when I put My sword into the hand of the king of Babylon and he <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21230AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21230AJ\"></sup>stretches it out against the land of Egypt.",
			"26": "<sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup>When I scatter the Egyptians among the nations and disperse them among the lands, then they will know that I am the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.’”"
		},
		"31": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">31 </span>In the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21232A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21232A\"></sup>eleventh year, in the third <i>month</i>, on the first of the month, the word of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> came to me saying,",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>“Son of man, say to Pharaoh king of Egypt and to his <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21233B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21233B\"></sup>hordes,‘Whom are you like in your greatness?",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>‘Behold, Assyria <i>was</i> a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21234C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21234C\"></sup>cedar in LebanonWith beautiful branches and forest shade,And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21234D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21234D\"></sup>very high,And its top was among the clouds.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>‘The <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21235E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21235E\"></sup>waters made it grow, the deep made it high.With its rivers it continually extended all around its planting place,And sent out its channels to all the trees of the field.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>‘Therefore <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21236F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21236F\"></sup>its height was loftier than all the trees of the fieldAnd its boughs became many and its branches longBecause of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21236G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21236G\"></sup>many waters as it spread them out.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>‘All the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21237H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21237H\"></sup>birds of the heavens nested in its boughs,And under its branches all the beasts of the field gave birth,And all great nations lived under its shade.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>‘So it was beautiful in its greatness, in the length of its branches;For its roots extended to many waters.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>‘The <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21239I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21239I\"></sup>cedars in <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21239J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21239J\"></sup>God’s garden could not match it;The cypresses could not compare with its boughs,And the plane trees could not match its branches.No tree in <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21239K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21239K\"></sup>God’s garden could compare with it in its beauty.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>‘I made it beautiful with the multitude of its branches,And all the trees of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21240L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21240L\"></sup>Eden, which were in the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21240M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21240M\"></sup>garden of God, were jealous of it.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>‘Therefore thus says the Lord <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">God</span>, “Because it is high in stature and has set its top among the clouds, and its <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21241N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21241N\"></sup>heart is haughty in its loftiness,",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>therefore I will give it into the hand of a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21242O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21242O\"></sup>despot of the nations; he will thoroughly deal with it. According to its wickedness I have <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21242P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21242P\"></sup>driven it away.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21243Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21243Q\"></sup>Alien <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21243R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21243R\"></sup>tyrants of the nations have cut it down and left it; on the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21243S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21243S\"></sup>mountains and in all the valleys its branches have fallen and its boughs have been broken in all the ravines of the land. And all the peoples of the earth have <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21243T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21243T\"></sup>gone down from its shade and left it.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>On its ruin all the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21244U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21244U\"></sup>birds of the heavens will dwell, and all the beasts of the field will be on its <i>fallen</i> branches",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>so that all the trees by the waters may not be exalted in their stature, nor set their top among the clouds, nor their well-watered mighty ones stand <i>erect</i> in their height. For they have all been given over to death, to the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21245V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21245V\"></sup>earth beneath, among the sons of men, with those who go down to the pit.”",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>‘Thus says the Lord <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">God</span>, “On the day when it went down to Sheol I <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21246W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21246W\"></sup>caused lamentations; I closed the deep over it and held back its rivers. And <i>its</i> many waters were stopped up, and I made Lebanon mourn for it, and all the trees of the field wilted away on account of it.",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>I made the nations <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21247X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21247X\"></sup>quake at the sound of its fall when I made it <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21247Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21247Y\"></sup>go down to Sheol with those who go down to the pit; and all the well-watered trees of Eden, the choicest and best of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21247Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21247Z\"></sup>Lebanon, were <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21247AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21247AA\"></sup>comforted in the earth beneath.",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>They also <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21248AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21248AB\"></sup>went down with it to Sheol to those who were <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21248AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21248AC\"></sup>slain by the sword; and those who were its strength lived <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21248AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21248AD\"></sup>under its shade among the nations.",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>“To which among the trees of Eden are you thus equal in glory and greatness? Yet you will be brought down with the trees of Eden to the earth beneath; you will lie in the midst of the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21249AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21249AE\"></sup>uncircumcised, with those who were slain by the sword. <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21249AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21249AF\"></sup>So is Pharaoh and all his hordes!”’ declares the Lord <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">God</span>.”"
		},
		"32": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">32 </span>In the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21250A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21250A\"></sup>twelfth year, in the twelfth <i>month</i>, on the first of the month, the word of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> came to me saying,",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>“Son of man, take up a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21251B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21251B\"></sup>lamentation over Pharaoh king of Egypt and say to him,‘You compared yourself to a young <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21251C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21251C\"></sup>lion of the nations,Yet you are like the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21251D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21251D\"></sup>monster in the seas;And you <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21251E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21251E\"></sup>burst forth in your riversAnd muddied the waters with your feetAnd fouled their rivers.’”",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>Thus says the Lord <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">God</span>,“Now I will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21252F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21252F\"></sup>spread My net over youWith a company of many peoples,And they shall lift you up in My net.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>“I will leave you on the land;I will cast you on the open field.And I will cause all the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21253G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21253G\"></sup>birds of the heavens to dwell on you,And I will satisfy the beasts of the whole earth with you.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>“I will lay your flesh <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21254H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21254H\"></sup>on the mountainsAnd fill the valleys with your refuse.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>“I will also make the land drink the discharge of your <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21255I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21255I\"></sup>bloodAs far as the mountains,And the ravines will be full of you.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>“And when <i>I</i> <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21256J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21256J\"></sup>extinguish you,I will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21256K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21256K\"></sup>cover the heavens and darken their <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21256L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21256L\"></sup>stars;I will cover the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21256M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21256M\"></sup>sun with a cloudAnd the moon will not give its light.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>“All the shining <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21257N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21257N\"></sup>lights in the heavensI will darken over youAnd will set darkness on your land,”Declares the Lord <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">God</span>.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>“I will also <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21258O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21258O\"></sup>trouble the hearts of many peoples when I <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21258P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21258P\"></sup>bring your destruction among the nations, into lands which you have not known.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>I will make many peoples <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21259Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21259Q\"></sup>appalled at you, and their kings will be horribly afraid of you when I brandish My sword before them; and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21259R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21259R\"></sup>they will tremble every moment, every man for his own life, on the day of your fall.”",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>For <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21260S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21260S\"></sup>thus says the Lord <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">God</span>, “The sword of the king of Babylon will come upon you.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>By the swords of the mighty ones I will cause your hordes to fall; all of them are <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21261T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21261T\"></sup>tyrants of the nations,And they will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21261U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21261U\"></sup>devastate the pride of Egypt,And all its hordes will be destroyed.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>“I will also destroy all its cattle from beside many waters;And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21262V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21262V\"></sup>the foot of man will not muddy them anymoreAnd the hoofs of beasts will not muddy them.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>“Then I will make their waters settleAnd will cause their rivers to run like oil,”Declares the Lord <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">God</span>.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>“When I make the land of Egypt a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21264W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21264W\"></sup>desolation,And the land is destitute of that which filled it,When I smite all those who live in it,Then they shall <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21264X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21264X\"></sup>know that I am the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>This is a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21265Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21265Y\"></sup>lamentation and they shall chant it. The daughters of the nations shall chant it. Over Egypt and over all her hordes they shall chant it,” declares the Lord <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">God</span>.",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>In the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21266Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21266Z\"></sup>twelfth year, on the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21266AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21266AA\"></sup>fifteenth of the month, the word of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> came to me saying,",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>“Son of man, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21267AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21267AB\"></sup>wail for the hordes of Egypt and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21267AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21267AC\"></sup>bring it down, her and the daughters of the powerful nations, to the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21267AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21267AD\"></sup>nether world, with those who go down to the pit;",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>‘Whom do you surpass in beauty?Go down and make your bed with the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21268AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21268AE\"></sup>uncircumcised.’",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>They shall fall in the midst of those who are slain by the sword. She is given over to the sword; they have <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21269AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21269AF\"></sup>drawn her and all her hordes away.",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>The <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21270AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21270AG\"></sup>strong among the mighty ones shall speak of him <i>and</i> his helpers from the midst of Sheol, ‘They have gone down, they lie still, the uncircumcised, slain by the sword.’",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>“<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21271AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21271AH\"></sup>Assyria is there and all her company; her graves are round about her. All of them are slain, fallen by the sword,",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>whose <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21272AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21272AI\"></sup>graves are set in the remotest parts of the pit and her company is round about her grave. All of them are slain, fallen by the sword, who spread terror in the land of the living.",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>“<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21273AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21273AJ\"></sup>Elam is there and all her hordes around her grave; all of them slain, fallen by the sword, who went down uncircumcised to the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21273AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21273AK\"></sup>lower parts of the earth, who instilled their terror in the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21273AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21273AL\"></sup>land of the living and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21273AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21273AM\"></sup>bore their disgrace with those who went down to the pit.",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup>They have made a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21274AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21274AN\"></sup>bed for her among the slain with all her hordes. Her graves are around it, they are all uncircumcised, slain by the sword (although their terror was instilled in the land of the living), and they bore their disgrace with those who go down to the pit; they were put in the midst of the slain.",
			"26": "<sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup>“<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21275AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21275AO\"></sup>Meshech, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21275AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21275AP\"></sup>Tubal and all their hordes are there; their graves surround them. All of them were slain by the sword <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21275AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21275AQ\"></sup>uncircumcised, though they instilled their terror in the land of the living.",
			"27": "<sup class=\"versenum\">27 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21276AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21276AR\"></sup>Nor do they lie beside the fallen <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21276AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21276AS\"></sup>heroes of the uncircumcised, who went down to Sheol with their weapons of war and whose swords were laid under their heads; but the punishment for their <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21276AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21276AT\"></sup>iniquity rested on their bones, though the terror of <i>these</i> heroes <i>was once</i> in the land of the living.",
			"28": "<sup class=\"versenum\">28 </sup>But in the midst of the uncircumcised you will be broken and lie with those slain by the sword.",
			"29": "<sup class=\"versenum\">29 </sup>“There also is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21278AU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AU&quot;&gt;AU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21278AU\"></sup>Edom, its kings and all its princes, who for <i>all</i> their might are laid with those slain by the sword; they will lie with the uncircumcised and with those who go down to the pit.",
			"30": "<sup class=\"versenum\">30 </sup>“There also are the chiefs of the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21279AV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AV&quot;&gt;AV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21279AV\"></sup>north, all of them, and all the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21279AW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AW&quot;&gt;AW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21279AW\"></sup>Sidonians, who in spite of the terror resulting from their might, in shame went down with the slain. So they lay down uncircumcised with those slain by the sword and bore their disgrace with those who go down to the pit.",
			"31": "<sup class=\"versenum\">31 </sup>“These Pharaoh will see, and he will be <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21280AX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AX&quot;&gt;AX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21280AX\"></sup>comforted for all his hordes slain by the sword, <i>even</i> Pharaoh and all his army,” declares the Lord <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">God</span>.",
			"32": "<sup class=\"versenum\">32 </sup>“Though I instilled a terror of him in the land of the living, yet he will be made to lie down among <i>the</i> uncircumcised <i>along</i> with those slain by the sword, <i>even</i> Pharaoh and all his hordes,” declares the Lord <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">God</span>."
		},
		"33": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">33 </span>And the word of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> came to me, saying,",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>“Son of man, speak to the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21283A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21283A\"></sup>sons of your people and say to them, ‘If I bring a sword upon a land, and the people of the land take one man from among them and make him their watchman,",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>and he sees the sword coming upon the land and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21284B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21284B\"></sup>blows on the trumpet and warns the people,",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>then he who hears the sound of the trumpet and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21285C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21285C\"></sup>does not take warning, and a sword comes and takes him away, his <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21285D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21285D\"></sup>blood will be on his <i>own</i> head.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>He heard the sound of the trumpet but did not take warning; his blood will be on himself. But had he taken warning, he would have <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21286E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21286E\"></sup>delivered his life.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>But if the watchman sees the sword coming and does not blow the trumpet and the people are not warned, and a sword comes and takes a person from them, he is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21287F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21287F\"></sup>taken away in his iniquity; but his <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21287G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21287G\"></sup>blood I will require from the watchman’s hand.’",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>“Now as for you, son of man, I have <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21288H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21288H\"></sup>appointed you a watchman for the house of Israel; so you will hear a message from My mouth and give them <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21288I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21288I\"></sup>warning from Me.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>When I say to the wicked, ‘O wicked man, you will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21289J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21289J\"></sup>surely die,’ and you do not speak to warn the wicked from his way, that wicked man shall die in his iniquity, but his blood I will require from your hand.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>But if you on your part warn a wicked man to turn from his way and he <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21290K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21290K\"></sup>does not turn from his way, he will die in his iniquity, but you have <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21290L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21290L\"></sup>delivered your life.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>“Now as for you, son of man, say to the house of Israel, ‘Thus you have spoken, saying, “Surely our transgressions and our sins are upon us, and we are <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21291M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21291M\"></sup>rotting away in them; <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21291N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21291N\"></sup>how then can we survive?”’",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>Say to them, ‘<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21292O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21292O\"></sup>As I live!’ declares the Lord <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">God</span>, ‘I take <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21292P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21292P\"></sup>no pleasure in the death of the wicked, but rather that the wicked <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21292Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21292Q\"></sup>turn from his way and live. <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21292R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21292R\"></sup>Turn back, turn back from your evil ways! Why then will you die, O house of Israel?’",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>And you, son of man, say to your fellow citizens, ‘The <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21293S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21293S\"></sup>righteousness of a righteous man will not deliver him in the day of his transgression, and as for the wickedness of the wicked, he will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21293T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21293T\"></sup>not stumble because of it in the day when he turns from his wickedness; whereas a righteous man will not be able to live by his righteousness on the day when he commits sin.’",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>When I say to the righteous he will surely live, and he <i>so</i> trusts in his righteousness that he <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21294U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21294U\"></sup>commits iniquity, none of his righteous deeds will be remembered; but in that same iniquity of his which he has committed he will die.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>But when I say to the wicked, ‘You will surely die,’ and he <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21295V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21295V\"></sup>turns from his sin and practices <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21295W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21295W\"></sup>justice and righteousness,",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup><i>if a</i> wicked man restores a pledge, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21296X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21296X\"></sup>pays back what he has taken by robbery, walks by the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21296Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21296Y\"></sup>statutes which ensure life without committing iniquity, he shall surely live; he shall not die.",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21297Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21297Z\"></sup>None of his sins that he has committed will be remembered against him. He has practiced justice and righteousness; he shall surely live.",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>“Yet your fellow citizens say, ‘The way of the Lord is not right,’ when it is their own way that is not right.",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>When the righteous turns from his righteousness and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21299AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21299AA\"></sup>commits iniquity, then he shall die in it.",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>But when the wicked turns from his wickedness and practices justice and righteousness, he will live by them.",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>Yet you say, ‘<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21301AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21301AB\"></sup>The way of the Lord is not right.’ O house of Israel, I will judge each of you according to his ways.”",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>Now <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21302AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21302AC\"></sup>in the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21302AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21302AD\"></sup>twelfth year of our exile, on the fifth of the tenth month, the refugees from Jerusalem came to me, saying, “<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21302AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21302AE\"></sup>The city has been taken.”",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>Now the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21303AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21303AF\"></sup>hand of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> had been upon me in the evening, before the refugees came. And He <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21303AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21303AG\"></sup>opened my mouth at the time <i>they</i> came to me in the morning; so my mouth was <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21303AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21303AH\"></sup>opened and I was no longer speechless.",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>Then the word of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> came to me saying,",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>“Son of man, they who <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21305AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21305AI\"></sup>live in these waste places in the land of Israel are saying, ‘<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21305AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21305AJ\"></sup>Abraham was <i>only</i> one, yet he possessed the land; so to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21305AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21305AK\"></sup>us who are many the land has been given as a possession.’",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup>Therefore say to them, ‘Thus says the Lord <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">God</span>, “You eat <i>meat</i> with the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21306AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21306AL\"></sup>blood <i>in it</i>, lift up your eyes to your idols as you shed blood. <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21306AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21306AM\"></sup>Should you then possess the land?",
			"26": "<sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup>You <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21307AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21307AN\"></sup>rely on your sword, you commit abominations and each of you defiles his neighbor’s wife. Should you then possess the land?”’",
			"27": "<sup class=\"versenum\">27 </sup>Thus you shall say to them, ‘Thus says the Lord <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">God</span>, “As I live, surely those who are in the waste places will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21308AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21308AO\"></sup>fall by the sword, and whoever is in the open field I will give to the beasts to be devoured, and those who are in the strongholds and in the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21308AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21308AP\"></sup>caves will die of pestilence.",
			"28": "<sup class=\"versenum\">28 </sup>I will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21309AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21309AQ\"></sup>make the land a desolation and a waste, and the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21309AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21309AR\"></sup>pride of her power will cease; and the mountains of Israel will be desolate so that no one will pass through.",
			"29": "<sup class=\"versenum\">29 </sup>Then they will know that I am the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, when I make the land a desolation and a waste because of all their abominations which they have committed.”’",
			"30": "<sup class=\"versenum\">30 </sup>“But as for you, son of man, your fellow citizens who talk about you by the walls and in the doorways of the houses, speak to one another, each to his brother, saying, ‘<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21311AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21311AS\"></sup>Come now and hear what the message is which comes forth from the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.’",
			"31": "<sup class=\"versenum\">31 </sup>They come to you as people come, and sit before you <i>as</i> My people and hear your words, but they do not do them, for they do the lustful desires <i>expressed</i> by their <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21312AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21312AT\"></sup>mouth, <i>and</i> their heart goes after their <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21312AU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AU&quot;&gt;AU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21312AU\"></sup>gain.",
			"32": "<sup class=\"versenum\">32 </sup>Behold, you are to them like a sensual song by one who has a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21313AV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AV&quot;&gt;AV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21313AV\"></sup>beautiful voice and plays well on an instrument; for they hear your words but they do not practice them.",
			"33": "<sup class=\"versenum\">33 </sup>So when it <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21314AW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AW&quot;&gt;AW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21314AW\"></sup>comes to pass—as surely it will—then they will know that a prophet has been in their midst.”"
		},
		"34": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">34 </span>Then the word of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> came to me saying,",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>“Son of man, prophesy against the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21316A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21316A\"></sup>shepherds of Israel. Prophesy and say to those shepherds, ‘Thus says the Lord <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">God</span>, “Woe, shepherds of Israel who have been <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21316B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21316B\"></sup>feeding themselves! Should not the shepherds <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21316C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21316C\"></sup>feed the flock?",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>You <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21317D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21317D\"></sup>eat the fat and clothe yourselves with the wool, you <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21317E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21317E\"></sup>slaughter the fat <i>sheep</i> without feeding the flock.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>Those who are sickly you have not strengthened, the diseased you have not healed, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21318F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21318F\"></sup>the broken you have not bound up, the scattered you have not brought back, nor have you <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21318G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21318G\"></sup>sought for the lost; but with force and with severity you have dominated them.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>They were <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21319H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21319H\"></sup>scattered for lack of a shepherd, and they became <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21319I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21319I\"></sup>food for every beast of the field and were scattered.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>My flock <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21320J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21320J\"></sup>wandered through all the mountains and on every high hill; <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21320K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21320K\"></sup>My flock was scattered over all the surface of the earth, and there was <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21320L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21320L\"></sup>no one to search or seek <i>for them</i>.”’”",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>Therefore, you shepherds, hear the word of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>:",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>“As I live,” declares the Lord <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">God</span>, “surely because My flock has become a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21322M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21322M\"></sup>prey, My flock has even become food for all the beasts of the field for lack of a shepherd, and My shepherds did not search for My flock, but <i>rather</i> the shepherds fed themselves and did not feed My flock;",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>therefore, you shepherds, hear the word of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>:",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>‘Thus says the Lord <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">God</span>, “Behold, I am <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21324N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21324N\"></sup>against the shepherds, and I will demand My sheep from them and make them <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21324O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21324O\"></sup>cease from feeding sheep. So the shepherds will not feed themselves anymore, but I will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21324P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21324P\"></sup>deliver My flock from their mouth, so that they will not be food for them.”’”",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>For thus says the Lord <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">God</span>, “Behold, I Myself will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21325Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21325Q\"></sup>search for My sheep and seek them out.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21326R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21326R\"></sup>As a shepherd cares for his herd in the day when he is among his scattered sheep, so I will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21326S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21326S\"></sup>care for My sheep and will deliver them from all the places to which they were scattered on a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21326T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21326T\"></sup>cloudy and gloomy day.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>I will bring them out from the peoples and gather them from the countries and bring them to their own land; and I will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21327U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21327U\"></sup>feed them on the mountains of Israel, by the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21327V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21327V\"></sup>streams, and in all the inhabited places of the land.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>I will feed them in a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21328W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21328W\"></sup>good pasture, and their grazing ground will be on the mountain heights of Israel. There they will lie down on good grazing ground and feed in <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21328X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21328X\"></sup>rich pasture on the mountains of Israel.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>I will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21329Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21329Y\"></sup>feed My flock and I will lead them to rest,” declares the Lord <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">God</span>.",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>“I will seek the lost, bring back the scattered, bind up the broken and strengthen the sick; but the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21330Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21330Z\"></sup>fat and the strong I will destroy. I will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21330AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21330AA\"></sup>feed them with judgment.",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>“As for you, My flock, thus says the Lord <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">God</span>, ‘Behold, I will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21331AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21331AB\"></sup>judge between one sheep and another, between the rams and the male goats.",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>Is it too <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21332AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21332AC\"></sup>slight a thing for you that you should feed in the good pasture, that you must tread down with your feet the rest of your pastures? Or that you should drink of the clear waters, that you must foul the rest with your feet?",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>As for My flock, they must eat what you tread down with your feet and drink what you foul with your feet!’”",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>Therefore, thus says the Lord <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">God</span> to them, “Behold, I, even I, will judge between the fat sheep and the lean sheep.",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>Because you push with side and with shoulder, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21335AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21335AD\"></sup>thrust at all the weak with your horns until you have scattered them abroad,",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>therefore, I will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21336AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21336AE\"></sup>deliver My flock, and they will no longer be a prey; and I will judge between one sheep and another.",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>“Then I will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21337AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21337AF\"></sup>set over them one <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21337AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21337AG\"></sup>shepherd, My servant <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21337AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21337AH\"></sup>David, and he will feed them; he will feed them himself and be their shepherd.",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>And I, the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, will be their God, and My servant <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21338AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21338AI\"></sup>David will be prince among them; I the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> have spoken.",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup>“I will make a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21339AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21339AJ\"></sup>covenant of peace with them and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21339AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21339AK\"></sup>eliminate harmful beasts from the land so that they may <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21339AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21339AL\"></sup>live securely in the wilderness and sleep in the woods.",
			"26": "<sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup>I will make them and the places around My hill a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21340AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21340AM\"></sup>blessing. And I will cause <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21340AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21340AN\"></sup>showers to come down in their season; they will be showers of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21340AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21340AO\"></sup>blessing.",
			"27": "<sup class=\"versenum\">27 </sup>Also the tree of the field will yield its fruit and the earth will yield its increase, and they will be <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21341AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21341AP\"></sup>secure on their land. Then they will know that I am the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, when I have <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21341AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21341AQ\"></sup>broken the bars of their yoke and have delivered them from the hand of those who enslaved them.",
			"28": "<sup class=\"versenum\">28 </sup>They will no longer be a prey to the nations, and the beasts of the earth will not devour them; but they will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21342AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21342AR\"></sup>live securely, and no one will make <i>them</i> afraid.",
			"29": "<sup class=\"versenum\">29 </sup>I will establish for them a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21343AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21343AS\"></sup>renowned planting place, and they will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21343AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21343AT\"></sup>not again be victims of famine in the land, and they will not <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21343AU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AU&quot;&gt;AU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21343AU\"></sup>endure the insults of the nations anymore.",
			"30": "<sup class=\"versenum\">30 </sup>Then they will know that <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21344AV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AV&quot;&gt;AV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21344AV\"></sup>I, the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> their God, am with them, and that they, the house of Israel, are My people,” declares the Lord <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">God</span>.",
			"31": "<sup class=\"versenum\">31 </sup>“As for you, My <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21345AW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AW&quot;&gt;AW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21345AW\"></sup>sheep, the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21345AX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AX&quot;&gt;AX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21345AX\"></sup>sheep of My pasture, you are men, and I am your God,” declares the Lord <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">God</span>."
		},
		"35": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">35 </span>Moreover, the word of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> came to me saying,",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>“Son of man, set your face against <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21347A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21347A\"></sup>Mount Seir, and prophesy against it",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>and say to it, ‘Thus says the Lord <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">God</span>,“Behold, I am against you, Mount Seir,And I will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21348B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21348B\"></sup>stretch out My hand against youAnd make you a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21348C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21348C\"></sup>desolation and a waste.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>“I will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21349D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21349D\"></sup>lay waste your citiesAnd you will become a desolation.Then you will know that I am the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>Because you have had everlasting <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21350E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21350E\"></sup>enmity and have delivered the sons of Israel to the power of the sword at the time of their calamity, at the time of the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21350F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21350F\"></sup>punishment of the end,",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>therefore as I live,” declares the Lord <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">God</span>, “I will give you over to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21351G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21351G\"></sup>bloodshed, and bloodshed will pursue you; since you have not hated bloodshed, therefore bloodshed will pursue you.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>I will make Mount Seir a waste and a desolation and I will cut off from it the one who passes through and returns.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>I will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21353H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21353H\"></sup>fill its mountains with its slain; on your hills and in your valleys and in all your ravines those slain by the sword will fall.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>I will make you an everlasting <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21354I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21354I\"></sup>desolation and your cities will not be inhabited. Then you will know that I am the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>“Because you have <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21355J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21355J\"></sup>said, ‘These two nations and these two lands will be mine, and we will possess them,’ although the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21355K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21355K\"></sup><span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> was there,",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>therefore as I live,” declares the Lord <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">God</span>, “I will deal <i>with you</i> <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21356L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21356L\"></sup>according to your anger and according to your envy which you showed because of your hatred against them; so I will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21356M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21356M\"></sup>make Myself known among them when I judge you.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>Then you will know that I, the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, have heard all your revilings which you have spoken against the mountains of Israel saying, ‘They are laid desolate; they are <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21357N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21357N\"></sup>given to us for food.’",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>And you have <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21358O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21358O\"></sup>spoken arrogantly against Me and have multiplied your words against Me; <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21358P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21358P\"></sup>I have heard <i>it</i>.”",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>Thus says the Lord <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">God</span>, “As all the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21359Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21359Q\"></sup>earth rejoices, I will make you a desolation.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>As you <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21360R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21360R\"></sup>rejoiced over the inheritance of the house of Israel because it was desolate, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21360S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21360S\"></sup>so I will do to you. You will be a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21360T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21360T\"></sup>desolation, O Mount Seir, and all Edom, all of it. Then they will know that I am the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.”’"
		},
		"36": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">36 </span>“And you, son of man, prophesy to the mountains of Israel and say, ‘O mountains of Israel, hear the word of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>Thus says the Lord <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">God</span>, “Because the enemy has spoken against you, ‘Aha!’ and, ‘The everlasting <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21362A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21362A\"></sup>heights have become our possession,’",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>therefore prophesy and say, ‘Thus says the Lord <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">God</span>, “For good reason they have made you <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21363B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21363B\"></sup>desolate and crushed you from every side, that you would become a possession of the rest of the nations and you have been taken up in the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21363C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21363C\"></sup>talk and the whispering of the people.”’”",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>Therefore, O <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21364D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21364D\"></sup>mountains of Israel, hear the word of the Lord <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">God</span>. Thus says the Lord <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">God</span> to the mountains and to the hills, to the ravines and to the valleys, to the desolate wastes and to the forsaken cities which have become a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21364E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21364E\"></sup>prey and a derision to the rest of the nations which are round about,",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>therefore thus says the Lord <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">God</span>, “Surely in the fire of My <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21365F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21365F\"></sup>jealousy I have spoken against the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21365G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21365G\"></sup>rest of the nations, and against all Edom, who appropriated My land for themselves as a possession with wholehearted <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21365H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21365H\"></sup>joy <i>and</i> with scorn of soul, to drive it out for a prey.”",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>Therefore prophesy concerning the land of Israel and say to the mountains and to the hills, to the ravines and to the valleys, “Thus says the Lord <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">God</span>, ‘Behold, I have spoken in My jealousy and in My wrath because you have <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21366I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21366I\"></sup>endured the insults of the nations.’",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>Therefore thus says the Lord <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">God</span>, ‘I have sworn that surely the nations which are around you will themselves endure their insults.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>But you, O mountains of Israel, you will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21368J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21368J\"></sup>put forth your branches and bear your fruit for My people Israel; for they will soon come.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>For, behold, I am for you, and I will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21369K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21369K\"></sup>turn to you, and you will be <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21369L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21369L\"></sup>cultivated and sown.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>I will multiply men on you, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21370M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21370M\"></sup>all the house of Israel, all of it; and the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21370N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21370N\"></sup>cities will be inhabited and the waste places will be rebuilt.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>I will multiply on you man and beast; and they will increase and be fruitful; and I will cause you to be inhabited as you were <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21371O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21371O\"></sup>formerly and will treat you <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21371P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21371P\"></sup>better than at the first. Thus you will know that I am the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>Yes, I will cause <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21372Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21372Q\"></sup>men—My people Israel—to walk on you and possess you, so that you will become their <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21372R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21372R\"></sup>inheritance and never again <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21372S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21372S\"></sup>bereave them of children.’",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>“Thus says the Lord <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">God</span>, ‘Because they say to you, “You are a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21373T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21373T\"></sup>devourer of men and have bereaved your nation of children,”",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>therefore you will no longer devour men and no longer bereave your nation of children,’ declares the Lord <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">God</span>.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>“I will not let you hear <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21375U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21375U\"></sup>insults from the nations anymore, nor will you bear <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21375V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21375V\"></sup>disgrace from the peoples any longer, nor will you cause your nation to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21375W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21375W\"></sup>stumble any longer,” declares the Lord <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">God</span>.’”",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>Then the word of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> came to me saying,",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>“Son of man, when the house of Israel was living in their own land, they <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21377X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21377X\"></sup>defiled it by their ways and their deeds; their way before Me was like <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21377Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21377Y\"></sup>the uncleanness of a woman in her impurity.",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>Therefore I <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21378Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21378Z\"></sup>poured out My wrath on them for the blood which they had shed on the land, because they had defiled it with their idols.",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>Also I <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21379AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21379AA\"></sup>scattered them among the nations and they were dispersed throughout the lands. <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21379AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21379AB\"></sup>According to their ways and their deeds I judged them.",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>When they came to the nations where they went, they <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21380AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21380AC\"></sup>profaned My holy name, because it was said of them, ‘These are the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21380AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21380AD\"></sup>people of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>; yet they have come out of His land.’",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>But I had concern for My <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21381AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21381AE\"></sup>holy name, which the house of Israel had profaned among the nations where they went.",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>“Therefore say to the house of Israel, ‘Thus says the Lord <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">God</span>, “It is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21382AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21382AF\"></sup>not for your sake, O house of Israel, that I am about to act, but for My holy name, which you have profaned among the nations where you went.",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>I will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21383AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21383AG\"></sup>vindicate the holiness of My great name which has been profaned among the nations, which you have profaned in their midst. Then the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21383AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21383AH\"></sup>nations will know that I am the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>,” declares the Lord <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">God</span>, “when I prove Myself holy among you in their sight.",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>For I will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21384AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21384AI\"></sup>take you from the nations, gather you from all the lands and bring you into your own land.",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup>Then I will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21385AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21385AJ\"></sup>sprinkle clean water on you, and you will be clean; I will cleanse you from all your <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21385AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21385AK\"></sup>filthiness and from all your <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21385AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21385AL\"></sup>idols.",
			"26": "<sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup>Moreover, I will give you a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21386AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21386AM\"></sup>new heart and put a new spirit within you; and I will remove the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21386AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21386AN\"></sup>heart of stone from your flesh and give you a heart of flesh.",
			"27": "<sup class=\"versenum\">27 </sup>I will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21387AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21387AO\"></sup>put My Spirit within you and cause you to walk in My statutes, and you will be careful to observe My ordinances.",
			"28": "<sup class=\"versenum\">28 </sup>You will live in the land that I gave to your forefathers; so you will be <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21388AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21388AP\"></sup>My people, and I will be your God.",
			"29": "<sup class=\"versenum\">29 </sup>Moreover, I will save you from all your uncleanness; and I will call for the grain and multiply it, and I <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21389AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21389AQ\"></sup>will not bring a famine on you.",
			"30": "<sup class=\"versenum\">30 </sup>I will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21390AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21390AR\"></sup>multiply the fruit of the tree and the produce of the field, so that you will not receive again the disgrace of famine among the nations.",
			"31": "<sup class=\"versenum\">31 </sup>Then you will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21391AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21391AS\"></sup>remember your evil ways and your deeds that were not good, and you will loathe yourselves in your own sight for your iniquities and your abominations.",
			"32": "<sup class=\"versenum\">32 </sup>I am not doing <i>this</i> <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21392AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21392AT\"></sup>for your sake,” declares the Lord <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">God</span>, “let it be known to you. Be ashamed and confounded for your ways, O house of Israel!”",
			"33": "<sup class=\"versenum\">33 </sup>‘Thus says the Lord <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">God</span>, “On the day that I cleanse you from all your iniquities, I will cause the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21393AU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AU&quot;&gt;AU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21393AU\"></sup>cities to be inhabited, and the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21393AV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AV&quot;&gt;AV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21393AV\"></sup>waste places will be rebuilt.",
			"34": "<sup class=\"versenum\">34 </sup>The desolate land will be cultivated instead of being a desolation in the sight of everyone who passes by.",
			"35": "<sup class=\"versenum\">35 </sup>They will say, ‘This desolate land has become like the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21395AW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AW&quot;&gt;AW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21395AW\"></sup>garden of Eden; and the waste, desolate and ruined cities are fortified <i>and</i> inhabited.’",
			"36": "<sup class=\"versenum\">36 </sup>Then the nations that are left round about you will know that I, the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, have rebuilt the ruined places <i>and</i> planted that which was desolate; I, the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, have spoken and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21396AX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AX&quot;&gt;AX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21396AX\"></sup>will do it.”",
			"37": "<sup class=\"versenum\">37 </sup>‘Thus says the Lord <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">God</span>, “This also I will let the house of Israel ask Me to do for them: I will increase their men like a flock.",
			"38": "<sup class=\"versenum\">38 </sup>Like the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21398AY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AY&quot;&gt;AY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21398AY\"></sup>flock for sacrifices, like the flock at Jerusalem during her appointed feasts, so will the waste cities be filled with <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21398AZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AZ&quot;&gt;AZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21398AZ\"></sup>flocks of men. Then they will know that I am the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.”’”"
		},
		"37": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">37 </span>The <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21399A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21399A\"></sup>hand of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> was upon me, and He <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21399B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21399B\"></sup>brought me out by the Spirit of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> and set me down in the middle of the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21399C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21399C\"></sup>valley; and it was full of bones.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>He caused me to pass among them round about, and behold, <i>there were</i> very many on the surface of the valley; and lo, <i>they were</i> very dry.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>He said to me, “Son of man, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21401D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21401D\"></sup>can these bones live?” And I answered, “O Lord <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">God</span>, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21401E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21401E\"></sup>You know.”",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>Again He said to me, “<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21402F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21402F\"></sup>Prophesy over these bones and say to them, ‘O dry bones, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21402G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21402G\"></sup>hear the word of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.’",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>Thus says the Lord <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">God</span> to these bones, ‘Behold, I will cause <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21403H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21403H\"></sup>breath to enter you that you may come to life.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>I will put sinews on you, make flesh grow back on you, cover you with skin and put breath in you that you may come alive; and you will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21404I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21404I\"></sup>know that I am the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.’”",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>So I prophesied <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21405J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21405J\"></sup>as I was commanded; and as I prophesied, there was a noise, and behold, a rattling; and the bones came together, bone to its bone.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>And I looked, and behold, sinews were on them, and flesh grew and skin covered them; but there was no breath in them.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>Then He said to me, “Prophesy to the breath, prophesy, son of man, and say to the breath, ‘Thus says the Lord <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">God</span>, “Come from the four winds, O breath, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21407K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21407K\"></sup>breathe on these slain, that they <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21407L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21407L\"></sup>come to life.”’”",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>So I prophesied as He commanded me, and the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21408M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21408M\"></sup>breath came into them, and they came to life and stood on their feet, an <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21408N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21408N\"></sup>exceedingly great army.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>Then He said to me, “Son of man, these bones are the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21409O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21409O\"></sup>whole house of Israel; behold, they say, ‘Our <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21409P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21409P\"></sup>bones are dried up and our hope has perished. We are completely <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21409Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21409Q\"></sup>cut off.’",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>Therefore prophesy and say to them, ‘Thus says the Lord <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">God</span>, “Behold, I will open your graves and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21410R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21410R\"></sup>cause you to come up out of your graves, My people; and I will bring you into the land of Israel.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>Then you will know that I am the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, when I have opened your graves and caused you to come up out of your graves, My people.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>I will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21412S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21412S\"></sup>put My Spirit within you and you will come to life, and I will place you on your own land. Then you will know that I, the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, have spoken and done it,” declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.’”",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>The word of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> came again to me saying,",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>“And you, son of man, take for yourself <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21414T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21414T\"></sup>one stick and write on it, ‘For <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21414U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21414U\"></sup>Judah and for the sons of Israel, his companions’; then take another stick and write on it, ‘For <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21414V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21414V\"></sup>Joseph, the stick of Ephraim and all the house of Israel, his companions.’",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>Then <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21415W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21415W\"></sup>join them for yourself one to another into one stick, that they may become one in your hand.",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>When the sons of your people speak to you saying, ‘Will you not declare to us <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21416X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21416X\"></sup>what you mean by these?’",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>say to them, ‘Thus says the Lord <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">God</span>, “Behold, I will take the stick of Joseph, which is in the hand of Ephraim, and the tribes of Israel, his companions; and I will put them with it, with the stick of Judah, and make them one stick, and they will be one in My hand.”’",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>The sticks on which you write will be in your hand before their eyes.",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>Say to them, ‘Thus says the Lord <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">God</span>, “Behold, I will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21419Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21419Y\"></sup>take the sons of Israel from among the nations where they have gone, and I will gather them from every side and bring them into their own land;",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>and I will make them <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21420Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21420Z\"></sup>one nation in the land, on the mountains of Israel; and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21420AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21420AA\"></sup>one king will be king for all of them; and they will no longer be two nations and no longer be divided into two kingdoms.",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>They will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21421AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21421AB\"></sup>no longer defile themselves with their idols, or with their detestable things, or with any of their transgressions; but <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21421AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21421AC\"></sup>I will deliver them from all their dwelling places in which they have sinned, and will cleanse them. And they will be My people, and I will be their God.",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>“My servant <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21422AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21422AD\"></sup>David will be king over them, and they will all have <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21422AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21422AE\"></sup>one shepherd; and they will walk in My ordinances and keep My statutes and observe them.",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup>They will live on the land that I gave to Jacob My servant, in which your fathers lived; and they will live on it, they, and their sons and their sons’ sons, forever; and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21423AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21423AF\"></sup>David My servant will be their prince forever.",
			"26": "<sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup>I will make a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21424AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21424AG\"></sup>covenant of peace with them; it will be an <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21424AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21424AH\"></sup>everlasting covenant with them. And I will place them and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21424AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21424AI\"></sup>multiply them, and will set My <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21424AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21424AJ\"></sup>sanctuary in their midst forever.",
			"27": "<sup class=\"versenum\">27 </sup>My <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21425AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21425AK\"></sup>dwelling place also will be with them; and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21425AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21425AL\"></sup>I will be their God, and they will be My people.",
			"28": "<sup class=\"versenum\">28 </sup>And the nations will know that I am the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21426AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21426AM\"></sup>who sanctifies Israel, when My sanctuary is in their midst forever.”’”"
		},
		"38": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">38 </span>And the word of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> came to me saying,",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>“Son of man, set your face toward <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21428A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21428A\"></sup>Gog of the land of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21428B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21428B\"></sup>Magog, the prince of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21428C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21428C\"></sup>Rosh, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21428D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21428D\"></sup>Meshech and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21428E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21428E\"></sup>Tubal, and prophesy against him",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>and say, ‘Thus says the Lord <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">God</span>, “Behold, I am against you, O Gog, prince of Rosh, Meshech and Tubal.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>I will turn you about and put hooks into your jaws, and I will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21430F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21430F\"></sup>bring you out, and all your army, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21430G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21430G\"></sup>horses and horsemen, all of them splendidly attired, a great company <i>with</i> buckler and shield, all of them wielding swords;",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21431H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21431H\"></sup>Persia, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21431I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21431I\"></sup>Ethiopia and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21431J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21431J\"></sup>Put with them, all of them <i>with</i> shield and helmet;",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21432K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21432K\"></sup>Gomer with all its troops; <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21432L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21432L\"></sup>Beth-togarmah <i>from</i> the remote parts of the north with all its troops—many peoples with you.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>“<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21433M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21433M\"></sup>Be prepared, and prepare yourself, you and all your companies that are assembled about you, and be a guard for them.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21434N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21434N\"></sup>After many days you will be summoned; in the latter years you will come into the land that is restored from the sword, <i>whose inhabitants</i> have been <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21434O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21434O\"></sup>gathered from many nations to the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21434P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21434P\"></sup>mountains of Israel which had been a continual waste; but its people were brought out from the nations, and they are <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21434Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21434Q\"></sup>living securely, all of them.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>You will go up, you will come <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21435R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21435R\"></sup>like a storm; you will be like a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21435S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21435S\"></sup>cloud covering the land, you and all your troops, and many peoples with you.”",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>‘Thus says the Lord <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">God</span>, “It will come about on that day, that thoughts will come into your mind and you will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21436T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21436T\"></sup>devise an evil plan,",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>and you will say, ‘I will go up against the land of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21437U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21437U\"></sup>unwalled villages. I will go against those who are <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21437V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21437V\"></sup>at rest, that live securely, all of them living without walls and having no bars or gates,",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21438W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21438W\"></sup>capture spoil and to seize plunder, to turn your hand against the waste places which are <i>now</i> inhabited, and against the people who are gathered from the nations, who have acquired cattle and goods, who live at the center of the world.’",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21439X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21439X\"></sup>Sheba and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21439Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21439Y\"></sup>Dedan and the merchants of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21439Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21439Z\"></sup>Tarshish with all its villages will say to you, ‘Have you come to capture spoil? Have you assembled your company to seize plunder, to carry away silver and gold, to take away cattle and goods, to capture great <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21439AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21439AA\"></sup>spoil?’”’",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>“Therefore prophesy, son of man, and say to Gog, ‘Thus says the Lord <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">God</span>, “On that day when My people Israel are <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21440AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21440AB\"></sup>living securely, will you not know <i>it</i>?",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21441AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21441AC\"></sup>You will come from your place out of the remote parts of the north, you and many peoples with you, all of them riding on horses, a great assembly and a mighty army;",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>and you will come up against My people Israel like a cloud to cover the land. It shall come about in the last days that I will bring you against My land, so that the nations may <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21442AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21442AD\"></sup>know Me when I am <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21442AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21442AE\"></sup>sanctified through you before their eyes, O Gog.”",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>‘Thus says the Lord <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">God</span>, “Are you the one of whom I spoke in former days through My servants the prophets of Israel, who <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21443AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21443AF\"></sup>prophesied in those days for <i>many</i> years that I would bring you against them?",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>It will come about on that day, when Gog comes against the land of Israel,” declares the Lord <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">God</span>, “that My fury will mount up in My <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21444AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21444AG\"></sup>anger.",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>In My <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21445AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21445AH\"></sup>zeal and in My blazing wrath I declare <i>that</i> on that day there will surely be a great <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21445AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21445AI\"></sup>earthquake in the land of Israel.",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21446AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21446AJ\"></sup>The fish of the sea, the birds of the heavens, the beasts of the field, all the creeping things that creep on the earth, and all the men who are on the face of the earth will shake at My presence; the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21446AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21446AK\"></sup>mountains also will be thrown down, the steep pathways will collapse and every wall will fall to the ground.",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>I will call for a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21447AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21447AL\"></sup>sword against him on all My mountains,” declares the Lord <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">God</span>. “<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21447AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21447AM\"></sup>Every man’s sword will be against his brother.",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>With pestilence and with blood I will enter into <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21448AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21448AN\"></sup>judgment with him; and I will rain on him and on his troops, and on the many peoples who are with him, a torrential rain, with <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21448AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21448AO\"></sup>hailstones, fire and brimstone.",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>I will magnify Myself, sanctify Myself, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21449AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21449AP\"></sup>make Myself known in the sight of many nations; and they will know that I am the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.”’"
		},
		"39": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">39 </span>“And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21450A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21450A\"></sup>you, son of man, prophesy against Gog and say, ‘Thus says the Lord <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">God</span>, “Behold, I am against you, O Gog, prince of Rosh, Meshech and Tubal;",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>and I will turn you around, drive you on, take you up from the remotest parts of the north and bring you against the mountains of Israel.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>I will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21452B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21452B\"></sup>strike your bow from your left hand and dash down your arrows from your right hand.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>You will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21453C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21453C\"></sup>fall on the mountains of Israel, you and all your troops and the peoples who are with you; I will give you as <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21453D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21453D\"></sup>food to every kind of predatory bird and beast of the field.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>You will fall on the open field; for it is I who have spoken,” declares the Lord <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">God</span>.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>“And I will send <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21455E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21455E\"></sup>fire upon Magog and those who inhabit the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21455F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21455F\"></sup>coastlands in safety; and they will know that I am the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>“My <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21456G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21456G\"></sup>holy name I will make known in the midst of My people Israel; and I will not let My holy name be <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21456H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21456H\"></sup>profaned anymore. And the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21456I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21456I\"></sup>nations will know that I am the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21456J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21456J\"></sup>Holy One in Israel.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>Behold, it is coming and it shall be done,” declares the Lord <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">God</span>. “That is the day of which I have spoken.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>“Then those who inhabit the cities of Israel will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21458K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21458K\"></sup>go out and make <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21458L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21458L\"></sup>fires with the weapons and burn <i>them</i>, both shields and bucklers, bows and arrows, war clubs and spears, and for seven years they will make fires of them.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>They will not take wood from the field or gather firewood from the forests, for they will make fires with the weapons; and they will take the spoil of those who despoiled them and seize the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21459M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21459M\"></sup>plunder of those who plundered them,” declares the Lord <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">God</span>.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>“On that day I will give Gog a burial ground there in Israel, the valley of those who pass by east of the sea, and it will block off those who would pass by. So they will bury Gog there with all his horde, and they will call <i>it</i> the valley of Hamon-gog.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>For seven months the house of Israel will be burying them in order to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21461N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21461N\"></sup>cleanse the land.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>Even all the people of the land will bury <i>them</i>; and it will be to their <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21462O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21462O\"></sup>renown <i>on</i> the day that I <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21462P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21462P\"></sup>glorify Myself,” declares the Lord <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">God</span>.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>“They will set apart men who will constantly pass through the land, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21463Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21463Q\"></sup>burying those who were passing through, even those left on the surface of the ground, in order to cleanse it. At the end of seven months they will make a search.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>As those who pass through the land pass through and anyone sees a man’s bone, then he will set up a marker by it until the buriers have buried it in the valley of Hamon-gog.",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>And even <i>the</i> name of <i>the</i> city will be Hamonah. So they will cleanse the land.”’",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>“As for you, son of man, thus says the Lord <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">God</span>, ‘Speak to every kind of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21466R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21466R\"></sup>bird and to every <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21466S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21466S\"></sup>beast of the field, “Assemble and come, gather from every side to My sacrifice which I am going to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21466T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21466T\"></sup>sacrifice for you, as a great sacrifice on the mountains of Israel, that you may eat flesh and drink blood.",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>You will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21467U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21467U\"></sup>eat the flesh of mighty men and drink the blood of the princes of the earth, as <i>though they were</i> <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21467V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21467V\"></sup>rams, lambs, goats and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21467W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21467W\"></sup>bulls, all of them fatlings of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21467X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21467X\"></sup>Bashan.",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>So you will eat fat until you are glutted, and drink blood until you are drunk, from My sacrifice which I have sacrificed for you.",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>You will be glutted at My table with <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21469Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21469Y\"></sup>horses and charioteers, with mighty men and all the men of war,” declares the Lord <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">God</span>.",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>“And I will set My <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21470Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21470Z\"></sup>glory among the nations; and all the nations will see My judgment which I have executed and My hand which I have laid on them.",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>And the house of Israel will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21471AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21471AA\"></sup>know that I am the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> their God from that day onward.",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>The nations will know that the house of Israel went into exile for their <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21472AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21472AB\"></sup>iniquity because they acted treacherously against Me, and I <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21472AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21472AC\"></sup>hid My face from them; so I gave them into the hand of their adversaries, and all of them fell by the sword.",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21473AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21473AD\"></sup>According to their uncleanness and according to their transgressions I dealt with them, and I hid My face from them.”’”",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup>Therefore thus says the Lord <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">God</span>, “Now I will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21474AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21474AE\"></sup>restore the fortunes of Jacob and have mercy on the whole <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21474AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21474AF\"></sup>house of Israel; and I will be <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21474AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21474AG\"></sup>jealous for My holy name.",
			"26": "<sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup>They will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21475AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21475AH\"></sup>forget their disgrace and all their treachery which they perpetrated against Me, when they <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21475AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21475AI\"></sup>live securely on their <i>own</i> land with <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21475AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21475AJ\"></sup>no one to make <i>them</i> afraid.",
			"27": "<sup class=\"versenum\">27 </sup>When I <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21476AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21476AK\"></sup>bring them back from the peoples and gather them from the lands of their enemies, then I shall be <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21476AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21476AL\"></sup>sanctified through them in the sight of the many nations.",
			"28": "<sup class=\"versenum\">28 </sup>Then they will know that I am the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> their God because I made them go into exile among the nations, and then gathered them <i>again</i> to their own land; and I will leave none of them there any longer.",
			"29": "<sup class=\"versenum\">29 </sup>I will not hide My face from them any longer, for I will have <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21478AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21478AM\"></sup>poured out My Spirit on the house of Israel,” declares the Lord <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">God</span>."
		},
		"40": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">40 </span>In the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21479A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21479A\"></sup>twenty-fifth year of our exile, at the beginning of the year, on the tenth of the month, in the fourteenth year after the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21479B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21479B\"></sup>city was taken, on that same day the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21479C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21479C\"></sup>hand of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> was upon me and He brought me there.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>In the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21480D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21480D\"></sup>visions of God He brought me into the land of Israel and set me on a very <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21480E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21480E\"></sup>high mountain, and on it <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21480F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21480F\"></sup>to the south <i>there was</i> a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21480G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21480G\"></sup>structure like a city.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>So He brought me there; and behold, there was a man whose appearance was like the appearance of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21481H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21481H\"></sup>bronze, with a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21481I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21481I\"></sup>line of flax and a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21481J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21481J\"></sup>measuring rod in his hand; and he was standing in the gateway.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>The man said to me, “<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21482K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21482K\"></sup>Son of man, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21482L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21482L\"></sup>see with your eyes, hear with your ears, and give attention to all that I am going to show you; for you have been brought here in order to show <i>it</i> to you. <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21482M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21482M\"></sup>Declare to the house of Israel all that you see.”",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>And behold, there was a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21483N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21483N\"></sup>wall on the outside of the temple all around, and in the man’s hand was a measuring rod of six cubits, <i>each of which was</i> a cubit and a handbreadth. So he measured the thickness of the wall, one rod; and the height, one rod.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>Then he went to the gate which faced <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21484O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21484O\"></sup>east, went up its steps and measured the threshold of the gate, one rod in width; and the other threshold <i>was</i> one rod in width.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>The <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21485P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21485P\"></sup>guardroom <i>was</i> one rod long and one rod wide; and <i>there were</i> five cubits between the guardrooms. And the threshold of the gate by the porch of the gate facing inward <i>was</i> one rod.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>Then he measured the porch of the gate facing inward, one rod.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>He measured the porch of the gate, eight cubits; and its side pillars, two cubits. And the porch of the gate was faced inward.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>The guardrooms of the gate toward the east <i>numbered</i> three on each side; the three of them had the same measurement. The side pillars also had the same measurement on each side.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>And he measured the width of the gateway, ten cubits, and the length of the gate, thirteen cubits.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup><i>There was</i> a barrier <i>wall</i> one cubit <i>wide</i> in front of the guardrooms on each side; and the guardrooms <i>were</i> six cubits <i>square</i> on each side.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>He measured the gate from the roof of the one guardroom to the roof of the other, a width of twenty-five cubits from <i>one</i> door to <i>the</i> door opposite.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>He made the side pillars sixty cubits <i>high</i>; the gate <i>extended</i> round about to the side pillar of the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21492Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21492Q\"></sup>courtyard.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup><i>From</i> the front of the entrance gate to the front of the inner porch of the gate <i>was</i> fifty cubits.",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup><i>There were</i> <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21494R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21494R\"></sup>shuttered windows <i>looking</i> toward the guardrooms, and toward their side pillars within the gate all around, and likewise for the porches. And <i>there were</i> windows all around inside; and on <i>each</i> side pillar <i>were</i> <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21494S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21494S\"></sup>palm tree ornaments.",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>Then he brought me into the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21495T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21495T\"></sup>outer court, and behold, <i>there were</i> <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21495U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21495U\"></sup>chambers and a pavement made for the court all around; thirty chambers faced the pavement.",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>The pavement (<i>that is</i>, the lower pavement) <i>was</i> by the side of the gates, corresponding to the length of the gates.",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>Then he measured the width from the front of the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21497V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21497V\"></sup>lower gate to the front of the exterior of the inner court, a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21497W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21497W\"></sup>hundred cubits on the east and on the north.",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup><i>As for</i> the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21498X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21498X\"></sup>gate of the outer court which faced the north, he measured its length and its width.",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>It had three <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21499Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21499Y\"></sup>guardrooms on each side; and its <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21499Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21499Z\"></sup>side pillars and its porches had the same measurement as the first gate. Its length <i>was</i> <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21499AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21499AA\"></sup>fifty cubits and the width <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21499AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21499AB\"></sup>twenty-five cubits.",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>Its <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21500AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21500AC\"></sup>windows and its porches and its palm tree ornaments <i>had</i> the same measurements as the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21500AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21500AD\"></sup>gate which faced toward the east; and it was reached by seven <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21500AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21500AE\"></sup>steps, and its porch <i>was</i> in front of them.",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>The inner court had a gate opposite the gate on the north as well as <i>the gate</i> on the east; and he measured a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21501AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21501AF\"></sup>hundred cubits from gate to gate.",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>Then he led me toward the south, and behold, there was a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21502AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21502AG\"></sup>gate toward the south; and he measured its <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21502AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21502AH\"></sup>side pillars and its porches according to those same measurements.",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup>The gate and its porches had <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21503AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21503AI\"></sup>windows all around like those other windows; the length <i>was</i> <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21503AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21503AJ\"></sup>fifty cubits and the width twenty-five cubits.",
			"26": "<sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup><i>There were</i> seven <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21504AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21504AK\"></sup>steps going up to it, and its porches <i>were</i> in front of them; and it had <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21504AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21504AL\"></sup>palm tree ornaments on its side pillars, one on each side.",
			"27": "<sup class=\"versenum\">27 </sup>The inner court had a gate toward the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21505AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21505AM\"></sup>south; and he measured from gate to gate toward the south, a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21505AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21505AN\"></sup>hundred cubits.",
			"28": "<sup class=\"versenum\">28 </sup>Then he brought me to the inner court by the south gate; and he measured the south gate <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21506AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21506AO\"></sup>according to those same measurements.",
			"29": "<sup class=\"versenum\">29 </sup>Its <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21507AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21507AP\"></sup>guardrooms also, its side pillars and its <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21507AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21507AQ\"></sup>porches <i>were</i> according to those same measurements. And the gate and its porches had <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21507AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21507AR\"></sup>windows all around; it <i>was</i> <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21507AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21507AS\"></sup>fifty cubits long and twenty-five cubits wide.",
			"30": "<sup class=\"versenum\">30 </sup><i>There were</i> <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21508AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21508AT\"></sup>porches all around, twenty-five cubits long and five cubits wide.",
			"31": "<sup class=\"versenum\">31 </sup>Its porches <i>were</i> toward the outer court; and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21509AU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AU&quot;&gt;AU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21509AU\"></sup>palm tree ornaments <i>were</i> on its side pillars, and its stairway <i>had</i> eight <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21509AV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AV&quot;&gt;AV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21509AV\"></sup>steps.",
			"32": "<sup class=\"versenum\">32 </sup>He brought me into the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21510AW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AW&quot;&gt;AW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21510AW\"></sup>inner court toward the east. And he measured the gate <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21510AX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AX&quot;&gt;AX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21510AX\"></sup>according to those same measurements.",
			"33": "<sup class=\"versenum\">33 </sup>Its <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21511AY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AY&quot;&gt;AY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21511AY\"></sup>guardrooms also, its side pillars and its porches <i>were</i> according to those same measurements. And the gate and its porches had <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21511AZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AZ&quot;&gt;AZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21511AZ\"></sup>windows all around; it <i>was</i> <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21511BA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BA&quot;&gt;BA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21511BA\"></sup>fifty cubits long and twenty-five cubits wide.",
			"34": "<sup class=\"versenum\">34 </sup>Its <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21512BB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BB&quot;&gt;BB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21512BB\"></sup>porches <i>were</i> toward the outer court; and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21512BC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BC&quot;&gt;BC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21512BC\"></sup>palm tree ornaments <i>were</i> on its side pillars, on each side, and its stairway <i>had</i> eight <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21512BD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BD&quot;&gt;BD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21512BD\"></sup>steps.",
			"35": "<sup class=\"versenum\">35 </sup>Then he brought me to the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21513BE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BE&quot;&gt;BE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21513BE\"></sup>north gate; and he measured <i>it</i> according to those same measurements,",
			"36": "<sup class=\"versenum\">36 </sup><i>with</i> its <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21514BF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BF&quot;&gt;BF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21514BF\"></sup>guardrooms, its side pillars and its <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21514BG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BG&quot;&gt;BG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21514BG\"></sup>porches. And the gate had <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21514BH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BH&quot;&gt;BH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21514BH\"></sup>windows all around; the length <i>was</i> <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21514BI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BI&quot;&gt;BI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21514BI\"></sup>fifty cubits and the width twenty-five cubits.",
			"37": "<sup class=\"versenum\">37 </sup>Its side pillars <i>were</i> toward the outer court; and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21515BJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BJ&quot;&gt;BJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21515BJ\"></sup>palm tree ornaments <i>were</i> on its side pillars on each side, and its stairway had eight <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21515BK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BK&quot;&gt;BK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21515BK\"></sup>steps.",
			"38": "<sup class=\"versenum\">38 </sup>A <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21516BL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BL&quot;&gt;BL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21516BL\"></sup>chamber with its doorway was by the side pillars at the gates; there they <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21516BM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BM&quot;&gt;BM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21516BM\"></sup>rinse the burnt offering.",
			"39": "<sup class=\"versenum\">39 </sup>In the porch of the gate <i>were</i> two <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21517BN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BN&quot;&gt;BN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21517BN\"></sup>tables on each side, on which to slaughter the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21517BO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BO&quot;&gt;BO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21517BO\"></sup>burnt offering, the sin offering and the guilt offering.",
			"40": "<sup class=\"versenum\">40 </sup>On the outer side, as one went up to the gateway toward the north, <i>were</i> two tables; and on the other side of the porch of the gate <i>were</i> two tables.",
			"41": "<sup class=\"versenum\">41 </sup>Four <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21519BP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BP&quot;&gt;BP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21519BP\"></sup>tables <i>were</i> on each side next to the gate; <i>or</i>, eight tables on which they slaughter <i>sacrifices</i>.",
			"42": "<sup class=\"versenum\">42 </sup>For the burnt offering <i>there were</i> four <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21520BQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BQ&quot;&gt;BQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21520BQ\"></sup>tables of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21520BR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BR&quot;&gt;BR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21520BR\"></sup>hewn stone, a cubit and a half long, a cubit and a half wide and one cubit high, on which they lay the instruments with which they slaughter the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21520BS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BS&quot;&gt;BS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21520BS\"></sup>burnt offering and the sacrifice.",
			"43": "<sup class=\"versenum\">43 </sup>The double hooks, one handbreadth in length, were installed in the house all around; and on the tables <i>was</i> the flesh of the offering.",
			"44": "<sup class=\"versenum\">44 </sup>From the outside to the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21522BT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BT&quot;&gt;BT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21522BT\"></sup>inner gate were <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21522BU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BU&quot;&gt;BU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21522BU\"></sup>chambers for the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21522BV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BV&quot;&gt;BV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21522BV\"></sup>singers in the inner court, <i>one of</i> which was at the side of the north gate, with its front toward the south, and one at the side of the south gate facing toward the north.",
			"45": "<sup class=\"versenum\">45 </sup>He said to me, “This is the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21523BW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BW&quot;&gt;BW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21523BW\"></sup>chamber which faces toward the south, <i>intended</i> for the priests who <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21523BX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BX&quot;&gt;BX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21523BX\"></sup>keep charge of the temple;",
			"46": "<sup class=\"versenum\">46 </sup>but the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21524BY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BY&quot;&gt;BY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21524BY\"></sup>chamber which faces toward the north is for the priests who <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21524BZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BZ&quot;&gt;BZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21524BZ\"></sup>keep charge of the altar. These are the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21524CA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CA&quot;&gt;CA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21524CA\"></sup>sons of Zadok, who from the sons of Levi <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21524CB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CB&quot;&gt;CB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21524CB\"></sup>come near to the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> to minister to Him.”",
			"47": "<sup class=\"versenum\">47 </sup>He measured the court, a <i>perfect</i> square, a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21525CC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CC&quot;&gt;CC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21525CC\"></sup>hundred cubits long and a hundred cubits wide; and the altar was in front of the temple.",
			"48": "<sup class=\"versenum\">48 </sup>Then he brought me to the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21526CD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CD&quot;&gt;CD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21526CD\"></sup>porch of the temple and measured <i>each</i> side pillar of the porch, five cubits on each side; and the width of the gate was three cubits on each side.",
			"49": "<sup class=\"versenum\">49 </sup>The length of the porch <i>was</i> twenty cubits and the width eleven cubits; and at the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21527CE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CE&quot;&gt;CE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21527CE\"></sup>stairway by which it was ascended <i>were</i> <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21527CF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CF&quot;&gt;CF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21527CF\"></sup>columns belonging to the side pillars, one on each side."
		},
		"41": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">41 </span>Then he <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21528A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21528A\"></sup>brought me to the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21528B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21528B\"></sup>nave and measured the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21528C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21528C\"></sup>side pillars; six cubits wide on each side <i>was</i> the width of the side pillar.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>The width of the entrance <i>was</i> ten cubits and the sides of the entrance <i>were</i> five cubits on each side. And he measured the length of the nave, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21529D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21529D\"></sup>forty cubits, and the width, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21529E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21529E\"></sup>twenty cubits.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>Then he went <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21530F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21530F\"></sup>inside and measured each <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21530G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21530G\"></sup>side pillar of the doorway, two cubits, and the doorway, six cubits <i>high</i>; and the width of the doorway, seven cubits.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>He measured its length, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21531H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21531H\"></sup>twenty cubits, and the width, twenty cubits, before the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21531I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21531I\"></sup>nave; and he said to me, “This is the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21531J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21531J\"></sup>most holy <i>place</i>.”",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>Then he measured the wall of the temple, six cubits; and the width of the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21532K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21532K\"></sup>side chambers, four cubits, all around about the house on every side.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21533L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21533L\"></sup>The side chambers were in three stories, one above another, and thirty in each story; and the side chambers <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21533M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21533M\"></sup>extended to the wall which <i>stood</i> on their inward side all around, that they might be fastened, and not be fastened into the wall of the temple <i>itself</i>.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>The side chambers surrounding the temple were wider at each successive story. Because the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21534N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21534N\"></sup>structure surrounding the temple went upward by stages on all sides of the temple, therefore the width of the temple <i>increased</i> as it went higher; and thus one went up from the lowest <i>story</i> to the highest by way of the second <i>story</i>.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>I saw also that the house had a raised platform all around; the foundations of the side chambers were a full rod of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21535O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21535O\"></sup>six long cubits <i>in height</i>.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>The thickness of the outer wall of the side chambers <i>was</i> five cubits. But the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21536P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21536P\"></sup>free space between the side chambers belonging to the temple",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>and the <i>outer</i> <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21537Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21537Q\"></sup>chambers <i>was</i> twenty cubits in width all around the temple on every side.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>The doorways of the side chambers toward the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21538R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21538R\"></sup>free space <i>consisted of</i> one doorway toward the north and another doorway toward the south; and the width of the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21538S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21538S\"></sup>free space <i>was</i> five cubits all around.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>The <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21539T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21539T\"></sup>building that <i>was</i> in front of the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21539U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21539U\"></sup>separate area at the side toward the west <i>was</i> seventy cubits wide; and the wall of the building <i>was</i> five cubits thick all around, and its length <i>was</i> ninety cubits.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>Then he measured the temple, a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21540V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21540V\"></sup>hundred cubits long; the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21540W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21540W\"></sup>separate area with the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21540X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21540X\"></sup>building and its walls <i>were</i> also a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21540Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21540Y\"></sup>hundred cubits long.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>Also the width of the front of the temple and <i>that of</i> the separate areas along the east <i>side totaled</i> a hundred cubits.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>He measured the length of the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21542Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21542Z\"></sup>building along the front of the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21542AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21542AA\"></sup>separate area behind it, with a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21542AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21542AB\"></sup>gallery on each side, a hundred cubits; <i>he</i> also <i>measured</i> the inner nave and the porches of the court.",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>The <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21543AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21543AC\"></sup>thresholds, the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21543AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21543AD\"></sup>latticed windows and the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21543AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21543AE\"></sup>galleries round about their <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21543AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21543AF\"></sup>three stories, opposite the threshold, were <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21543AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21543AG\"></sup>paneled with wood all around, and <i>from</i> the ground to the windows (but the windows were covered),",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>over the entrance, and to the inner house, and on the outside, and on all the wall all around inside and outside, by measurement.",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>It was carved with <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21545AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21545AH\"></sup>cherubim and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21545AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21545AI\"></sup>palm trees; and a palm tree was between cherub and cherub, and every cherub had two faces,",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21546AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21546AJ\"></sup>man’s face toward the palm tree on one side and a young <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21546AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21546AK\"></sup>lion’s face toward the palm tree on the other side; they were carved on all the house all around.",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>From the ground to above the entrance <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21547AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21547AL\"></sup>cherubim and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21547AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21547AM\"></sup>palm trees were carved, as well as <i>on</i> the wall of the nave.",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>The <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21548AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21548AN\"></sup>doorposts of the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21548AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21548AO\"></sup>nave were square; as for the front of the sanctuary, the appearance of one doorpost was like that of the other.",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>The <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21549AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21549AP\"></sup>altar <i>was</i> of wood, three cubits high and its length two cubits; its corners, its base and its sides <i>were</i> of wood. And he said to me, “This is the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21549AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21549AQ\"></sup>table that is before the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.”",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>The <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21550AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21550AR\"></sup>nave and the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21550AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21550AS\"></sup>sanctuary each had a double <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21550AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21550AT\"></sup>door.",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>Each of the doors had two leaves, two <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21551AU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AU&quot;&gt;AU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21551AU\"></sup>swinging leaves; two <i>leaves</i> for one door and two leaves for the other.",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup>Also there were carved on them, on the doors of the nave, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21552AV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AV&quot;&gt;AV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21552AV\"></sup>cherubim and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21552AW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AW&quot;&gt;AW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21552AW\"></sup>palm trees like those carved on the walls; and <i>there was</i> a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21552AX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AX&quot;&gt;AX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21552AX\"></sup>threshold of wood on the front of the porch outside.",
			"26": "<sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup><i>There were</i> <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21553AY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AY&quot;&gt;AY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21553AY\"></sup>latticed windows and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21553AZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AZ&quot;&gt;AZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21553AZ\"></sup>palm trees on one side and on the other, on the sides of the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21553BA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BA&quot;&gt;BA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21553BA\"></sup>porch; thus <i>were</i> the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21553BB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BB&quot;&gt;BB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21553BB\"></sup>side chambers of the house and the thresholds."
		},
		"42": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">42 </span>Then he <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21554A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21554A\"></sup>brought me out into the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21554B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21554B\"></sup>outer court, the way <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21554C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21554C\"></sup>toward the north; and he brought me to the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21554D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21554D\"></sup>chamber which <i>was</i> opposite the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21554E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21554E\"></sup>separate area and opposite the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21554F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21554F\"></sup>building toward the north.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>Along the length, <i>which was</i> a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21555G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21555G\"></sup>hundred cubits, <i>was</i> the north door; the width <i>was</i> fifty cubits.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>Opposite the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21556H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21556H\"></sup>twenty <i>cubits</i> which belonged to the inner court, and opposite the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21556I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21556I\"></sup>pavement which belonged to the outer court, <i>was</i> <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21556J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21556J\"></sup>gallery corresponding to gallery in three stories.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>Before the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21557K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21557K\"></sup>chambers <i>was</i> an inner walk ten cubits wide, a way of one <i>hundred</i> cubits; and their openings <i>were</i> on the north.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>Now the upper chambers <i>were</i> smaller because the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21558L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21558L\"></sup>galleries took more <i>space</i> away from them than from the lower and middle ones in the building.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>For they <i>were</i> in <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21559M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21559M\"></sup>three stories and had no pillars like the pillars of the courts; therefore <i>the upper chambers</i> were set back from the ground upward, more than the lower and middle ones.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>As for the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21560N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21560N\"></sup>outer wall by the side of the chambers, toward the outer court facing the chambers, its length <i>was</i> fifty cubits.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>For the length of the chambers which <i>were</i> in the outer court <i>was</i> fifty cubits; and behold, <i>the length of those</i> facing the temple <i>was</i> a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21561O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21561O\"></sup>hundred cubits.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>Below these chambers <i>was</i> the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21562P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21562P\"></sup>entrance on the east side, as one enters them from the outer court.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>In the thickness of the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21563Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21563Q\"></sup>wall of the court toward the east, facing the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21563R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21563R\"></sup>separate area and facing the building, <i>there were</i> <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21563S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21563S\"></sup>chambers.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>The <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21564T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21564T\"></sup>way in front of them <i>was</i> like the appearance of the chambers which <i>were</i> on the north, according to their length so was their width, and all their exits <i>were</i> both according to their arrangements and openings.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>Corresponding to the openings of the chambers which were toward the south was an opening at the head of the way, the way in front of the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21565U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21565U\"></sup>wall toward the east, as one enters them.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>Then he said to me, “The north chambers <i>and</i> the south chambers, which are opposite the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21566V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21566V\"></sup>separate area, they are the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21566W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21566W\"></sup>holy chambers where the priests who are <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21566X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21566X\"></sup>near to the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> shall eat the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21566Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21566Y\"></sup>most holy things. There they shall lay the most holy things, the grain offering, the sin offering and the guilt offering; for the place is holy.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>When the priests enter, then they shall not go out into the outer court from the sanctuary without <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21567Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21567Z\"></sup>laying there their <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21567AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21567AA\"></sup>garments in which they minister, for they are holy. They shall put on other garments; then they shall approach that which is for the people.”",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>Now when he had finished measuring the inner house, he brought me out by the way of the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21568AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21568AB\"></sup>gate which faced toward the east and measured it all around.",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>He measured on the east side with the measuring reed five hundred reeds by the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21569AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21569AC\"></sup>measuring reed.",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>He measured on the north side five hundred reeds by the measuring reed.",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>On the south side he measured five hundred reeds with the measuring reed.",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>He turned to the west side <i>and</i> measured five hundred reeds with the measuring reed.",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>He measured it on the four sides; it had a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21573AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21573AD\"></sup>wall all around, the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21573AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21573AE\"></sup>length five hundred and the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21573AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21573AF\"></sup>width five hundred, to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21573AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21573AG\"></sup>divide between the holy and the profane."
		},
		"43": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">43 </span>Then he led me to the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21574A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21574A\"></sup>gate, the gate facing toward the east;",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>and behold, the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21575B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21575B\"></sup>glory of the God of Israel was coming from the way of the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21575C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21575C\"></sup>east. And His <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21575D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21575D\"></sup>voice was like the sound of many waters; and the earth <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21575E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21575E\"></sup>shone with His glory.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>And <i>it was</i> like the appearance of the vision which I saw, like the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21576F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21576F\"></sup>vision which I saw when He came to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21576G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21576G\"></sup>destroy the city. And the visions <i>were</i> like the vision which I saw by the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21576H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21576H\"></sup>river Chebar; and I <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21576I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21576I\"></sup>fell on my face.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>And the glory of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> came into the house by the way of the gate facing toward the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21577J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21577J\"></sup>east.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>And the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21578K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21578K\"></sup>Spirit lifted me up and brought me into the inner court; and behold, the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21578L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21578L\"></sup>glory of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> filled the house.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>Then I heard one speaking to me from the house, while a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21579M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21579M\"></sup>man was standing beside me.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>He said to me, “Son of man, <i>this is</i> the place of My <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21580N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21580N\"></sup>throne and the place of the soles of My feet, where I will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21580O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21580O\"></sup>dwell among the sons of Israel forever. And the house of Israel will not again defile My holy name, neither they nor their kings, by their harlotry and by the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21580P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21580P\"></sup>corpses of their kings when they die,",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>by setting their threshold by My threshold and their door post beside My door post, with <i>only</i> the wall between Me and them. And they have <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21581Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21581Q\"></sup>defiled My holy name by their abominations which they have committed. So I have consumed them in My anger.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>Now let them <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21582R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21582R\"></sup>put away their harlotry and the corpses of their kings far from Me; and I will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21582S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21582S\"></sup>dwell among them forever.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>“As for you, son of man, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21583T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21583T\"></sup>describe the temple to the house of Israel, that they may be <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21583U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21583U\"></sup>ashamed of their iniquities; and let them measure the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21583V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21583V\"></sup>plan.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>If they are ashamed of all that they have done, make known to them the design of the house, its structure, its <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21584W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21584W\"></sup>exits, its entrances, all its designs, all its statutes, and all its laws. And write <i>it</i> <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21584X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21584X\"></sup>in their sight, so that they may observe its whole design and all its statutes and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21584Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21584Y\"></sup>do them.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>This is the law of the house: its entire area on the top of the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21585Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21585Z\"></sup>mountain all around <i>shall be</i> most holy. Behold, this is the law of the house.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>“And these are the measurements of the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21586AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21586AA\"></sup>altar by cubits (the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21586AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21586AB\"></sup>cubit being a cubit and a handbreadth): the base <i>shall be</i> a cubit and the width a cubit, and its border on its edge round about one span; and this <i>shall be</i> the <i>height</i> of the base of the altar.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>From the base on the ground to the lower <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21587AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21587AC\"></sup>ledge <i>shall be</i> two cubits and the width one cubit; and from the smaller ledge to the larger ledge <i>shall be</i> four cubits and the width one cubit.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>The altar hearth <i>shall be</i> four cubits; and from the altar hearth shall extend upwards four <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21588AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21588AD\"></sup>horns.",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>Now the altar hearth <i>shall be</i> twelve <i>cubits</i> long by twelve wide, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21589AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21589AE\"></sup>square in its four sides.",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>The ledge <i>shall be</i> fourteen <i>cubits</i> long by fourteen wide in its four sides, the border around it <i>shall be</i> half a cubit and its base <i>shall be</i> a cubit round about; and its <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21590AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21590AF\"></sup>steps shall <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21590AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21590AG\"></sup>face the east.”",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>And He said to me, “<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21591AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21591AH\"></sup>Son of man, thus says the Lord <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">God</span>, ‘These are the statutes for the altar on the day it is built, to offer <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21591AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21591AI\"></sup>burnt offerings on it and to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21591AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21591AJ\"></sup>sprinkle blood on it.",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>You shall give to the Levitical priests who are from the offspring of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21592AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21592AK\"></sup>Zadok, who draw <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21592AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21592AL\"></sup>near to Me to minister to Me,’ declares the Lord <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">God</span>, ‘a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21592AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21592AM\"></sup>young bull for a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21592AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21592AN\"></sup>sin offering.",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>You shall take some of its blood and put it on its four <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21593AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21593AO\"></sup>horns and on the four corners of the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21593AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21593AP\"></sup>ledge and on the border round about; thus you shall <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21593AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21593AQ\"></sup>cleanse it and make atonement for it.",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>You shall also take the bull for the sin offering, and it <i>shall be</i> <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21594AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21594AR\"></sup>burned in the appointed place of the house, outside the sanctuary.",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>‘On the second day you shall offer a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21595AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21595AS\"></sup>male goat without blemish for a sin offering, and they shall <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21595AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21595AT\"></sup>cleanse the altar as they cleansed <i>it</i> with the bull.",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>When you have finished cleansing <i>it</i>, you shall present a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21596AU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AU&quot;&gt;AU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21596AU\"></sup>young bull without blemish and a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21596AV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AV&quot;&gt;AV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21596AV\"></sup>ram without blemish from the flock.",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>You shall present them before the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, and the priests shall throw <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21597AW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AW&quot;&gt;AW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21597AW\"></sup>salt on them, and they shall offer them up as a burnt offering to the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21598AX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AX&quot;&gt;AX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21598AX\"></sup>For seven days you shall prepare daily a goat for a sin offering; also a young bull and a ram from the flock, without blemish, shall be prepared.",
			"26": "<sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup>For seven days they shall make atonement for the altar and purify it; so shall they consecrate it.",
			"27": "<sup class=\"versenum\">27 </sup>When they have completed the days, it shall be that on the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21600AY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AY&quot;&gt;AY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21600AY\"></sup>eighth day and onward, the priests shall offer your burnt offerings on the altar, and your <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21600AZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AZ&quot;&gt;AZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21600AZ\"></sup>peace offerings; and I will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21600BA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BA&quot;&gt;BA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21600BA\"></sup>accept you,’ declares the Lord <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">God</span>.”"
		},
		"44": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">44 </span>Then He brought me back by the way of the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21601A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21601A\"></sup>outer gate of the sanctuary, which faces the east; and it was shut.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>The <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> said to me, “This gate shall be shut; it shall not be opened, and no one shall enter by it, for the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21602B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21602B\"></sup><span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> God of Israel has entered by it; therefore it shall be shut.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>As for the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21603C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21603C\"></sup>prince, he shall sit in it as prince to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21603D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21603D\"></sup>eat bread before the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>; he shall <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21603E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21603E\"></sup>enter by way of the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21603F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21603F\"></sup>porch of the gate and shall go out by the same way.”",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>Then He brought me by way of the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21604G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21604G\"></sup>north gate to the front of the house; and I looked, and behold, the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21604H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21604H\"></sup>glory of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> filled the house of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, and I <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21604I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21604I\"></sup>fell on my face.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>The <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> said to me, “Son of man, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21605J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21605J\"></sup>mark well, see with your eyes and hear with your ears all that I say to you concerning all the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21605K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21605K\"></sup>statutes of the house of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> and concerning all its laws; and mark well the entrance of the house, with all exits of the sanctuary.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>You shall say to the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21606L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21606L\"></sup>rebellious ones, to the house of Israel, ‘Thus says the Lord <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">God</span>, “<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21606M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21606M\"></sup>Enough of all your abominations, O house of Israel,",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>when you brought in <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21607N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21607N\"></sup>foreigners, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21607O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21607O\"></sup>uncircumcised in heart and uncircumcised in flesh, to be in My sanctuary to profane it, <i>even</i> My house, when you <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21607P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21607P\"></sup>offered My food, the fat and the blood; for they <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21607Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21607Q\"></sup>made My covenant void—<i>this</i> in addition to all your abominations.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>And you have not <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21608R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21608R\"></sup>kept charge of My holy things yourselves, but you have set <i>foreigners</i> to keep charge of My sanctuary.”",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>‘Thus says the Lord <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">God</span>, “<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21609S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21609S\"></sup>No foreigner uncircumcised in heart and uncircumcised in flesh, of all the foreigners who are among the sons of Israel, shall enter My sanctuary.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>But the Levites who went far from Me when Israel went astray, who <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21610T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21610T\"></sup>went astray from Me after their idols, shall <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21610U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21610U\"></sup>bear the punishment for their iniquity.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>Yet they shall be <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21611V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21611V\"></sup>ministers in My sanctuary, having <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21611W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21611W\"></sup>oversight at the gates of the house and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21611X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21611X\"></sup>ministering in the house; they shall <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21611Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21611Y\"></sup>slaughter the burnt offering and the sacrifice for the people, and they shall <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21611Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21611Z\"></sup>stand before them to minister to them.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>Because they ministered to them <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21612AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21612AA\"></sup>before their idols and became a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21612AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21612AB\"></sup>stumbling block of iniquity to the house of Israel, therefore I have <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21612AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21612AC\"></sup>sworn against them,” declares the Lord <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">God</span>, “that they shall <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21612AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21612AD\"></sup>bear <i>the punishment for</i> their iniquity.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>And they shall <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21613AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21613AE\"></sup>not come near to Me to serve as a priest to Me, nor come near to any of My holy things, to the things that are most holy; but they will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21613AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21613AF\"></sup>bear their shame and their abominations which they have committed.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>Yet I will appoint them to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21614AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21614AG\"></sup>keep charge of the house, of all its service and of all that shall be done in it.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>“But the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21615AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21615AH\"></sup>Levitical priests, the sons of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21615AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21615AI\"></sup>Zadok, who <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21615AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21615AJ\"></sup>kept charge of My sanctuary when the sons of Israel <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21615AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21615AK\"></sup>went astray from Me, shall come near to Me to minister to Me; and they shall <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21615AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21615AL\"></sup>stand before Me to offer Me the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21615AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21615AM\"></sup>fat and the blood,” declares the Lord <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">God</span>.",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>“They shall <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21616AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21616AN\"></sup>enter My sanctuary; they shall come near to My <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21616AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21616AO\"></sup>table to minister to Me and keep My charge.",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>It shall be that when they enter at the gates of the inner court, they shall be clothed with <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21617AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21617AP\"></sup>linen garments; and wool shall not be on them while they are ministering in the gates of the inner court and in the house.",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>Linen <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21618AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21618AQ\"></sup>turbans shall be on their heads and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21618AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21618AR\"></sup>linen undergarments shall be on their loins; they shall not gird themselves with <i>anything which makes them</i> sweat.",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>When they go out into the outer court, into the outer court to the people, they shall <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21619AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21619AS\"></sup>put off their garments in which they have been ministering and lay them in the holy chambers; then they shall put on other garments so that they will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21619AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21619AT\"></sup>not transmit holiness to the people with their garments.",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>Also they shall <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21620AU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AU&quot;&gt;AU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21620AU\"></sup>not shave their heads, yet they shall not <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21620AV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AV&quot;&gt;AV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21620AV\"></sup>let their locks grow long; they shall only trim <i>the hair of</i> their heads.",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21621AW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AW&quot;&gt;AW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21621AW\"></sup>Nor shall any of the priests drink wine when they enter the inner court.",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>And they shall not marry a widow or a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21622AX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AX&quot;&gt;AX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21622AX\"></sup>divorced woman but shall <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21622AY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AY&quot;&gt;AY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21622AY\"></sup>take virgins from the offspring of the house of Israel, or a widow who is the widow of a priest.",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>Moreover, they shall teach My people <i>the</i> <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21623AZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AZ&quot;&gt;AZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21623AZ\"></sup><i>difference</i> between the holy and the profane, and cause them to discern between the unclean and the clean.",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>In a dispute <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21624BA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BA&quot;&gt;BA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21624BA\"></sup>they shall take their stand to judge; they shall judge it according to My ordinances. They shall also keep My laws and My statutes in all My <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21624BB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BB&quot;&gt;BB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21624BB\"></sup>appointed feasts and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21624BC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BC&quot;&gt;BC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21624BC\"></sup>sanctify My sabbaths.",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21625BD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BD&quot;&gt;BD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21625BD\"></sup>They shall not go to a dead person to defile <i>themselves</i>; however, for father, for mother, for son, for daughter, for brother, or for a sister who has not had a husband, they may defile themselves.",
			"26": "<sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup>After he is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21626BE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BE&quot;&gt;BE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21626BE\"></sup>cleansed, seven days shall elapse for him.",
			"27": "<sup class=\"versenum\">27 </sup>On the day that he goes into the sanctuary, into the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21627BF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BF&quot;&gt;BF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21627BF\"></sup>inner court to minister in the sanctuary, he shall offer his <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21627BG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BG&quot;&gt;BG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21627BG\"></sup>sin offering,” declares the Lord <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">God</span>.",
			"28": "<sup class=\"versenum\">28 </sup>“And it shall be with regard to an inheritance for them, <i>that</i> <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21628BH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BH&quot;&gt;BH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21628BH\"></sup>I am their inheritance; and you shall give them no possession in Israel—I am their possession.",
			"29": "<sup class=\"versenum\">29 </sup>They shall <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21629BI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BI&quot;&gt;BI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21629BI\"></sup>eat the grain offering, the sin offering and the guilt offering; and every <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21629BJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BJ&quot;&gt;BJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21629BJ\"></sup>devoted thing in Israel shall be theirs.",
			"30": "<sup class=\"versenum\">30 </sup>The first of all the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21630BK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BK&quot;&gt;BK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21630BK\"></sup>first fruits of every kind and every contribution of every kind, from all your contributions, shall be for the priests; you shall also give to the priest the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21630BL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BL&quot;&gt;BL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21630BL\"></sup>first of your dough to cause a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21630BM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BM&quot;&gt;BM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21630BM\"></sup>blessing to rest on your house.",
			"31": "<sup class=\"versenum\">31 </sup>The priests shall not eat any bird or beast that has <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21631BN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BN&quot;&gt;BN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21631BN\"></sup>died a natural death or has been torn to pieces."
		},
		"45": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">45 </span>“And when you <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21632A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21632A\"></sup>divide by lot the land for inheritance, you shall offer an <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21632B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21632B\"></sup>allotment to the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21632C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21632C\"></sup>holy portion of the land; the length shall be the length of 25,000 <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21632D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21632D\"></sup><i>cubits</i>, and the width shall be 20,000. It shall be holy within all its boundary round about.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>Out of this there shall be for the holy place a square round about <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21633E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21633E\"></sup>five hundred by five hundred <i>cubits</i>, and fifty cubits for its <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21633F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21633F\"></sup>open space round about.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>From this area you shall measure a length of 25,000 <i>cubits</i> and a width of 10,000 <i>cubits</i>; and in it shall be the sanctuary, the most holy place.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>It shall be the holy portion of the land; it shall be for the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21635G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21635G\"></sup>priests, the ministers of the sanctuary, who <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21635H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21635H\"></sup>come near to minister to the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, and it shall be a place for their houses and a holy place for the sanctuary.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup><i>An area</i> <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21636I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21636I\"></sup>25,000 <i>cubits</i> in length and 10,000 in width shall be for the Levites, the ministers of the house, <i>and</i> for their possession cities to dwell in.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>“You shall give the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21637J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21637J\"></sup>city possession of <i>an area</i> 5,000 <i>cubits</i> wide and 25,000 <i>cubits</i> long, alongside the allotment of the holy portion; it shall be for the whole house of Israel.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>“The <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21638K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21638K\"></sup>prince shall have <i>land</i> on either side of the holy allotment and the property of the city, adjacent to the holy allotment and the property of the city, on the west side toward the west and on the east side toward the east, and in length comparable to one of the portions, from the west border to the east border.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>This shall be his land for a possession in Israel; so My princes shall no longer <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21639L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21639L\"></sup>oppress My people, but they shall give <i>the rest of</i> the land to the house of Israel <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21639M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21639M\"></sup>according to their tribes.”",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>‘Thus says the Lord <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">God</span>, “<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21640N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21640N\"></sup>Enough, you princes of Israel; put away <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21640O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21640O\"></sup>violence and destruction, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21640P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21640P\"></sup>practice justice and righteousness. Stop your <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21640Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21640Q\"></sup>expropriations from My people,” declares the Lord <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">God</span>.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>“You shall have <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21641R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21641R\"></sup>just balances, a just <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21641S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21641S\"></sup>ephah and a just <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21641T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21641T\"></sup>bath.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>The ephah and the bath shall be the same quantity, so that the bath will contain a tenth of a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21642U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21642U\"></sup>homer and the ephah a tenth of a homer; their standard shall be according to the homer.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>The <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21643V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21643V\"></sup>shekel shall be twenty <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21643W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21643W\"></sup>gerahs; twenty shekels, twenty-five shekels, <i>and</i> fifteen shekels shall be your maneh.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>“This is the offering that you shall offer: a sixth of an ephah from a homer of wheat; a sixth of an ephah from a homer of barley;",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>and the prescribed portion of oil (<i>namely</i>, the bath of oil), a tenth of a bath from <i>each</i> kor (<i>which is</i> ten baths <i>or</i> a homer, for ten baths are a homer);",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>and one sheep from <i>each</i> flock of two hundred from the watering places of Israel—for a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21646X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21646X\"></sup>grain offering, for a burnt offering and for peace offerings, to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21646Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21646Y\"></sup>make atonement for them,” declares the Lord <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">God</span>.",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>“<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21647Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21647Z\"></sup>All the people of the land shall give to this offering for the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21647AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21647AA\"></sup>prince in Israel.",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>It shall be the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21648AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21648AB\"></sup>prince’s part <i>to provide</i> the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21648AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21648AC\"></sup>burnt offerings, the grain offerings and the drink offerings, at the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21648AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21648AD\"></sup>feasts, on the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21648AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21648AE\"></sup>new moons and on the sabbaths, at all the appointed feasts of the house of Israel; he shall provide the sin offering, the grain offering, the burnt offering and the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21648AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21648AF\"></sup>peace offerings, to make atonement for the house of Israel.”",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>‘Thus says the Lord <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">God</span>, “In the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21649AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21649AG\"></sup>first <i>month</i>, on the first of the month, you shall take a young bull <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21649AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21649AH\"></sup>without blemish and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21649AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21649AI\"></sup>cleanse the sanctuary.",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>The priest shall take some of the blood from the sin offering and put <i>it</i> on the door posts of the house, on the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21650AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21650AJ\"></sup>four corners of the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21650AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21650AK\"></sup>ledge of the altar and on the posts of the gate of the inner court.",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>Thus you shall do on the seventh <i>day</i> of the month for everyone who goes <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21651AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21651AL\"></sup>astray or is naive; so you shall make <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21651AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21651AM\"></sup>atonement for the house.",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>“In the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21652AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21652AN\"></sup>first <i>month</i>, on the fourteenth day of the month, you shall have the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21652AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21652AO\"></sup>Passover, a feast of seven days; unleavened bread shall be eaten.",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>On that day the prince shall provide for himself and all the people of the land a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21653AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21653AP\"></sup>bull for a sin offering.",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup><i>During</i> the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21654AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21654AQ\"></sup>seven days of the feast he shall provide as a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21654AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21654AR\"></sup>burnt offering to the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21654AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21654AS\"></sup>seven bulls and seven rams without blemish on every day of the seven days, and a male goat daily for a sin offering.",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>He shall provide as a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21655AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21655AT\"></sup>grain offering an ephah with a bull, an ephah with a ram and a hin of oil with an ephah.",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup>In the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21656AU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AU&quot;&gt;AU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21656AU\"></sup>seventh <i>month</i>, on the fifteenth day of the month, at the feast, he shall provide like this, seven days for the sin offering, the burnt offering, the grain offering and the oil.”"
		},
		"46": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">46 </span>‘Thus says the Lord <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">God</span>, “The <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21657A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21657A\"></sup>gate of the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21657B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21657B\"></sup>inner court facing east shall be <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21657C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21657C\"></sup>shut the six <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21657D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21657D\"></sup>working days; but it shall be opened on the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21657E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21657E\"></sup>sabbath day and opened on the day of the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21657F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21657F\"></sup>new moon.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>The <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21658G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21658G\"></sup>prince shall enter by way of the porch of the gate from outside and stand by the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21658H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21658H\"></sup>post of the gate. Then the priests shall provide his burnt offering and his peace offerings, and he shall worship at the threshold of the gate and then go out; but the gate shall not be <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21658I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21658I\"></sup>shut until the evening.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>The <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21659J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21659J\"></sup>people of the land shall also worship at the doorway of that gate before the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> on the sabbaths and on the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21659K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21659K\"></sup>new moons.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>The <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21660L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21660L\"></sup>burnt offering which the prince shall offer to the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> on the sabbath day shall be <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21660M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21660M\"></sup>six lambs without blemish and a ram without blemish;",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>and the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21661N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21661N\"></sup>grain offering shall be an ephah with the ram, and the grain offering with the lambs as much as he is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21661O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21661O\"></sup>able to give, and a hin of oil with an ephah.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>On the day of the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21662P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21662P\"></sup>new moon <i>he shall offer</i> a young bull without blemish, also six lambs and a ram, <i>which</i> shall be without blemish.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>And he shall provide a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21663Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21663Q\"></sup>grain offering, an ephah with the bull and an ephah with the ram, and with the lambs as much as he is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21663R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21663R\"></sup>able, and a hin of oil with an ephah.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>When the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21664S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21664S\"></sup>prince enters, he shall go in by way of the porch of the gate and go out by the same way.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>But when the people of the land come <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21665T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21665T\"></sup>before the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> at the appointed feasts, he who enters by way of the north gate to worship shall go out by way of the south gate. And he who enters by way of the south gate shall go out by way of the north gate. No one shall return by way of the gate by which he entered but shall go straight out.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>When they go in, the prince shall go in <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21666U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21666U\"></sup>among them; and when they go out, he shall go out.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>“At the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21667V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21667V\"></sup>festivals and the appointed feasts the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21667W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21667W\"></sup>grain offering shall be an ephah with a bull and an ephah with a ram, and with the lambs as much as one is able to give, and a hin of oil with an ephah.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>When the prince provides a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21668X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21668X\"></sup>freewill offering, a burnt offering, or peace offerings <i>as</i> a freewill offering to the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, the gate facing east shall be <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21668Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21668Y\"></sup>opened for him. And he shall provide his burnt offering and his peace offerings as he does on the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21668Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21668Z\"></sup>sabbath day. Then he shall go out, and the gate shall be shut after he goes out.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>“And you shall provide a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21669AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21669AA\"></sup>lamb a year old without blemish for a burnt offering to the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> daily; <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21669AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21669AB\"></sup>morning by morning you shall provide it.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>Also you shall provide a grain offering with it morning by morning, a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21670AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21670AC\"></sup>sixth of an ephah and a third of a hin of oil to moisten the fine flour, a grain offering to the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> continually by a perpetual ordinance.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>Thus they shall provide the lamb, the grain offering and the oil, morning by morning, for a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21671AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21671AD\"></sup>continual burnt offering.”",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>‘Thus says the Lord <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">God</span>, “If the prince gives a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21672AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21672AE\"></sup>gift <i>out of</i> his inheritance to any of his sons, it shall belong to his sons; it is their possession by inheritance.",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>But if he gives a gift from his inheritance to one of his servants, it shall be his until the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21673AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21673AF\"></sup>year of liberty; then it shall return to the prince. His inheritance <i>shall be</i> only his sons’; it shall belong to them.",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>The prince shall <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21674AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21674AG\"></sup>not take from the people’s inheritance, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21674AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21674AH\"></sup>thrusting them out of their possession; he shall give his sons inheritance from his own possession so that My people will not be scattered, anyone from his possession.”’”",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>Then he brought me through the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21675AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21675AI\"></sup>entrance, which <i>was</i> at the side of the gate, into the holy chambers for the priests, which faced north; and behold, there <i>was</i> a place at the extreme rear toward the west.",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>He said to me, “This is the place where the priests shall boil the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21676AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21676AJ\"></sup>guilt offering and the sin offering <i>and</i> where they shall <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21676AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21676AK\"></sup>bake the grain offering, in order that they may not bring <i>them</i> out into the outer court to transmit holiness to the people.”",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>Then he brought me out into the outer court and led me across to the four corners of the court; and behold, in every corner of the court <i>there was</i> a <i>small</i> court.",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>In the four corners of the court <i>there were</i> enclosed courts, forty <i>cubits</i> long and thirty wide; these four in the corners <i>were</i> the same size.",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup><i>There was</i> a row <i>of masonry</i> round about in them, around the four of them, and boiling places were made under the rows round about.",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>Then he said to me, “These are the boiling places where the ministers of the house shall boil the sacrifices of the people.”"
		},
		"47": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">47 </span>Then he brought me back to the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21681A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21681A\"></sup>door of the house; and behold, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21681B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21681B\"></sup>water was flowing from under the threshold of the house toward the east, for the house faced east. And the water was flowing down from under, from the right side of the house, from south of the altar.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>He brought me out by way of the north gate and led me around on the outside to the outer gate by way of <i>the gate</i> that faces east. And behold, water was trickling from the south side.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>When the man went out toward the east with a line in his hand, he measured a thousand cubits, and he led me through the water, water <i>reaching</i> the ankles.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>Again he measured a thousand and led me through the water, water <i>reaching</i> the knees. Again he measured a thousand and led me through <i>the water</i>, water <i>reaching</i> the loins.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>Again he measured a thousand; <i>and it was</i> a river that I could not ford, for the water had risen, <i>enough</i> water to swim in, a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21685C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21685C\"></sup>river that could not be forded.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>He said to me, “Son of man, have you <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21686D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21686D\"></sup>seen <i>this</i>?” Then he brought me back to the bank of the river.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>Now when I had returned, behold, on the bank of the river there <i>were</i> very many <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21687E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21687E\"></sup>trees on the one side and on the other.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>Then he said to me, “These waters go out toward the eastern region and go down into the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21688F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21688F\"></sup>Arabah; then they go toward the sea, being made to flow into the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21688G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21688G\"></sup>sea, and the waters <i>of the sea</i> become fresh.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>It will come about that every living creature which swarms in every place where the river goes, will live. And there will be very many fish, for these waters go there and <i>the others</i> become fresh; so <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21689H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21689H\"></sup>everything will live where the river goes.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>And it will come about that <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21690I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21690I\"></sup>fishermen will stand beside it; from <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21690J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21690J\"></sup>Engedi to Eneglaim there will be a place for the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21690K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21690K\"></sup>spreading of nets. Their fish will be according to their kinds, like the fish of the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21690L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21690L\"></sup>Great Sea, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21690M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21690M\"></sup>very many.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>But its swamps and marshes will not become fresh; they will be left for <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21691N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21691N\"></sup>salt.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21692O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21692O\"></sup>By the river on its bank, on one side and on the other, will grow all <i>kinds of</i> <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21692P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21692P\"></sup>trees for food. Their <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21692Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21692Q\"></sup>leaves will not wither and their fruit will not fail. They will bear every month because their water flows from the sanctuary, and their fruit will be for food and their <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21692R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21692R\"></sup>leaves for healing.”",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>Thus says the Lord <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">God</span>, “This <i>shall be</i> the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21693S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21693S\"></sup>boundary by which you shall divide the land for an inheritance among the twelve tribes of Israel; Joseph <i>shall have</i> two <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21693T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21693T\"></sup>portions.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>You shall divide it for an inheritance, each one equally with the other; for I <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21694U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21694U\"></sup>swore to give it to your forefathers, and this land shall fall to you as an inheritance.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>“This <i>shall be</i> the boundary of the land: on the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21695V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21695V\"></sup>north side, from the Great Sea <i>by</i> the way of Hethlon, to the entrance of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21695W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21695W\"></sup>Zedad;",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21696X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21696X\"></sup>Hamath, Berothah, Sibraim, which is between the border of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21696Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21696Y\"></sup>Damascus and the border of Hamath; Hazer-hatticon, which is by the border of Hauran.",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>The boundary shall extend from the sea <i>to</i> <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21697Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21697Z\"></sup>Hazar-enan <i>at</i> the border of Damascus, and on the north toward the north is the border of Hamath. This is the north side.",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>“The <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21698AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21698AA\"></sup>east side, from between Hauran, Damascus, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21698AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21698AB\"></sup>Gilead and the land of Israel, <i>shall be</i> the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21698AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21698AC\"></sup>Jordan; from the <i>north</i> border to the eastern sea you shall measure. This is the east side.",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>“The <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21699AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21699AD\"></sup>south side toward the south <i>shall extend</i> from <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21699AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21699AE\"></sup>Tamar as far as the waters of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21699AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21699AF\"></sup>Meribath-kadesh, to the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21699AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21699AG\"></sup>brook <i>of Egypt and</i> to the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21699AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21699AH\"></sup>Great Sea. This is the south side toward the south.",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>“The <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21700AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21700AI\"></sup>west side <i>shall be</i> the Great Sea, from the <i>south</i> border to a point opposite <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21700AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21700AJ\"></sup>Lebo-hamath. This is the west side.",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>“So you shall divide this land among yourselves according to the tribes of Israel.",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>You shall divide it by <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21702AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21702AK\"></sup>lot for an inheritance among yourselves and among the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21702AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21702AL\"></sup>aliens who stay in your midst, who bring forth sons in your midst. And they shall be to you as the native-born among the sons of Israel; they shall be allotted an <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21702AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21702AM\"></sup>inheritance with you among the tribes of Israel.",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>And in the tribe with which the alien stays, there you shall give <i>him</i> his inheritance,” declares the Lord <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">God</span>."
		},
		"48": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">48 </span>“Now <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21704A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21704A\"></sup>these are the names of the tribes: from the northern extremity, beside the way of Hethlon to Lebo-hamath, <i>as far as</i> Hazar-enan <i>at</i> the border of Damascus, toward the north beside Hamath, running from east to west, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21704B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21704B\"></sup>Dan, one <i>portion</i>.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>Beside the border of Dan, from the east side to the west side, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21705C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21705C\"></sup>Asher, one <i>portion</i>.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>Beside the border of Asher, from the east side to the west side, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21706D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21706D\"></sup>Naphtali, one <i>portion</i>.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>Beside the border of Naphtali, from the east side to the west side, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21707E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21707E\"></sup>Manasseh, one <i>portion</i>.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>Beside the border of Manasseh, from the east side to the west side, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21708F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21708F\"></sup>Ephraim, one <i>portion</i>.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>Beside the border of Ephraim, from the east side to the west side, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21709G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21709G\"></sup>Reuben, one <i>portion</i>.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>Beside the border of Reuben, from the east side to the west side, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21710H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21710H\"></sup>Judah, one <i>portion</i>.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>“And beside the border of Judah, from the east side to the west side, shall be the allotment which you shall set apart, 25,000 <i>cubits</i> in width, and in length like one of the portions, from the east side to the west side; and the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21711I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21711I\"></sup>sanctuary shall be in the middle of it.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>The allotment that you shall set apart to the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> <i>shall be</i> 25,000 <i>cubits</i> in length and 10,000 in width.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>The holy allotment shall be for these, <i>namely</i> for the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21713J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21713J\"></sup>priests, toward the north 25,000 <i>cubits in length</i>, toward the west 10,000 in width, toward the east 10,000 in width, and toward the south 25,000 in length; and the sanctuary of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> shall be in its midst.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup><i>It shall be</i> for the priests who are sanctified of the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21714K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21714K\"></sup>sons of Zadok, who have kept My charge, who did not go astray when the sons of Israel went astray as the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21714L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21714L\"></sup>Levites went astray.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>It shall be an allotment to them from the allotment of the land, a most holy place, by the border of the Levites.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>Alongside the border of the priests the Levites <i>shall have</i> 25,000 <i>cubits</i> in length and 10,000 in width. The whole length <i>shall be</i> 25,000 <i>cubits</i> and the width 10,000.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>Moreover, they <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21717M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21717M\"></sup>shall not sell or exchange any of it, or alienate this choice <i>portion</i> of land; for it is holy to the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>“The remainder, 5,000 <i>cubits</i> in width and 25,000 in length, shall be for <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21718N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21718N\"></sup>common use for the city, for dwellings and for open spaces; and the city shall be in its midst.",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>These <i>shall be</i> its measurements: the north side 4,500 <i>cubits</i>, the south side <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21719O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21719O\"></sup>4,500 <i>cubits</i>, the east side 4,500 <i>cubits</i>, and the west side 4,500 <i>cubits</i>.",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>The city shall have open spaces: on the north 250 <i>cubits</i>, on the south 250 <i>cubits</i>, on the east 250 <i>cubits</i>, and on the west 250 <i>cubits</i>.",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>The remainder of the length alongside the holy allotment shall be 10,000 <i>cubits</i> toward the east and 10,000 toward the west; and it shall be alongside the holy allotment. And its produce shall be food for the workers of the city.",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>The workers of the city, out of all the tribes of Israel, shall cultivate it.",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>The whole allotment <i>shall be</i> 25,000 by 25,000 <i>cubits</i>; you shall set apart the holy allotment, a square, with the property of the city.",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>“The <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21724P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21724P\"></sup>remainder <i>shall be</i> for the prince, on the one side and on the other of the holy allotment and of the property of the city; in front of the 25,000 <i>cubits</i> of the allotment toward the east border and westward in front of the 25,000 toward the west border, alongside the portions, <i>it shall be</i> for the prince. And the holy allotment and the sanctuary of the house shall be in the middle of it.",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>Exclusive of the property of the Levites and the property of the city, <i>which</i> are in the middle of that which belongs to the prince, <i>everything</i> between the border of Judah and the border of Benjamin shall be for the prince.",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>“As for the rest of the tribes: from the east side to the west side, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21726Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21726Q\"></sup>Benjamin, one <i>portion</i>.",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>Beside the border of Benjamin, from the east side to the west side, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21727R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21727R\"></sup>Simeon, one <i>portion</i>.",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup>Beside the border of Simeon, from the east side to the west side, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21728S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21728S\"></sup>Issachar, one <i>portion</i>.",
			"26": "<sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup>Beside the border of Issachar, from the east side to the west side, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21729T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21729T\"></sup>Zebulun, one <i>portion</i>.",
			"27": "<sup class=\"versenum\">27 </sup>Beside the border of Zebulun, from the east side to the west side, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21730U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21730U\"></sup>Gad, one <i>portion</i>.",
			"28": "<sup class=\"versenum\">28 </sup>And beside the border of Gad, at the south side toward the south, the border shall be from <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21731V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21731V\"></sup>Tamar to the waters of Meribath-kadesh, to the brook <i>of Egypt</i>, to the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21731W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21731W\"></sup>Great Sea.",
			"29": "<sup class=\"versenum\">29 </sup>This is the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21732X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21732X\"></sup>land which you shall divide by lot to the tribes of Israel for an inheritance, and these are their <i>several</i> portions,” declares the Lord <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">God</span>.",
			"30": "<sup class=\"versenum\">30 </sup>“These are the exits of the city: on the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21733Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21733Y\"></sup>north side, 4,500 <i>cubits</i> by measurement,",
			"31": "<sup class=\"versenum\">31 </sup>shall be the gates of the city, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21734Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21734Z\"></sup>named for the tribes of Israel, three gates toward the north: the gate of Reuben, one; the gate of Judah, one; the gate of Levi, one.",
			"32": "<sup class=\"versenum\">32 </sup>On the east side, 4,500 <i>cubits</i>, shall be three gates: the gate of Joseph, one; the gate of Benjamin, one; the gate of Dan, one.",
			"33": "<sup class=\"versenum\">33 </sup>On the south side, 4,500 <i>cubits</i> by measurement, shall be three gates: the gate of Simeon, one; the gate of Issachar, one; the gate of Zebulun, one.",
			"34": "<sup class=\"versenum\">34 </sup>On the west side, 4,500 <i>cubits, shall be</i> three gates: the gate of Gad, one; the gate of Asher, one; the gate of Naphtali, one.",
			"35": "<sup class=\"versenum\">35 </sup><i>The city shall be</i> 18,000 <i>cubits</i> round about; and the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21738AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21738AA\"></sup>name of the city from <i>that</i> day <i>shall be</i>, ‘The <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-21738AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-21738AB\"></sup><span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> is there.’”"
		}
	}
};
module.exports = book;